      &lt;![CDATA[
      body {
        min-width: $(content.width);
      }

      .content-outer, .content-fauxcolumn-outer, .region-inner {
        min-width: $(content.width);
        max-width: $(content.width);
        _width: $(content.width);
      }

      .main-inner .columns {
        padding-left: $(main.column.left.width);
        padding-right: $(main.column.right.width);
      }

      .main-inner .fauxcolumn-center-outer {
        left: $(main.column.left.width);
        right: $(main.column.right.width);
        /* IE6 does not respect left and right together */
        _width: expression(this.parentNode.offsetWidth -
            parseInt("$(main.column.left.width)") -
            parseInt("$(main.column.right.width)") + 'px');
      }

      .main-inner .fauxcolumn-left-outer {
        width: $(main.column.left.width);
      }

      .main-inner .fauxcolumn-right-outer {
        width: $(main.column.right.width);
      }

      .main-inner .column-left-outer {
        width: $(main.column.left.width);
        right: 100%;
        margin-left: -$(main.column.left.width);
      }

      .main-inner .column-right-outer {
        width: $(main.column.right.width);
        margin-right: -$(main.column.right.width);
      }

      #layout {
        min-width: 0;
      }

      #layout .content-outer {
        min-width: 0;
        width: 800px;
      }

      #layout .region-inner {
        min-width: 0;
        width: auto;
      }
      ]]&gt;
    &lt;/b:template-skin&gt;
  &lt;/head&gt;

      &lt;b:section class='header' id='header' maxwidgets='1' showaddelement='no'&gt;
&lt;b:widget id='Header1' locked='true' title='bikini 2012 - swimwear - girl bikini - micro bikini (Header)' type='Header'&gt;

  &lt;b:if cond='data:useImage'&gt;
    &lt;b:if cond='data:imagePlacement == &amp;quot;BEHIND&amp;quot;'&gt;
      &lt;!--
      Show image as background to text. You can't really calculate the width
      reliably in JS because margins are not taken into account by any of
      clientWidth, offsetWidth or scrollWidth, so we don't force a minimum
      width if the user is using shrink to fit.
      This results in a margin-width's worth of pixels being cropped. If the
      user is not using shrink to fit then we expand the header.
      --&gt;
      &lt;b:if cond='data:mobile'&gt;
          &lt;div id='header-inner'&gt;
            &lt;div class='titlewrapper' style='background: transparent'&gt;
              &lt;h1 class='title' style='background: transparent; border-width: 0px'&gt;
                &lt;b:include name='title'/&gt;
              &lt;/h1&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;b:include name='description'/&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;b:else/&gt;
          &lt;div expr:style='&amp;quot;background-image: url(\&amp;quot;&amp;quot; + data:sourceUrl + &amp;quot;\&amp;quot;); &amp;quot;                        + &amp;quot;background-position: &amp;quot;                        + data:backgroundPositionStyleStr + &amp;quot;; &amp;quot;                        + data:widthStyleStr                        + &amp;quot;min-height: &amp;quot; + data:height                        + &amp;quot;_height: &amp;quot; + data:height                        + &amp;quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; &amp;quot;' id='header-inner'&gt;
            &lt;div class='titlewrapper' style='background: transparent'&gt;
              &lt;h1 class='title' style='background: transparent; border-width: 0px'&gt;
                &lt;b:include name='title'/&gt;
              &lt;/h1&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;b:include name='description'/&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/b:if&gt;
    &lt;b:else/&gt;
      &lt;!--Show the image only--&gt;
      &lt;div id='header-inner'&gt;
        &lt;a expr:href='data:blog.homepageUrl' style='display: block'&gt;
          &lt;img expr:alt='data:title' expr:height='data:height' expr:id='data:widget.instanceId + &amp;quot;_headerimg&amp;quot;' expr:src='data:sourceUrl' expr:width='data:width' style='display: block'/&gt;
        &lt;/a&gt;
        &lt;!--Show the description--&gt;
        &lt;b:if cond='data:imagePlacement == &amp;quot;BEFORE_DESCRIPTION&amp;quot;'&gt;
          &lt;b:include name='description'/&gt;
        &lt;/b:if&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/b:if&gt;
  &lt;b:else/&gt;
    &lt;!--No header image --&gt;

      &lt;/div&gt;

        &lt;div class='status-msg-hidden'&gt;&lt;data:navMessage/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div style='clear: both;'/&gt;
  &lt;/b:if&gt;
&lt;/b:includable&gt;
&lt;b:includable id='comment-form' var='post'&gt;
  &lt;div class='comment-form'&gt;
    &lt;a name='comment-form'/&gt;
    &lt;b:if cond='data:mobile'&gt;
      &lt;h4 id='comment-post-message'&gt;
        &lt;a expr:id='data:widget.instanceId + &amp;quot;_comment-editor-toggle-link&amp;quot;' href='javascript:void(0)'&gt;&lt;data:postCommentMsg/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;&lt;data:blogCommentMessage/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;data:blogTeamBlogMessage/&gt;
      &lt;a expr:href='data:post.commentFormIframeSrc' id='comment-editor-src'/&gt;
      &lt;iframe allowtransparency='true' class='blogger-iframe-colorize blogger-comment-from-post' frameborder='0' height='410' id='comment-editor' name='comment-editor' src='' style='display: none' width='100%'/&gt;
    &lt;b:else/&gt;
      &lt;h4 id='comment-post-message'&gt;&lt;data:postCommentMsg/&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;&lt;data:blogCommentMessage/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;data:blogTeamBlogMessage/&gt;
      &lt;a expr:href='data:post.commentFormIframeSrc' id='comment-editor-src'/&gt;
      &lt;iframe allowtransparency='true' class='blogger-iframe-colorize blogger-comment-from-post' frameborder='0' height='410' id='comment-editor' name='comment-editor' src='' width='100%'/&gt;
    &lt;/b:if&gt;
    &lt;data:post.friendConnectJs/&gt;
    &lt;data:post.cmtfpIframe/&gt;
    &lt;script type='text/javascript'&gt;
      BLOG_CMT_createIframe(&amp;#39;&lt;data:post.appRpcRelayPath/&gt;&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;&lt;data:post.communityId/&gt;&amp;#39;);
    &lt;/script&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

      &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;/b:if&gt;

    &lt;span expr:class='&amp;quot;item-control &amp;quot; + data:post.adminClass'&gt;

&lt;b:includable id='main' var='top'&gt;

  &lt;b:if cond='data:mobileindex'&gt;
    &lt;!-- mobile index --&gt;
    &lt;div class='blog-posts hfeed'&gt;
      &lt;b:loop values='data:posts' var='post'&gt;
        &lt;b:if cond='data:post.isFirstPost == &amp;quot;false&amp;quot;'&gt;
          &amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
        &lt;/b:if&gt;
        &amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;mobile-date-outer date-outer&amp;quot;&amp;gt;
        &lt;b:include data='post' name='mobile-index-post'/&gt;
        &lt;b:if cond='data:post.trackLatency'&gt;
          &lt;data:post.latencyJs/&gt;
        &lt;/b:if&gt;
      &lt;/b:loop&gt;
      &lt;b:if cond='data:numPosts != 0'&gt;
        &amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
      &lt;/b:if&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;b:else/&gt;

    &lt;!-- posts --&gt;
    &lt;div class='blog-posts hfeed'&gt;

      &lt;b:include data='top' name='status-message'/&gt;

      &lt;data:defaultAdStart/&gt;
      &lt;b:loop values='data:posts' var='post'&gt;
        &lt;b:if cond='data:post.isDateStart'&gt;
          &lt;b:if cond='data:post.isFirstPost == &amp;quot;false&amp;quot;'&gt;
            &amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
          &lt;/b:if&gt;
        &lt;/b:if&gt;
        &lt;b:if cond='data:post.isDateStart'&gt;
          &amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;date-outer&amp;quot;&amp;gt;
        &lt;/b:if&gt;
        &lt;b:if cond='data:post.dateHeader'&gt;
          &lt;h2 class='date-header'&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;data:post.dateHeader/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
        &lt;/b:if&gt;
        &lt;b:if cond='data:post.isDateStart'&gt;
          &amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;date-posts&amp;quot;&amp;gt;
        &lt;/b:if&gt;
        &lt;div class='post-outer'&gt;
        &lt;b:include data='post' name='post'/&gt;
        &lt;b:if cond='data:blog.pageType == &amp;quot;static_page&amp;quot;'&gt;
          &lt;b:include data='post' name='comments'/&gt;
        &lt;/b:if&gt;
        &lt;b:if cond='data:blog.pageType == &amp;quot;item&amp;quot;'&gt;
          &lt;b:include data='post' name='comments'/&gt;
        &lt;/b:if&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;b:if cond='data:post.includeAd'&gt;
          &lt;b:if cond='data:post.isFirstPost'&gt;
            &lt;data:defaultAdEnd/&gt;
          &lt;b:else/&gt;
            &lt;data:adEnd/&gt;
          &lt;/b:if&gt;
          &lt;b:if cond='data:mobile == &amp;quot;false&amp;quot;'&gt;
            &lt;div class='inline-ad'&gt;
              &lt;data:adCode/&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/b:if&gt;
          &lt;data:adStart/&gt;
        &lt;/b:if&gt;
        &lt;b:if cond='data:post.trackLatency'&gt;
          &lt;data:post.latencyJs/&gt;
        &lt;/b:if&gt;
      &lt;/b:loop&gt;
      &lt;b:if cond='data:numPosts != 0'&gt;
        &amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
      &lt;/b:if&gt;
      &lt;data:adEnd/&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/b:if&gt;

  &lt;!-- navigation --&gt;
  &lt;b:if cond='data:mobile'&gt;
    &lt;b:include name='mobile-nextprev'/&gt;
  &lt;b:else/&gt;
    &lt;b:include name='nextprev'/&gt;

    &lt;!-- feed links --&gt;
    &lt;b:include name='feedLinks'/&gt;
  &lt;/b:if&gt;

  &lt;b:if cond='data:top.showStars'&gt;
    &lt;script src='//www.google.com/jsapi' type='text/javascript'/&gt;
    &lt;script type='text/javascript'&gt;
      google.load(&amp;quot;annotations&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;1&amp;quot;, {&amp;quot;locale&amp;quot;: &amp;quot;&lt;data:top.languageCode/&gt;&amp;quot;});
      function initialize() {
        google.annotations.setApplicationId(&lt;data:top.blogspotReviews/&gt;);
        google.annotations.createAll();
        google.annotations.fetch();
      }
      google.setOnLoadCallback(initialize);
    &lt;/script&gt;
  &lt;/b:if&gt;

  &lt;b:if cond='data:top.showDummy'&gt;
    &lt;data:top.dummyBootstrap/&gt;
  &lt;/b:if&gt;

&lt;/b:includable&gt;
&lt;b:includable id='commentDeleteIcon' var='comment'&gt;
  &lt;span expr:class='&amp;quot;item-control &amp;quot; + data:comment.adminClass'&gt;
    &lt;b:if cond='data:showCmtPopup'&gt;
      &lt;div class='goog-toggle-button'&gt;
        &lt;div class='goog-inline-block comment-action-icon'/&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;b:else/&gt;
      &lt;a class='comment-delete' expr:href='data:comment.deleteUrl' expr:title='data:top.deleteCommentMsg'&gt;

      &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/b:if&gt;
  &lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/b:includable&gt;
&lt;b:includable id='feedLinks'&gt;
  &lt;b:if cond='data:blog.pageType != &amp;quot;item&amp;quot;'&gt; &lt;!-- Blog feed links --&gt;
    &lt;b:if cond='data:feedLinks'&gt;
      &lt;div class='blog-feeds'&gt;
        &lt;b:include data='feedLinks' name='feedLinksBody'/&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/b:if&gt;

    &lt;b:else/&gt; &lt;!--Post feed links --&gt;
    &lt;div class='post-feeds'&gt;
      &lt;b:loop values='data:posts' var='post'&gt;
        &lt;b:if cond='data:post.allowComments'&gt;
          &lt;b:if cond='data:post.feedLinks'&gt;
            &lt;b:include data='post.feedLinks' name='feedLinksBody'/&gt;
          &lt;/b:if&gt;
        &lt;/b:if&gt;
      &lt;/b:loop&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/b:if&gt;
&lt;/b:includable&gt;
&lt;b:includable id='mobile-index-post' var='post'&gt;
  &lt;b:if cond='data:post.dateHeader'&gt;
    &lt;div class='mobile-index-date'&gt;
      &lt;div class='date-header'&gt;
        &lt;span&gt;&lt;data:post.dateHeader/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/b:if&gt;

  &lt;div class='mobile-post-outer'&gt;
    &lt;a expr:href='data:post.url'&gt;
      &lt;div class='mobile-index-title-outer'&gt;
        &lt;h3 class='mobile-index-title entry-title'&gt;
          &lt;data:post.title/&gt;
        &lt;/h3&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;

      &lt;div&gt;
        &lt;div class='mobile-index-arrow'&gt;
          &amp;amp;rsaquo;
        &lt;/div&gt;

        &lt;div class='mobile-index-contents'&gt;
          &lt;b:if cond='data:post.thumbnailUrl'&gt;
            &lt;div class='mobile-index-thumbnail'&gt;
              &lt;div class='Image'&gt;
                &lt;img expr:src='data:post.thumbnailUrl'/&gt;
              &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/b:if&gt;

          &lt;div class='post-body'&gt;
            &lt;b:if cond='data:post.snippet'&gt;&lt;data:post.snippet/&gt;&lt;/b:if&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div style='clear: both;'/&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/a&gt;

    &lt;div class='mobile-index-comment'&gt;
      &lt;b:if cond='data:blog.pageType != &amp;quot;item&amp;quot;'&gt;
        &lt;b:if cond='data:blog.pageType != &amp;quot;static_page&amp;quot;'&gt;
          &lt;b:if cond='data:post.allowComments'&gt;
            &lt;b:if cond='data:post.numComments != 0'&gt;
              &lt;a class='comment-link' expr:href='data:post.addCommentUrl' expr:onclick='data:post.addCommentOnclick'&gt;&lt;b:if cond='data:post.numComments == 1'&gt;1 &lt;data:top.commentLabel/&gt;&lt;b:else/&gt;&lt;data:post.numComments/&gt; &lt;data:top.commentLabelPlural/&gt;&lt;/b:if&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
            &lt;/b:if&gt;
          &lt;/b:if&gt;
        &lt;/b:if&gt;
      &lt;/b:if&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;data:feedLinksMsg/&gt;
  &lt;b:loop values='data:links' var='f'&gt;
     &lt;a class='feed-link' expr:href='data:f.url' expr:type='data:f.mimeType' target='_blank'&gt;&lt;data:f.name/&gt; (&lt;data:f.feedType/&gt;)&lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;/b:loop&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/b:includable&gt;
&lt;b:includable id='comments' var='post'&gt;
  &lt;div class='comments' id='comments'&gt;
    &lt;a name='comments'/&gt;
    &lt;b:if cond='data:post.allowComments'&gt;
      &lt;h4&gt;
        &lt;b:if cond='data:post.numComments == 1'&gt;
          1 &lt;data:commentLabel/&gt;:
        &lt;b:else/&gt;
          &lt;data:post.numComments/&gt; &lt;data:commentLabelPlural/&gt;:
        &lt;/b:if&gt;
      &lt;/h4&gt;

      &lt;b:if cond='data:post.commentPagingRequired'&gt;
        &lt;span class='paging-control-container'&gt;
          &lt;a expr:class='data:post.oldLinkClass' expr:href='data:post.oldestLinkUrl'&gt;&lt;data:post.oldestLinkText/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
          &amp;#160;
          &lt;a expr:class='data:post.oldLinkClass' expr:href='data:post.olderLinkUrl'&gt;&lt;data:post.olderLinkText/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
          &amp;#160;
          &lt;data:post.commentRangeText/&gt;
          &amp;#160;
          &lt;a expr:class='data:post.newLinkClass' expr:href='data:post.newerLinkUrl'&gt;&lt;data:post.newerLinkText/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
          &amp;#160;
          &lt;a expr:class='data:post.newLinkClass' expr:href='data:post.newestLinkUrl'&gt;&lt;data:post.newestLinkText/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
        &lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;/b:if&gt;

      &lt;div expr:id='data:widget.instanceId + &amp;quot;_comments-block-wrapper&amp;quot;'&gt;
        &lt;dl expr:class='data:post.avatarIndentClass' id='comments-block'&gt;
          &lt;b:loop values='data:post.comments' var='comment'&gt;
            &lt;dt expr:class='&amp;quot;comment-author &amp;quot; + data:comment.authorClass' expr:id='data:comment.anchorName'&gt;
              &lt;b:if cond='data:comment.favicon'&gt;
                &lt;img expr:src='data:comment.favicon' height='16px' style='margin-bottom:-2px;' width='16px'/&gt;
              &lt;/b:if&gt;
              &lt;a expr:name='data:comment.anchorName'/&gt;
              &lt;b:if cond='data:blog.enabledCommentProfileImages'&gt;
                &lt;data:comment.authorAvatarImage/&gt;
              &lt;/b:if&gt;
              &lt;b:if cond='data:comment.authorUrl'&gt;
                &lt;a expr:href='data:comment.authorUrl' rel='nofollow'&gt;&lt;data:comment.author/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
              &lt;b:else/&gt;
                &lt;data:comment.author/&gt;
              &lt;/b:if&gt;
              &lt;data:commentPostedByMsg/&gt;
            &lt;/dt&gt;
            &lt;dd class='comment-body' expr:id='data:widget.instanceId + data:comment.cmtBodyIdPostfix'&gt;
              &lt;b:if cond='data:comment.isDeleted'&gt;
                &lt;span class='deleted-comment'&gt;&lt;data:comment.body/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
              &lt;b:else/&gt;
                &lt;p&gt;
                  &lt;data:comment.body/&gt;
                &lt;/p&gt;
              &lt;/b:if&gt;
            &lt;/dd&gt;
            &lt;dd class='comment-footer'&gt;
              &lt;span class='comment-timestamp'&gt;
                &lt;a expr:href='data:comment.url' title='comment permalink'&gt;
                  &lt;data:comment.timestamp/&gt;
                &lt;/a&gt;
                &lt;b:include data='comment' name='commentDeleteIcon'/&gt;
              &lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/dd&gt;
          &lt;/b:loop&gt;
        &lt;/dl&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;

      &lt;b:if cond='data:post.commentPagingRequired'&gt;
        &lt;span class='paging-control-container'&gt;
          &lt;a expr:class='data:post.oldLinkClass' expr:href='data:post.oldestLinkUrl'&gt;
            &lt;data:post.oldestLinkText/&gt;
          &lt;/a&gt;
          &lt;a expr:class='data:post.oldLinkClass' expr:href='data:post.olderLinkUrl'&gt;
            &lt;data:post.olderLinkText/&gt;
          &lt;/a&gt;
          &amp;#160;
          &lt;data:post.commentRangeText/&gt;
          &amp;#160;
          &lt;a expr:class='data:post.newLinkClass' expr:href='data:post.newerLinkUrl'&gt;
            &lt;data:post.newerLinkText/&gt;
          &lt;/a&gt;
          &lt;a expr:class='data:post.newLinkClass' expr:href='data:post.newestLinkUrl'&gt;
            &lt;data:post.newestLinkText/&gt;
          &lt;/a&gt;
        &lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;/b:if&gt;

      &lt;p class='comment-footer'&gt;
        &lt;b:if cond='data:post.embedCommentForm'&gt;
          &lt;b:if cond='data:post.allowNewComments'&gt;
            &lt;b:include data='post' name='comment-form'/&gt;
          &lt;b:else/&gt;
            &lt;data:post.noNewCommentsText/&gt;
          &lt;/b:if&gt;
        &lt;b:else/&gt;
          &lt;b:if cond='data:post.allowComments'&gt;
            &lt;a expr:href='data:post.addCommentUrl' expr:onclick='data:post.addCommentOnclick'&gt;&lt;data:postCommentMsg/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
          &lt;/b:if&gt;
        &lt;/b:if&gt;

      &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/b:if&gt;
    &lt;b:if cond='data:showCmtPopup'&gt;
      &lt;div id='comment-popup'&gt;
        &lt;iframe allowtransparency='true' frameborder='0' id='comment-actions' name='comment-actions' scrolling='no'&gt;
        &lt;/iframe&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/b:if&gt;

    &lt;div id='backlinks-container'&gt;
    &lt;div expr:id='data:widget.instanceId + &amp;quot;_backlinks-container&amp;quot;'&gt;
       &lt;b:if cond='data:post.showBacklinks'&gt;
         &lt;b:include data='post' name='backlinks'/&gt;
       &lt;/b:if&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

Cng vi cuc thi Vietnam's Next Top Model, Trang   quyt nh Nam tin tm c hi trong s nghip ngi mu v ca ht.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody"&gt;Hai nm sau nhng thnh cng ban u t cuc thi Miss Teen,  m Thu Trang chia s c dng nh khng cn hp vi hnh nh ca mt  ngi sao tui teen na, bi lc no c cng c v gi hn trc tui. B  hnh rt nng m m Thu Trang va thc hin l mt minh chng cho s  trng thnh vi hnh nh mt lady m m Thu Trang ang hng ti.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody"&gt;Trong b hnh ny, m Thu Trang  ph din v gi cm, thanh tn ca mt c gi tr ang tui trng thnh.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" width="200"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="'Nng' vi hnh nh mi ca Miss Nhng vi  bn lnh v s t tin, Nguyn Th Loan  chinh phc c ban gim kho.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody"&gt;Nguyn  Th Loan hin l sinh vin H Thng Mi, cao 1,74m, nng 55kg vi s  o ba vng: 89  64  91. Khng c ch  c bit t nhng vng ngoi  nhng Loan li thu ht ngi i din bi mt v mc mc, khe khon.  Ngay sau khi ng quang, khi c cc phng vin vy quanh, c cng chia  s ht sc bt ng vi danh hiu ny.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody"&gt;Sinh ra trong  gia nh nh nng  x Hng Chu, huyn Tin Hi, Thi Bnh, b m cao  1m64, nhng Loan v cu em trai li nhanh chng pht trin chiu cao t  nhng nm cp 2. Nm hc lp 8, c khn gi ln H Ni gia nhp vo i  bng chuyn tr th  vi v tr ch cng. Nhng hin ti, c ang theo  hc ti i hc Thng Mi vi mong mun s tr thnh mt doanh nhn  trong tng lai.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pHead" style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="oImage" alt="Ngm nhan sc ngi p Sau khi xem cc hnh nh do chng ti cung cp, ng Vit bc  xc: Khng th c kiu trnh din bikini no m c nhng ng tc v n  mc phn cm nh th ny c.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;i&gt; &lt;/i&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Khi c hi  bo co ton b s vic cho ng H  Vn Nin - ph ch tch UBND tnh, ph ban t chc ph trch an ninh l  hi. n ti cng ngy, ng H Vn Nin  ch o dng ngay chng  trnh biu din phn cm ny vo cc m cn li v yu cu ng Hunh  Trung Nam - ch tch HQT kim tng gim c Imperial Group, ngi chu  trch nhim v chng trnh ny - bo co ton b v vic.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;MINH LUN (&lt;cite&gt;Tui Tr Online)&lt;/cite&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div "khng" m c cng phi tri  qua cc vng casting nh bao din vin khc.&lt;p style="text-align: justify;" class="pBody"&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Cho Elly, cm gic ca bn th no khi  ln u tin c mi ng phim, li may mn c tham gia b phim 3D  u tin ca Vit Nam?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;" class="pBody"&gt;- y khng phi l ln u tin mnh ng phim. Trc ,  Elly  tham gia mt b phim nha ti Thi Lan ri, nhng &lt;em&gt;Hn ma  siu quy&lt;/em&gt; l phim 3D u tin Elly tham gia cng ng thi l flim  3D u tin sn xut ti Vit Nam. Mnh rt vui v bt ng khi c ng  gp vo nn in nh nc nh, nht l dng phim 3D m khn gi tr  ang trng i rt nhiu.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;" class="pBody"&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Elly c c dn mng bit n nh vng 1 "ngoi  c", vy bn ngh sao nu c nhiu  kin cho rng Elly c mi ng  phim l nh chuyn ? &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;" class="pBody"&gt;- Khng ng, mnh cng n vi vai din mt cch bnh  thng nh bao bn khc. Mnh cng phi tri qua cc vng casting   nhn vai ch khng phi c nhn vai lun. Theo mnh ngh cu tr li  tt nht khng phi by gi, m l lc phim ra mt, cc khn gi s l  ngi thay mnh tr li cu hi ny.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width="200" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/372/t372534.jpg" class="oImage" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" alt="Hot girl Elly: 'c nhn vai  khng phi v vng 1'" align="middle" border="0" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;" class="pBody"&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Elly tng chia s mun  mt vai din khng sexy, vy cn vai din ln ny ca Elly liu c  thot khi s sexy? &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;" class="pBody"&gt;- Tht kh  chia s v vai din mi ca mnh trong b  phim &lt;em&gt;Hn ma siu quy &lt;/em&gt;bi pha nh sn xut vn mun gi kn  tn n khi phim cng chiu. Elly thch gi cht bt ng khi khn gi  xem phim v th, xin khng tit l thm v vai din ny. Nhng thng tin  chung vn c on phim cng b ti hp bo trc  ri. Ch bit  rng y l mt vai din mi l, mt s tri nghim mi v nhn vt  khin Elly mong mun c th thch v khng nh. V vai din trong  phim khc hon ton vi Elly ngoi i. y va l kh khn nhng cng  l mt ng lc  mnh tp trung hon thnh tt nhn vt ca mnh.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;" class="pBody"&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Ct-x ng phim ca  Elly cng cao hn nhng din vin khc. Phi chng vic lin tc c  cc mi tham gia cc d n  nc ngoi  chi phi n th lao ng  phim trong nc ca bn?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;" class="pBody"&gt;- Mnh cng khng tm hiu nhiu v mc ct-x chung hin  nay, mnh ch nhn mc ct x xng ng vi cng sc ca mnh m thi.  Vic tham gia cc s kin  nc ngoi cng khng th lm cho mc ct-s  ca mnh tng cao so vi nhiu din vin khc. Ct-x c tr theo  ng nhng g m mnh lm c. Hn na mnh cng tng i hc thm  mt lp din xut ri nn vic tham gia nhiu d n phim trong thi gian  ny thc s l mt tri nghim tt vi Elly. iu kh khn u tin l  phi t t mnh vo nhn vt, c li suy ngh cng nh thi quen .&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;" class="pBody"&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Mt vi hot girl i  ng phim nhng khng vt qua ci bng ca chnh mnh,  b ch trch  v din xut khng ti, iu  c gy p lc cho bn?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;" class="pBody"&gt;- Elly khng mun so snh  mnh vi cch hot girl khc i ng phim. Ring v iu ny Elly s  chng minh khi tham gia din xut 3 phim ti Vit Nam trong nm nay,  ha thn vo nhng nhn vt hon ton khng ging vi c tnh ca mnh  ngoi i tht. thng bng  bt tay vo nhng d n mi.  C ngi mu gc Bc Ninh  khng ngn ngi mc bikini v to dng  trc ngay trn bi bin, trc s ng ngng ca rt nhiu ngi. bikini'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-5372837114884406432</id><published>2010-07-01T20:19:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:39.788-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hoa Hu - Siu Mu'/><title type='text'>Nhng m nhn Vit c nguy c " chng"</title><content type='html'>&lt;h2 class="detail_sapo"&gt;Ti nng, xinh p, thng minh, sc so, ni  ting v thnh cng i khi chnh l ro cn ca nhng m nhn Vit n  vi hnh phc  &lt;/h2&gt;  &lt;div class="detail_content"&gt;  &lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng  Thanh Vn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/07/01/22/22/Ngo-Thanh-Van.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/07/01/22/22/Ngo-Thanh-Van.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Xinh p,  ti nng, bn lnh chnh l con dao hai li ngn cn hnh phc n vi  &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Thanh Vn&lt;/span&gt;. Sau rt nhiu  scandal khng mong mun, nhng n o lin quan n&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt; Quc Bo&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Tun Hng&lt;/span&gt; v gn y nht l "dnh" nh hnh vi bng vi &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Johnny Tr Nguyn&lt;/span&gt;. Bt k nhng  scandal no lin quan n &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Thanh Vn&lt;/span&gt;  u rt &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;"lm xm"&lt;/span&gt; v tn nhiu  giy mc ca bo gii nhng Vn lun chn cch im lng v tng li n,  iu  cng chnh l b quyt  c c c ngy hm nay, mt din vin  c nh gi cao, mt doanh nhn trin vng v l mt ngi ni ting  c ng cp c &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;"thch i thch li"&lt;/span&gt;  trong sut 10 nm tri trong lng gii tr Vit.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;oan Trang&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/07/01/22/34/doan-trang.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/07/01/22/34/doan-trang.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Gn y,  ngi p &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;S C La&lt;/span&gt; tit l rng  ang c ngi yu l Vit Kiu nhng ch ang trong giai on...tm  hiu, mt ip khc vn lun c cc ngi p&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt; "mun chng"&lt;/span&gt; chia s. Tnh cch rt nh hng n  chuyn tnh cm v &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;oan Trang&lt;/span&gt;  khng nm ngoi l, c c &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;"nt"&lt;/span&gt;,  trang im nh nhng s p nhng n mc rt c...vn , c lun thch  ni tri bng cch ly trang phc "" ging ht, thch s ch ng v  lun mun mnh l tm im ca m ng. n c nh s vic va ri, c   n mc style "vn khng nh trng" i d tic. iu  d khin  ngi khc ngh n s bng bt, cha chn lm ln trong cch to dng  hnh nh ca oan Trang. V trong tnh yu, c l mt ngi lun mun  mnh ch ng v khc ngi, iu ny d lm n ng...s.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Thu Minh&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/07/01/22/43/Thu-Minh.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 450px; height: 676px;" src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/07/01/22/43/Thu-Minh.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Ngi p  "Chung gi" &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Thu Minh&lt;/span&gt; cng c  lit vo danh sch c th  chng bi nt c tnh n d di ca c.  Tt va ri, tng chng tm thip mi hnh phc ca &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Thu Minh&lt;/span&gt; s c trao cho nhng ngi  bn nhng ri li hon. Con tim ca &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Thu  Minh&lt;/span&gt; vn ang "loay hoay" tm bn b hnh phc thc s ca mnh,  dng c vn cha thc s quyt on trong vn  ny. Gi nh s la  chn sng sut l &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;"ra ch"&lt;/span&gt;   ht c Thu Minh "p" vo trong Tnh yu th c l &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Thu Minh&lt;/span&gt; s khng cn phi mt mnh.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Kiu Thanh &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/07/01/22/56/kieu-thanh.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 450px; height: 672px;" src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/07/01/22/56/kieu-thanh.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Cc vai din a  trun, c s phn o le  "m" vo cuc sng ca &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Kiu Thanh&lt;/span&gt;. C vn&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt; "mt mnh ta vi ta"&lt;/span&gt; v kh khn  trong vic la chn  trung nhn. Ngi ngoi nhn vo, tng rng c c  mt cuc sng si ni nhng thc ra c l mt ngi sng ni tm v rt  thiu thn tnh cm.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;H Qunh Hng&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/07/01/23/02/ho-quynh-huong.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 451px; height: 677px;" src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/07/01/23/02/ho-quynh-huong.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Sau khi chia  tay vi H Dng, &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;H Qunh Hng&lt;/span&gt;  tha nhn rng li l  n ng, &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;H  Dng&lt;/span&gt; - ngi khng bit gi c. Mi quan h n o gia mt i  gia v c ca s ny l  ti c bn tn nhiu nht trong mt thi  gian di. C th thy c mt  dy nht s xut hin ca h trn bo  gii l bt c khi no ra sp, hnh nh ca H Qunh Hng ph y cc  mt bo v lp la lp lng chuyn yu, khng yu vi thy c, H Dng.  Hin ti, giai nhn ny ang c n bi mt l c ang tiu tn qu  nhiu thi gian cho cng cuc &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;"trng  tu"&lt;/span&gt; nhan sc m qun vic c  n tui ly chng (?)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;M  Tm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/07/01/23/13/My-Tam.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/07/01/23/13/My-Tam.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;M Tm&lt;/span&gt;  lun c nhc n l mt ca s thnh cng nht trong lp ca s tr.  Qua thi k nh cao, &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;M Tm&lt;/span&gt; c  c ch ng ring trong lng khn gi nhng vic c c mt ch ng  trong tri tim ngi c yu sao m kh qu. V tnh yu, c khng bao  gi dm k l trn bo ch v th, chuyn M Tm yu ai vn ang l mt  n s cha c gii. Hin ti, M Tm mit mi lm t thin, tm kim  s tnh tm trong tm hn, s cn bng trong cuc sng sau qung thi  gian si ni ca tui tr c  cng hin cho m nhc. Hy vng rng &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;M Tm&lt;/span&gt; s sm tm c mt na ch  thc ca mnh trong thi gian sm.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;L Quyn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/07/01/23/23/Le-Quyen.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 448px; height: 672px;" src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/07/01/23/23/Le-Quyen.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;C ca s a  oan gc H Thnh nh &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;"qu bom n  chm",&lt;/span&gt; ging ht nh nhng, mt m hp nhng bn tnh ca c tit  tu chm ri chnh v th chuyn tnh yu ca c cng trm v khng c  g khi sc. Cui 2009, &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;L Quyn&lt;/span&gt;  b li ng sau s a oan li th , c lng nghe con tim quyt tm  Nam tin v s nghip m nhc v hn ht l theo ting gi ca con tim,  ngp ngh tui 30 ri nn lng c c l cng ang "nh la t".&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Mai Khi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/07/01/23/32/Mai-Khoi.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 450px; height: 900px;" src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/07/01/23/32/Mai-Khoi.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;"Ngi  n b tr con"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt; Mai Khi &lt;/span&gt;c  l tng sng v nhng suy ngh rt cc oan, c sng v yu ht mnh,  qun ht ngy mai v c  tng tuyn b rng khng mun c con, v con  ci ch l ci n nn v l v mt i ngi lun kh au nhiu hn hnh  phc v khng mun to thm mt&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt; kip  kh&lt;/span&gt; na.  tui mn m hn 2 siu mu tr, nhng  n din vin &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Halle Berry &lt;/span&gt;cng  th hin sc nng ca mnh khng ch  s o 3 vng ng ghen t ca  bit bao c gi tr, m nc da mu chocolate khe khon ca c cng  khin ci nhn v n din vin ny tr nn y sc sng hn bao gi. L ph n,  bn cng cn quan tm ti cc ch s vng mt ca mnh. Nu bn c vng  ngc ngoi c nh ti, vic la chn chic bra ph hp l yu t rt  quan trng. Trong thi  gian ti, Kelly s xut hin trn tp ch Playboy vi mt b nh c  bit. scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><title type='text'>Chu Tinh Tr, Chu Nhun Pht tr thnh t ph Trung Quc</title><content type='html'>&lt;h2 class="detail_sapo"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:100%;"&gt;Hai "ng trm gii tr" h Chu hin ang s hu  khi ti sn ln ti hng t nhn dn t.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;  &lt;div class="detail_content"&gt;  &lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/06/04/06/48/0406tiphuhongkong1.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/06/04/06/48/0406tiphuhongkong1.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Bo ch Trung Quc a tin v hai ng t ph  lng gii tr ny.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Gn y, khi gi nh t  Hong  Kong bc vo thi k iu chnh, khng t ngh s trong lng gii tr  lin rc rch u t vo lnh vc y thu ht ny. Trn thc t, u t  vo bt ng sn lun l con ng lm giu ca nhiu ngh s, trong   hai ngi sao hng u&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt; Chu Nhun Pht &lt;/span&gt;v  &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Chu Tinh Tr&lt;/span&gt; l nhng t ph  tiu biu trong lng gii tr giu ln nh bit u t ng cch vo  ngnh ny. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/06/04/06/48/0406tiphuhongkong2.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/06/04/06/48/0406tiphuhongkong2.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/06/04/06/48/0406tiphuhongkong3.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/06/04/06/48/0406tiphuhongkong3.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/06/04/06/49/0406tiphuhongkong4.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/06/04/06/49/0406tiphuhongkong4.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Chu  Nhun Pht&lt;/span&gt; c coi l ngi sao in nh hng u ca ln gii  tr Hoa ng, k t khi tn cng thnh cng vo kinh  in nh  Hollywood, ct-x ca anh ln ti 5 triu la M (khong 40 triu la  Hong Kong). Ngoi kh nng kim tin ca mnh, &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Chu Nhun Pht&lt;/span&gt; cn c mt u th vt tri l ngi v  ti nng trong lnh vc qun l ti chnh. Hin nay, &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Chu Nhun Pht&lt;/span&gt; c trong tay 7 hng  mc bt ng sn  Hong Kong vi gi tr khong 800 triu nhn dn t.  Nu cng thm bt ng sn, c phiu v tin gi tit kim  nc ngoi,  ngi sao ny s hu khi ti sn ln ti hng t nhn dn t.  &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/06/04/06/49/0406tiphuhongkong5.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/06/04/06/49/0406tiphuhongkong5.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/06/04/06/49/0406tiphuhongkong7.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/06/04/06/49/0406tiphuhongkong7.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/06/04/06/50/0406tiphuhongkong6.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/06/04/06/50/0406tiphuhongkong6.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;ng "vua hi kch" ca in nh Hong Kong &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Chu Tinh Tr &lt;/span&gt;cng l mt i gia  trong lng gii tr. Ngoi vic lm o din v ng phim, &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Chu Tinh Tr&lt;/span&gt; cn u t vo c phiu  v bt ng sn, c bit gn y s kin anh tr thnh c ng ch cht  ca mt cng ty  a gi tr c phiu trong tay anh ln ti 85 triu  t.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Thnh cng trong u t c phiu, song &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Chu Tinh Tr &lt;/span&gt;cn xut sc hn trong  u t vo bt ng sn. o din  din vin ni ting ny  c bit  gy kinh ngc cho gii bt ng sn khi cho d b mt ta nh khng l   ti thit li vi li nhun d tnh c th ln ti gn 2 t nhn dn  t.  &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: right;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;Subbie&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;Theo  Tom&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-6712520873317318962?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/6712520873317318962'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/6712520873317318962'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2010/06/chau-tinh-tri-chau-nhuan-phat-tro-thanh.html' title='Chu Tinh Tr, Chu Nhun Pht tr thnh t ph Trung Quc'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-3103278734476621365</id><published>2010-04-08T20:47:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:42.940-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hoa Hu - Siu Mu'/><title type='text'>Siu mu Ngc Bch gi cm vi bikini</title><content type='html'>Ci b hnh tng mt Ngc Bch c v ngoan hin gn  lin vi nhng vic lm t thin, Ngc Bch "phin bn mi" 2010 l mt  c gi y v gi cm trong nhng b bikini.&lt;p class="pBody"&gt;ot  gii vng Siu mu Vit Nam 2009, tuy nhin, con ng s nghip ngi  mu ca Ngc Bch c v khng my thun li khi lin tc b mang ra so  snh vi Hunh Thanh Tuyn - ngi p trt chn trong s k vng ca  nhiu khn gi. href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2010/04/thai-ha-goi-cam-tren-giuong.html' title='Thi H gi cm trn ging'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-3167051710188276006</id><published>2010-03-27T10:59:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:43.480-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hot Girl - Scandal'/><title type='text'>Hong Thy Linh: 'Khng th c hn nhin mi c'</title><content type='html'>C ca s tr li m nhc vi hnh nh nng bng v cho  rng mnh  la chn ph hp  chinh phc khn gi.&lt;p class="pQuestion"&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Ti sao Linh li chn thi im ny  pht hnh  abum khi m nhc Vit ang b bo ha, ca s ra album m m nh g   trng?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: left;"&gt;- Ti ngh m  nhc Vit cn mt "thi k qu " nh hin nay  dn i vo s chuyn  nghip v pht trin. S si ng trong m nhc hin nay gia gi tr  o v gi tr tht s khin chng ta hi mng lung mt cht.  l iu  tt yu trong mt x hi ang pht trin nn chng ta khng nn qu kht  khe v s chuyn ha ny.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: left;"&gt;Ti  ngh cn c s cnh tranh  to ra nhng sn phm cht lng.  nhng  ngi i trc khng ch bit ngi yn mt ch v nhng ngi tr tui   im xut pht h s phi n lc nhiu hn. Khn gi s c nhiu s la  chn hn. Ti ngh  l iu tt bi trong s pht trin lun c nhiu  mt ca n v chng ta phi khch quan. Cn ring bn thn ti, ti  khng c quyn la chn thi im mnh c sinh ra. V th trong bt k  hon cnh no ti cng vn phi c gng, n lc  thc hin c m ca  mnh thi.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" width="200"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="oImage" alt="Hong Thy Linh: 'Gi cm l th mnh ca ti!'" onclick="return  showImage(this.src)" src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/309/t309349.jpg" align="middle" border="0" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class="pQuestion"&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Tr li vi hnh nh mt c gi gi cm, phi  chng Hong Thy Linh ang hng ti xy dng hnh tng "sexy singer"  ang rt thnh hnh trong showbiz Vit?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: left;"&gt;- Ti chn ci ph hp vi mnh, chn s  trng v th mnh ca mnh ch khng chn ci ang thnh hnh. Bi khi  n ht thnh hnh, khi bn khng bit phi khai thc nh th no na,  bn s li tip tc loay hoay tm gii php tnh th  cu ly tn tui  ca mnh. Chn ci thnh hnh m khng phi th mnh ca bn, bn s  ch bit i bt chc m khng c s sng to.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: left;"&gt;Lm tt vic ca mnh th lc no bn cng c  mt ch ng ring trong lng khn gi ch khng cn phi ua theo ci  ang thnh hnh nht. Chy theo nh th th mt lm. Lm ngh thut c  hi in in mt cht cng phi l ci in in t chnh trong con  ngi mnh, khng phi bt trc ci in ca ngi khc. Nu ch  thy hnh nh ca ti gi cm th ti cm thy rt vui v ti bit l  ph n ai cng mun mnh quyn r v hp dn trong mt ngi i din.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Tuy nhin, ngi hm  m vn thch mt hnh nh Hong Thy Linh hn nhin, tr trung ch khng  thch Hong Thy Linh gi cm. Linh ngh sao?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: left;"&gt;- Ti cng thch s hn nhin v tr trung.  Nhng n mt lc no  bn nh phi chp nhn mt iu: Bn khng th  c hn nhin mi v bn cng khng th c tr trung mi.  l quy lut  cuc sng ri.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: left;"&gt;Ti khng  th thay i c mc d ti rt mun. Ti nh phi sng ng vi con  ngi v tui tc ca mnh thi. Ai thc s yu qu ti th h s khng  ln tn v iu .&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" width="200"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="oImage" alt="Hong Thy Linh: 'Gi cm l th mnh ca ti!'" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/309/t309350.jpg" align="middle" border="0" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class="pQuestion"&gt;&lt;em&gt;-  Qu kh vn cn  nhng cng  ng yn, d lun cng ci m n cho  s tr li ca Linh trn m nhc v c phim nh. Tr li lng gii tr  vi album u tay, chn hn Linh cng b p lc lm?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: left;"&gt;- Ti p lc ch, ti bit l  nhng g  qua khng th ly li c v th ti thc s lun b p lc  vi cuc sng hin ti. p lc bi ti lun phi n o suy ngh nhng  quyt nh trong mi hnh ng ca mnh. p lc ca s s phm phi sai  lm. p lc bi bn vn phi c nim tin vo nhng ngi mi quen, vo  c hi v cuc sng nhng bn li a nghi hn v bn phi cht lc n.  Cuc sng ca ti cn ang hon thin v ti rt nhiu ln phi kh s  v mu thun vi chnh bn thn mnh&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pQuestion"&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Xem  ra Linh vn rt thn trng mi khi xut hin, t li n ting ni Phi  chng 2 nm sng trong s thn trng by gi n tr thnh thi quen v  Linh phn x rt t nhin? &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;- Ti ngh mnh phi trch nhim hn vi cuc i ca chnh  mnh.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pQuestion"&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Linh ni mt cht v album nh: Linh  mt bao lu  hon thin n, iu g khin Linh hi lng v cha hi  lng nht khi a con ca mnh chun b trnh lng?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: left;"&gt;- Ti mt 6 thng. Ti c lm  xong l li mun lm li. Ti ngh c lm i lm li hoi nh vy kho  n gi cng cha xong c vic g. Ti nh phi hc cch n gin vi  mi th hn v th l.. pht hnh album. Ti thch nhng g ti  lm  nhng vn lun ngh nu lm vol2, mi th s tt hn na..&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" width="200"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="oImage" alt="Hong Thy Linh: 'Gi cm l th mnh ca ti!'" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/309/t309351.jpg" align="middle" border="0" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class="pQuestion"&gt;&lt;em&gt;-  Linh s hu cht ging nh nhng, ph hp vi pop nhng iu m ngi  nghe c th cm nhn c cch y vi nm l hi yu. iu ny c ci  thin nh th no trong album?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;- Ch nn thc hin mt bi phng vn nhc  s Lu Thin Hng v iu ny. (ci)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pQuestion"&gt;&lt;em&gt;-  Nhiu ca s ang nh m vi nhng bn pop ballad nh nhng, lng mn  Linh c e rng nhng ca khc pop ca mnh kh c th vt qua ci bng  ca h?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;- Trong  ngh thut chng c thc o no chnh xc c. Tt c l cm xc ca  chnh chng ta. V ai lm tt vic ca mnh th cng s c mt v tr  ring.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pQuestion"&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Thc ra, Linh cng  ngh ti 2  trng hp: thnh cng hay tht bi ca album ch? &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;- Ti khng bit nh ngha  ca ch v ci gi l thnh cng s nh th no. Nhng vi ti, ti   vt qua nhng kh khn tng xy ra trong suy ngh v t duy ca mnh   c ngy hm nay. iu  c ngha ti  thnh cng.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pQuestion"&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Khng tham gia ngh thut mt thi gian, li u  t cho album kh chn chu, hi tht Linh c gp kh khn v ti chnh  khng?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: left;"&gt;- Vic thc  hin mt album khng c g qu to tt so vi kh nng kinh t ca ti.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" width="200"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="oImage" alt="Hong Thy Linh: 'Gi cm l th mnh ca ti!'" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/309/t309352.jpg" align="middle" border="0" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class="pQuestion"&gt;&lt;em&gt;-  K nim ng nh nht ca Linh khi thc hin album l g?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;- Ti ngh  l nhng ln  thuyt phc ngi khc tin mnh.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pQuestion"&gt;&lt;em&gt;- m nhc  v in nh  ci no l hng i chnh ca Linh?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;- Ti thy mnh ph hp vi  c hai lnh vc. Nhng hin ti ti ang chn m nhc.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pQuestion"&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Linh tng chia s rng: Linh l ngi gia  trng, c on v kh tnh. C th hiu s gia trng  ca Linh nh  no y?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: left;"&gt;- Ti l  ngi cng bng trong tt c mi chuyn. Hoc ch cng c th hiu mt  cch khc,  l trong tt c mi trng hp, ti lun yu cu phi c  i x mt cch cng bng.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pQuestion"&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Ai cng cn  lm mt ngi n ng  s chia, mt b vai  da Linh mun ngi n  ng ca mnh s nh no?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;- Ch c th hi cu khc c khng? Ti by t quan im v  nhng cu hi tng t nh th ny cng kh nhiu ln ri.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" width="200"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="oImage" alt="Hong Thy Linh: 'Gi cm l th mnh ca ti!'" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/309/t309353.jpg" align="middle" border="0" width="248" height="372" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="oImage" alt="Hong Thy Linh: 'Gi cm l th mnh ca ti!'" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/309/t309354.jpg" align="middle" border="0" width="248" height="372" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class="pQuestion"&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Xinh p  thng minh v c ti, Linh c ngh  mnh c sinh ra hon ho v ngoi hnh? Nu c c, Linh mun mnh  s nh no? &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;- Ti  l ngi rt thch c khen ngi cho nn ch thc s khin ti rt  vui... Nhng ti  thc t  bit mnh khng phi ngi hon ho. V  khng vin vng n mc c mnh l &lt;em&gt;Thin Thn&lt;/em&gt;. Ti ch cn l  Hong Thy Linh nh by gi.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pAuthor"&gt;H Thanh&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-3167051710188276006?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/3167051710188276006'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/3167051710188276006'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2010/03/hoang-thuy-linh-cu-hon-nhien-mai-uoc.html' title='Hong Thy Linh: &amp;#39;Khng th c hn nhin mi c&amp;#39;'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-8677535544751748234</id><published>2010-03-24T04:59:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:43.675-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><title type='text'>Nhng mi tc ngn quyn r nht ca sao Vit (P1)</title><content type='html'>Tro lu tc ngn bt u nhen nhm t nm 2008 v n r trn th gii  sut nm 2009, d on y c coi l xu hng tc chnh trong nm nay  ti Vit Nam. Khc vi nm trc, khi hng lot cc bn tr pht "st  vi kiu tc ngn ca Vic, nm nay kiu tc hot nht c nhiu nt tng  ng vi tc Vic nhng di chm vai. To kiu cho tc ngn nm nay ph  bin nht thng l p, sy phng to s bng bnh t nhin hoc to  xon sng nh.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;1. Tng Thanh H&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Mt  trong nhng s xut hin c gy n tng nht phi k n Tng Thanh  H vi kiu tc n gin v l mt trong &lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;Bng dng mun khc &lt;/span&gt;v &lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;p tng centimet.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/15/07/ha4.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/15/07/ha4.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;table style="text-align: left; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" id="table1" border="0" cellspacing="1" Ngi mu  Vn Anh&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ngi mu, din vin Vn Anh lun xut hin tr  trung v xinh p, t ai ngh rng c  kt hn t lu v c mt cuc  sng m m hnh phc. C l s t trong s nhng chn di t tai ting  v c kh nng ngoi ng tt vi cc th ting: Anh, Php v Trung Quc.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/46/200330tocngansaovietP110.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/46/200330tocngansaovietP110.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;  &lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;table style="text-align: left; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" id="table4" border="0" cellspacing="1" width="37%"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/46/200330tocngansaovietP111.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/46/200330tocngansaovietP111.jpg" border="0" width="250" height="333" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/46/200330tocngansaovietP112.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/46/200330tocngansaovietP112.jpg" border="0" width="250" height="333" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;5 -7. B  ba Diva M Linh- Thanh Lam- H Trn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;M Linh&lt;/span&gt;  thnh cng khi xy dng  hnh nh &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Tc ngn, mt b cu rt  hin &lt;/span&gt;v n  tr thnh thng hiu vi c cho n thi im  ny. M Linh cng rt chu kh u t v thit k cc kiu khc cho  mi tc c tnh ca mnh.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;table style="text-align: left; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" id="table5" border="0" cellspacing="1" width="37%"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/15/09/linhaTTVH.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/15/09/linhaTTVH.jpg" border="0" width="247" height="371" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/15/09/db5mylinh18.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/15/09/db5mylinh18.jpg" border="0" width="255" height="371" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/46/200330tocngansaovietP114.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/46/200330tocngansaovietP114.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table style="text-align: left; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" id="table6" border="0" cellspacing="1" width="37%"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/15/09/1.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/15/09/1.jpg" border="0" width="247" height="347" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/15/09/496ea5b4hn.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/15/09/496ea5b4hn.jpg" border="0" width="260" height="346" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;M Linh  bit cn bng cuc sng v s nghip. Hin ti, c hi lng vi&lt;br /&gt; cuc  sng ca mnh. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Thanh  Lam&lt;/span&gt; nu so vi nhng diva cn li,  c th hin s bay bng, t  do tuyt i v t n nh nht. Thanh Lam s hu mt v p mn mi v  rt n b vi i mt a tnh. Mi tc ngn khin c xut hin tr  trung v mi m hn.&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/47/200330tocngansaovietP118.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/47/200330tocngansaovietP118.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;table style="text-align: left; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" id="table7" border="0" cellspacing="1" width="37%"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p align="center"&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/15/09/4.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/15/09/4.jpg" border="0" width="320" height="240" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p align="center"&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/15/09/65123298small136568.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/15/09/65123298small136568.jpg" border="0" width="180" height="239" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center; font-style: italic;"&gt;  Thanh Lam s hu v  p rt n b&lt;br /&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;H Trn &lt;/span&gt;vi  mi tc ngn c tnh  th hin ng tnh cch phng khong v rt  phiu ca c. Sau khi kt hn, s xut hin v sn phm ngh thut ca  H Trn xut hin khng nhiu ti Vit Nam nhng thng hiu H Trn vn   mnh  lu su vo tm nh 19- 21: Khn gi lun mong ngng n  nhng sn phm m nhc tip theo ca H Trn.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/47/200330tocngansaovietP119.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/47/200330tocngansaovietP119.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/47/200330tocngansaovietP120.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/47/200330tocngansaovietP120.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/47/200330tocngansaovietP121.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/47/200330tocngansaovietP121.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;8. Thu Minh&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Thu  Minh mang v p sexy ngay c t v b ngoi, thn thi v trong cch  ht. T u nm ti gi, c kh im lng v hu nh khng xut hin nhiu  trn bo ch.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/48/200330tocngansaovietP122.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/48/200330tocngansaovietP122.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/48/200330tocngansaovietP123.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/48/200330tocngansaovietP123.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/48/200330tocngansaovietP124.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/48/200330tocngansaovietP124.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center; font-style: italic;"&gt; Thu Minh thot khi gii n mc phn cm nm2009&lt;br /&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;9. Ngc Oanh&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; hu Ngc Oanh  hng ti hnh nh ngi ph n mang v p quyn r v sc so.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;C  lun c nh ga cao trong kh nng ng x, x l tnh hung nh  nhng v thng minh&lt;br /&gt; Tho Trang Idol&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Tha Trang  t xy dng mt v p l gip c khc bit v ni bt trong rt nhiu  nhng m n ca V-biz. Tho Trang mang v p mnh khe v nng ng,  iu ny c c c th xut pht t nhng kh khn, vt v trong cuc  sng lc nin thiu c  tng tri qua.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/48/200330tocngansaovietP128.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/48/200330tocngansaovietP128.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/48/200330tocngansaovietP129.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/48/200330tocngansaovietP129.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/49/200330tocngansaovietP130.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/03/22/11/49/200330tocngansaovietP130.jpg" border="0" width="500" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center; font-style: italic;"&gt;  Tho Trang v thng hiu p l&lt;br /&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: right;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;Phng Thy (Tng hp)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-8677535544751748234?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/8677535544751748234'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/8677535544751748234'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2010/03/nhung-mai-toc-ngan-quyen-ru-nhat-cua.html' title='Nhng mi tc ngn quyn r nht ca sao Vit (P1)'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-761137204701622110</id><published>2010-03-23T00:50:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:43.733-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hot Girl - Scandal'/><title type='text'>Hong Thy Linh ht mnh cho album u tay</title><content type='html'>&lt;p class="Lead"&gt;Din vin "Nht k Vng Anh" khoe v o, li th hnh  th v phong cch c tnh trong hu trng clip "Nhp p gic m" -  im nhn trong sn phm m nhc sp trnh lng cui thng 3 ca c.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2010/03/3BA190D2/" class="Lead"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; Quanh i qun li cng ch c mt  l do nhm chn: mt in thoi, mt laptop, mt my nh&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;By gi, khi c nhng ci  tt git gn, cu khch nh vy, c ngi ci khy b qua, c ngi  khng ht hong na nhng v ci bn nng t m th c tch vo xem  nh th no, cng c ngi bu mi cho rng li to scandal  hay  chiu bi ny c ri Mt, hai ln cn cc tc dng, ln th ba l b  phn tc dng ri.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Khng  cn hiu qu bi chiu thc b tung nh nng do mt  dng c nhn  na, cc "x ta" Vit c thm nhiu chiu gy s ch  khc, u nht  thit phi khoe thn. Cng im li xem nhng c gi lm chiu trong  lng gii tr Vit  hm nng tn tui ca mnh nh th no:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pSubTitle"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. L hng kiu khc&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" width="200"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td colspan="2"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/306/t306918.jpg" class="oImage" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" alt="Nhng 'c nng  lm chiu' trong showbiz Vit" align="middle" border="0" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="text-align: right;"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/306/t306919.jpg" class="oImage" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" alt="Nhng 'c nng lm chiu'  trong showbiz Vit" align="middle" border="0" width="150" height="226" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/306/t306920.jpg" class="oImage" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" alt="Nhng 'c nng lm chiu'  trong showbiz Vit" align="middle" border="0" width="339" height="226" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Xt v kha cnh ngh ngi mu th tut dy vy hon ton c  th l gii c rng  ch l mt tai nn khng ng c, do mt cht  s sut ca ch nhn. Sau mt thi gian im hi lng ting, ngi mu,  din vin &lt;a href="http://www.zing.vn/news/dep/trang-nhung-nuc-no-vi-lo-anh-nong/a75182.html"&gt;Trang  Nhung&lt;/a&gt; nhanh chng nng tr li khi mt ngy p tri tm hnh c b  tut dy vy v l nguyn mt bn g bng o trn mng.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Tt nhin, sau tai nn tri  ging ny Trang Nhung ln bo m m ch  gii thch i gii thch li  v chuyn ny, rng  ch l mt tai nn ngh nghip ch khng phi l  mt kch bn c sn C cng nhiu ln tuyn b s khng tr li v tai  nn tut dy vy ca mnh nhng cha thy bi no l cui cng c.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Thc ra khi xem bc nh ca  Trang Nhung, ngi xem c cm gic chic hnh c chp trong trng thi  bnh tnh ch khng phi chp ly c hi na. Mt iu rt l, khi dy  vy b tut, theo bn nng ngay lp tc nhn vt s phi ly tay che i  khi cha kp ko li dy, s rt kh  paparazzi c mt bc nh hon  chnh nh th c.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Tt  nhin, Trang Nhung vn c nng tr li, ph kn trn mng vi nhng b  nh gi cm cng chia s v vai din mi ca mnh trong &lt;em&gt;Anh em nh  bc s&lt;/em&gt; phin bn Vit. V khng t ngi cho rng, Trang Nhung ang  PR cho b phim m c m nhn vai chnh ny.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. &lt;a href="http://www.zing.vn/news/nhac-viet-nam/cuu-thanh-vien-nhom-doremi-bi-chem/a73256.html"&gt;Ngc  Hin&lt;/a&gt; ni hn vi nickname &lt;a href="http://www.zing.vn/news/phim-viet-nam/nguoi-dep-bi-chem-lieu-voi-canh-nong/a77886.html"&gt;ngi  p b chm&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" width="200"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/306/t306994.jpg" class="oImage" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" alt="Nhng 'c nng lm chiu'  trong showbiz Vit" align="middle" border="0" width="147" height="220" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/306/t306995.jpg" class="oImage" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" alt="Nhng 'c nng lm chiu'  trong showbiz Vit" align="middle" border="0" width="331" height="220" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td colspan="2" style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/306/t306996.jpg" class="oImage" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" alt="Nhng 'c nng lm chiu'  trong showbiz Vit" align="middle" border="0" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Scandal l ngi th 3 lm  rn nt chuyn tnh p ca Lu Hng Giang v H Hoi Anh khng  nng   c gi xinh p gc H thnh ni ting  Si Gn nm nao. ng l  khng c la lm sao c khi nhng vic H Hoi Anh ln bo chi phng  khng bit thnh vin oremi l ai khin Ngc Hin qu.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: left;"&gt;Phi n tai nn chm nhm cui  nm ngoi, khi m cng an phi vo cuc iu tra hung th th s vic  mi tr nn nghim trng, tai nn ca Ngc Hin c quan tm ng o,  c nhn c nhiu s s chia hn.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Khi vn cn nm trn ging bnh v tng  chng nh con ng ngh thut ca Hin m mt th khng t ngi t cm  thng  ra nhng cu hi tri ngc khi "ngi p b chm" ln lt  pht hnh album v gii thiu b phim mi vi nhng cnh qu nng bng.  Gn y, Ngc Hin  tr li vi nhng hnh nh gi cm, ti tr. Vy  nn, nu ni c ni ting nh b chm nhm cng khng sai!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Thy Tin v nhng  &lt;a href="http://www.zing.vn/news/nhac-viet-nam/thuy-tien-toi-la-nguoi-tao-ra-trao-luu/a71642.html"&gt;tuyn  ngn gy sc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" width="200"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/306/t306980.jpg" class="oImage" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" alt="Nhng 'c nng lm chiu'  trong showbiz Vit" align="middle" border="0" width="225" height="300" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/306/t306981.jpg" class="oImage" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" alt="Nhng 'c nng lm chiu'  trong showbiz Vit" align="middle" border="0" width="204" height="300" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class="pBody"&gt;u tin phi nhc  n Thy Tin  c ca s c bit nhiu hn v scandal so vi ging  ht.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody"&gt;c bit n qua ca khc &lt;em&gt;Gic m tuyt  trng&lt;/em&gt; nhng tn tui ca Thy Tin cng nh con ng m nhc ca  c thc s i ln nh diu gp gi sau scandal l nh nng. D khng c  sn phm m nhc mi nhng Thy Tin xut hin dy c v tr thnh   ti hot k t khi snh i vi tin o L Cng Vinh. y qu l s kt  hp hon ho a y tn tui khng nhng ca Thy Tin m c L Cng  Vinh na. Mt nm tri, khng th m xu nhng bi bo vit v cp i  ny. Cui cng l b nh chp vi style gi cm, sexy khi c 2 mc c  qun jean ng m nhau nhng li khng mang n cho ngi xem cm nhn  v p sexy ca b nh. Ngc li, sau b nh  nhiu ngi ng ngng  v i ngi cho cp i ny. Thm ch, mt c gi cn vit ring mt bi  &lt;em&gt;Thy Tin  Cng Vinh tip th tnh yu kiu r tin&lt;/em&gt; hay nhng  ch  trn mng x hi dng &lt;em&gt;Chng ti ght Thy Tin  Cng Vinh&lt;/em&gt;   ch trch. Cc fan hm m ti dn bng ca Cng Vinh cng tr nn  hoang mang v s thay i ca thn tng.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody"&gt;Khng  ch kiu trang im khc ngi, m chnh cch pht ngn gy shock cng  lm cho Thy Tin khng c lng cng chng. Ban u l nhng li "chia  s" nh: &lt;em&gt;Ti tng yu 7 ngi&lt;/em&gt;, "&lt;em&gt;Nhiu ngi hay nhm ln  gi cm vi h hang nn ti khng mun dng t gi cm  trnh b hiu  nhm. u im ca ti l dng p, chn p nn ti mc nhng trang  phc khoe c i chn di thng ca mnh. Ti khng thch khoe ngc  nh mt s ngi khc", &lt;/em&gt;"&lt;em&gt;Ti v Cng Vinh khng cn ni ting  na&lt;/em&gt;... Ri ti &lt;em&gt;Ti  c mt vai din di trong b phim  truyn hnh "Ngi nh hnh phc" gy c s ch  vi t s rating cao&lt;/em&gt;,  trong khi , vai din ca Thy Tin b nh gi qu t. Thm ch c  ngi cn khng nh  l chic o qu rng so vi nng lc din xut  ca c.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Gn y nht,  c ca s ca&lt;em&gt; Gic m tuyt trng &lt;/em&gt;li tuyn b: &lt;em&gt;Ti s rt  lui khi lng gii tr vo 2 -3 nm ti,  trnh th phi v  tp  trung cho nhng k hoch kinh doanh ring ca mnh&lt;/em&gt;. Vi nhng cu  ni nh th ny, khng bit l c tnh hay v tnh nhng Thy Tin khin  nhiu ngi kh chubi h cho rng c t tin thi qu, khng bit  ngi bit ta.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4.  nh nng v vit v  ti sex&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" width="200"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/306/t306986.jpg" class="oImage" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" alt="Nhng 'c nng lm chiu'  trong showbiz Vit" align="middle" border="0" width="209" height="315" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/306/t306987.jpg" class="oImage" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" alt="Nhng 'c nng lm chiu'  trong showbiz Vit" align="middle" border="0" width="189" height="320" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Cha ht sc v b nh nng ca &lt;a target="_blank" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); ca c nng b ngng xut bn do sau khi tung ln mng nhng  trang hot nht, ngay lp tc cun sch nhn c v s phn hi tri  chiu. Nhiu ngi bc xc cho rng n chng khc nhng g cun tiu  thuyt 3 xu Din bin ca s kin ny vn ang khin khn gi t m.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. Hong ip chi tri&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" width="200"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td colspan="2"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/307/t307328.jpg" class="oImage" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" alt="Nhng 'c nng  lm chiu' trong showbiz Vit" align="middle" border="0" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="text-align: right;"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/307/t307287.jpg" class="oImage" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" alt="Nhng 'c nng lm chiu'  trong showbiz Vit" align="middle" border="0" width="248" height="164" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/307/t307288.jpg" class="oImage" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" alt="Nhng 'c nng lm chiu'  trong showbiz Vit" align="middle" border="0" width="248" height="164" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Nu ai quan tm hn cng nhn ra &lt;em&gt;N hong sc p quc t&lt;/em&gt;  2009 ngy cng ni lon hn k t pht ng quang. Trc  thm ch  nhiu ngi cn chng bit c l ai, d thnh tch cao nht ca Hong  ip l lt Top 10 Hoa hu Vit Nam.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Thng thng, cc Hoa hu khi ng quang  thng m thm v thn trng hn trong li n ting ni nhng vi Hong  ip th c khc. C khng ngi cng khai chuyn tnh cm, sn sng  khoe bn trai trn mt bo d ngi yu c khng phi l mt anh chng  p trai, quyn r Bn cnh , c vn gi cch ni nng thng thng,  chng n h ai.  mi l Hong ip!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Tuy nhin, iu lm ngi hm m thy phn  cm nht chnh l vic thi gian gn y, &lt;em&gt;N hong sc p quc t&lt;/em&gt;  i din cng vi &lt;a href="http://www.zing.vn/news/dep/hoang-diep-mang-26-ve-si-khi-di-dien/a79440.html"&gt;mt  i qun v s rt honh trng&lt;/a&gt;. An ton l tt nhng  vic lm m  th ny s phn tc dng, n khin d lun c nhng suy  ngh tri chiu gy hiu lm v chnh bn thn&lt;em&gt; N hong sc p&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Nhng ngi sao nh m nht  th gii, c hng trm fan cung v paparazzi vy quanh nh Angelina  Jolie, Britney Spears, Victoria Beckham, Paris Hilton, Miley Cyrus cng  khng trnh khi nhng rc ri t ngi hm m nhng cha bao gi m   nh Hong ip ca Vit Nam!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pAuthor"&gt;H Thanh&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-8121468850717940612?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/8121468850717940612'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/8121468850717940612'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2010/03/nhung-nang-lam-chieu-trong-showbiz-viet.html' title='Nhng &amp;#39;c nng lm chiu&amp;#39;
