C v nh Nhung ang ngi ngay cnh in thoi  ch i   &lt;div class="detail_content"&gt;  &lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Cuc in thoi ca ti vi &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Trang Nhung&lt;/span&gt; ngt qung lin tc bi c thng im lng v khc nc n. Qu thc, khi ni chuyn vi c, ti cng phi ngp ngng rt nhiu v nhng cu hi y c th khin c hong lon&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/01/15/15/13/small41090.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/01/15/15/13/small41090.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Ngi mu, din vin Trang Nhung&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;Trn mt s din n  xut hin nhng bc nh kh nhy cm ca mt nhn vt c gng mt ging Trang Nhung? Ch bit tin ny cha?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;(Im lng)  Ti  bit (xt xt)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/01/15/15/35/trang-nhung4psd.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/01/15/15/35/trang-nhung4psd.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Bc hnh "khng khip" theo li Trang Nhung&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;Khi c bo tin ny, ch  ngh g?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ti cng bit do c mt ngi bn bo cho. Lc , ti  sng st, khng hiu c chuyn g xy ra. Lc u, ti trch anh y v ngh rng anh y a qu ng&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;y c v l mt bc hnh c chp bng my v gc chp kh tt nn chc khng phi l bc nh  chp trm, Trang Nhung c th gii thch r hn v s c ny?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ti thc s khng gii thch c.  l mt  bui chp hnh thi trang( im lng)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;C phi khi chp hnh thi trang, ngi mu thng gp phi nhng s c tng t nh vy v bt cn? &lt;/span&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Nhng ngi  tng lm vic vi ti u bit rt r ti l ngi th no. Ti rt cn thn trong chuyn thay qun o, nht l chp hnh ngoi tri. Thc ra, s c ny l do qu vi v, khi ti chp hnh cho mt t bo. Bui chp hnh din ra vo bui tra v bo ch xin php cng vin n khong 12h tra nn chng ti u rt vi Thc s, ti khng bit phi ni g, c ni g chc mi ngi cng s ch ni l ti bin minh cho mnh. Ti khng trch ai, ch l do s c khng may&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;S c ny din ra kh trng hp khi ch ang m nhn vai n chnh trong b phim c quan tm "Anh em nh bc s". V vy, nu nhiu ngi  xo v chuyn ny v cho rng, vic tung bc nh ln mng l hnh ng c ch , Trang Nhung s gii thch ra sao?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ti khng di g em thn th mnh ra  PR cho ci tn m khng phi nhiu ngi cha bit. Nu ai hiu ti, chi thn vi ti s hiu ti nh th no. Ti cm thy rt bun v xu h khi nhn c bc hnh . Khi bn ti bo cho ti tin ny, ti ang bn vic v gn nh hong lon, khng th tp trung vo iu g. Thc ra lc , ti ch ngh mc  khng n th ny, ti tht s khng bit c bc hnh &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ch c bit v sao bc hnh li c pht tn ln mng?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ti  khc rt nhiu v ni chuyn vi makeup ca mnh l anh Phc Li. V cng vic do ny kh bn rn nn ti khng nh chnh xc l bc nh ny c chp lc no. Nhng c ti v anh Li u nh lng mng l bc hnh chp hm  cch y gn 2 thng ri. Ti khng hiu ti sao n by gi li c nhng bc hnh  v li ngay vo thi im ti k hp ng vi Anh em nh bc s nn ti gn nh b hiu lm. Ti khng c g  gii thch c, ch mong mi ngi hiu cho mnh.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;Trc y, Trang Nhung  tng ni "Hy qun scandal i nh". Cu ni  gi vn l tn ch cho s nghip ngh thut ca ch ch?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ti khng c tnh to scandal (khc nc n). S c xy ra khin ti v cng au kh. Con ng ngh thut ca ti khng tri hoa hng. Ti  gp rt nhiu kh khn nhng cha c iu g kinh khng nh th ny. Gi th ti  hiu cu ni khng ai bit c ch ng. iu g xy ra vi bn, bn khng th bit trc c. Ngy mai, ngy kia, ngy sau na ti thy s&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ti  gi gn hnh nh din vin, ngi mu ca mnh trong sut 4 nm qua khng mt iu ting g. Chng l, ti li p  tt c ch bng mt hnh nh m theo ti tht ng s ny sao? Bn b  an i ti rt nhiu nhng ti khng chc trong nhng ngy ti mnh s th no. Ti mong khn gi hy dnh cho ti mt lng tin  ti tip tc c gng.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/01/15/15/15/0910262trangnhung3.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2010/01/15/15/15/0910262trangnhung3.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Trang Nhung mong mi ngi hy dnh cho c  mt nim tin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;Sau khi hay tin v bc hnh khng hay ny c a ln mng, tinh thn ca Trang Nhung th no?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Bc hnh a ln mng khng lu, bn b  bo tin cho ti. Lc , ngi ta an i ti l chc s khng nhiu ngi bit u nhng ti  rt hong lon. Ti bit chuyn ny s tr nn m  v ti khng bit ai l ngi pht tn bc anh. V ng nh nhng g ti ngh, gi th  c qu nhiu ngi bit. Ti nhn thy tm hnh ng s y lan truyn rng ri m bt lc (khc ln). Ti  ngh ti  cch  i din vi iu ny nhng ti khng bit lm g c.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;Sau s c khng mong mun ni, ch mun ni vi khn gi ca mnh iu g?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ti ch mong khn gi - nhng ngi  yu thch v bit ti hy gip ti qun i chuyn ny v ti cng mun xin li ti mi ngi v s c ri ro ny ca ti.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ch nhn nh th no v scandal l hng  c nhiu n ngh s s dng trong thi gian qua v rt thnh cng?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Tu vo nhng g h  lm  thy  l s c ri ro hay do h c tnh nhng Nhung ngh rng khng ai di g li a nhng hnh nh khng tt v mnh hay l ph trng thn th  to scandal. Ti mong mi ngi hy hiu, vic ny i vi ti ch l s c. V ti xin php s khng tr li bt c cu hi no v chuyn ny na&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: right;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;Tng Chi(2sao)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-8780139290658016721?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/8780139290658016721'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/8780139290658016721'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2010/01/trang-nhung-bat-khoc-vi-lo-anh-nong.html' title='Trang Nhung bt khc v l nh nng'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-3656386841817950082</id><published>2010-01-10T22:51:00.000-08:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:45.360-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hot Girl - Scandal'/><title type='text'>Ngi tnh cht, Tila Nguyn mang bu!?</title><content type='html'>&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Cha hon hn v ci cht ca ngi tnh ng tnh, Tila Nguyn li gy n o d lun vi nhng tit l p m trn Twitter rng c ang mang trong ngi mt a tr. Ti khng c nhiu thi gian  chm sc a tr ca ring mnh  cha bao gi ti cm thy ti  sn sng  mang bu nhng khng c mt thc t rng lc ny ti ang mang trong mnh mt a tr.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Tila Nguyn tr nn ni ting t mt mng x hi MySpace. Di y l mt s tn tui  em chung i nh x ngi kh thnh cng:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;1. Thi H:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;S hu mt thn hnh cc chun 90-61-92, Thi H hin ang l ngi mu t show nht hin nay. Vi gii  hu 1 Hoa hu H Ni, Phong cch Siu mu Vit Nam 2009, Thi H  c chn l gng mt i din cho Vit Nam ti cuc thi &lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;N hong du lch Quc t&lt;/span&gt; ti Thnh ph Trnh Chu, tnh H Nam, &lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;Trung Quc&lt;/span&gt;. Tuy khng ginh c gii thng ti cuc thi ny nhng Thi H  nhn c s nh gi cao bi phong cch lm vic chuyn nghip.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/08/124521445Thaiha217015%20%282%29.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/08/124521445Thaiha217015%20%282%29.jpg" width="500" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/08/1240191524ThaiHa02%20%282%29.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/08/1240191524ThaiHa02%20%282%29.jpg" width="500" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;5. Phng Mai:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Tuy cha c gii thng trong nc cho ring mnh, nhng ti cuc thi Siu mu Chu  c t chc ti Nam Ninh, Qung Ty, Trung Quc, Phng Mai  xut sc lt vo top 10. Hin nay, c ang l ngi mu c quyn ca cng ty Venus Min Bc. Trong cuc thi ny, cng ty Venus Min Bc cn c thm 2 i din  l ngi mu Ngc Oanh, top 10 HHVN 2008 Nguyn Hng Nhung nhng ch c Phng Mai l ngi c c thnh tch trong cuc thi. Nm nay c 20 tui.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/09/30PhuongMai.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/09/30PhuongMai.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;6. Trn Th Qunh:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Hoa hu th thao 2007 Trn Th Qunh l gng mt i din cho Vit Nam ti cuc thi Hoa hu Quc t 2009 din ra t ngy 13- 28/11/2009 ti Trung Quc. Do thiu kinh nghim trn sn din cng nh trc ng knh Trn Th Qunh  khng lt vo Top 15 ca cuc thi.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/09/tranthiquyhh301.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/09/tranthiquyhh301.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;7. Hng Giang:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;u im ca Hng Giang  chnh l n ci thn thin. Trong nm 2009, Hng Giang  ginh gii  hu cuc thi Hoa hu Vit Nam ton cu 2009. Ti cuc thi ny, c cn  ginh thm 2 gii ph  l Hoa hu nh v Hoa hu mc o di p nht. Hng Giang l i din ca Vit Nam trong cuc thi Hoa hu th gii 2009. Ti cuc thi ny, Hng Giang lt vo top 16 v ginh thm 1 gii ph  hu 1 Miss Model.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/09/huonggian173.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/09/huonggian173.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;8. Hong Th Yn:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Ti cuc thi Hoa hu qu b 2009 c t chc ti tnh &lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;B Ra  Vng Tu, Vit Nam&lt;/span&gt;, gii nht thuc v ngi p &lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;Nga - Victoriya Radochinskaya&lt;/span&gt;. Hoa hu M Andrea Roberston ot gii  hu 1. Hoa hu Vit Nam  ginh gii  hu 2 -  l Hong Th Yn n t thnh ph H Ch Minh. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/10/hoangthiyen.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/10/hoangthiyen.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;9. Chung Thc Quyn&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;i din ca Vit Nam ti cuc thi Hoa hu Siu quc gia  c mt trong top 15 ca cuc thi c t chc ti Plock, Ba Lan. Ti cuc thi ny, Chung Thc Quyn cn ot 2 gii ph l &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Trang phc dn tc p nht&lt;/span&gt; v &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Miss Internet&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/10/160809chungthucquyen5.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/10/160809chungthucquyen5.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/10/images106919thucquen1.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/10/images106919thucquen1.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;10. Vnh Thu&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Trong cuc thi&lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt; Mister International 2009&lt;/span&gt; c t chc ti &lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;i Loan&lt;/span&gt;, gii bc Siu mu Vit Nam 2009  Vnh Thu  dng li ti v tr Top 15 v gii gng mt n nh. Ti cuc thi ny, gii nht Mister International 2008 Tin on cng c mt ti v tr Ban Gim kho.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/11/091229saoViet46.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/30/15/11/091229saoViet46.jpg" width="500" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Cng trong nm nay, 2 chn di Vit l&lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt; Trng Th May &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;v&lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt; Hunh Thanh Tuyn&lt;/span&gt;  l hn ti 2 cuc thi ln  l Miss Bikini International v Miss Earth. Nm 2009  khp li, Hi vng nm 2010 s m ra mt trang mi vi nhng thnh tch xut sc ca sc p Vit trn u trng sc p quc t.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;Hng Unique &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;(Tng hp)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-9205917550701485352?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/9205917550701485352'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/9205917550701485352'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/12/nhan-sac-viet-1-nam-va-nhung-dau.html' title='Nhan sc Vit - 1 nm v nhng du n...'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-3987846605138133424</id><published>2009-12-27T22:31:00.000-08:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:45.889-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hoa Hu - Siu Mu'/><title type='text'>Top 10 gng mt VNG trong lng mu Vit 2009!</title><content type='html'>&lt;h2 style="font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="head-noidung"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:78%;"&gt;Bng xp hng c thc hin da trn qu trnh tng hp cc  kin, nhn nh ca nhiu chuyn gia uy tn trong lng thi trang Vit Nam. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Thanh Hng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Lun gi v tr vedtte trong cc show trnh din thi trang t vi nm tr li y, c gi s hu i chn di nht lng mu Vit tip tc c mt nm 2009 thnh cng khi xut hin lin tc trn ba cc n phm thi trang ln, l khch vip trong nhiu s kin vn ha quan trng v nhn c nhng khon catxe cc k u i nu c mi si bc trn sn catwalk.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Top 10 gng mt VNG trong lng mu Vit 2009! Kh nng din xut tt  gip Thanh Hng mang v mt s gii thng in nh quan trng. u nm sau, b phim bom tn &lt;em&gt;Nhng n hn rc r&lt;/em&gt; ca ma Tt 2010 do Thanh Hng th vai chnh cng ang ha hn mang li nhiu bt ng th v.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. V Thu Phng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;L lp ngi mu k cn Thanh Hng, sung sc trong nm 2008 khi nhn c gii thng ngi mu xut sc nht, nm 2009 cng l mt nm ng nh ca V Thu Phng khi c lun c nhc n nh mt ngi mu hng u bi s chm ch, mit mi v phong cch lm vic chuyn nghip, cu tin.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Top 10 gng mt VNG trong lng mu Vit 2009! V Hong Yn&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;V tr th 3 phi k n l chn di s hu khun mt ty v chiu cao l tng ny. V Hong Yn l ci tn c bo ch quan tm nhiu trong 2 nm tr li y.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Top 10 gng mt VNG trong lng mu Vit 2009! Tuy khng gt hi c thnh cng nh mong i, nhng s ng h ca khn gi trong sut qu trnh Yn d thi cng cng c hn v tr l mt trong nhng ngi mu hng u trong lng cng chng hin nay.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Nguyn Ngc Lan Hng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Nu nh 8 thng trc cha ai bit Lan Hng l ai, th gi y, sau gii  hu 4 ca cuc thi Miss Model of the world, ci tn ny vt chc tr thnh im nng.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Top 10 gng mt VNG trong lng mu Vit 2009! Hng Giang&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Khng gy c n tng khi tham d mt s cuc thi sc p  trong nc trc , nhng Hng Giang li l ci tn c yu mn khi i din cho Vit Nam bn ba  x ngi.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Top 10 gng mt VNG trong lng mu Vit 2009! Khi im bng gii &lt;a href="http://www.24h.com.vn/news/detail/78/234673/Huong-Giang-gianh-ngoi-a-hau-2.24h?news_nextnews=0?news_nextnews=0"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;u&gt; hu 2&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; trong cuc thi Hoa hu Vit Nam ton cu ti M,  cuc thi &lt;a href="http://www.24h.com.vn/cate/event/78/759/Miss-World-2009.24h"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hoa hu Th gii 2009&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; c gi cao 1m80 c Globalbeauties nh gi rt cao ny thc s gy n tng vi ban t chc v ngi hm m khi ginh gii  hu 1 Top Model v l 1 trong 3 i din chu  lt vo Top 16 chung cuc. Tr v nc t cuc thi, Hng Giang nghim nhin tr thnh mt trong nhng ngi mu c quan tm v yu thch nht hin nay.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6. Trng Th May&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Mang trong mnh dng mu Kh"mer nhng  hu Dn tc Trng Th May lun lm ngi i din phi ng ngng trc v p rt Ty v cng rt c tnh ca mnh. Nu khng gp tai nn ri ro th c l c gi c kh cht rt sng ny  to c nhng im nhn ng k ti cuc thi Hoa hu Tri t 2009.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Top 10 &amp;quot;bom tn&amp;quot; trong lng mu Vit 2009!(Phn cui), Thi trang, " src="http://www25.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-27/1261904093-1256870329-images1581119_Tr.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Top 10 &amp;quot;bom tn&amp;quot; trong lng mu Vit 2009!(Phn cui), Thi trang, " style="width: 225px; height: 321px;" src="http://www25.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-27/1261904189-may01.jpg" /&gt; &lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Top 10 &amp;quot;bom tn&amp;quot; trong lng mu Vit 2009!(Phn cui), Thi trang, " style="width: 258px; height: 322px;" src="http://www25.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-27/1261904189-t9-35-.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Thi gian gn y, ci tn Trng Th May lun nhn c s quan tm c bit ca bo ch nh nhng bc i iu luyn trn sn catwalk cng nh s xut hin ni bt ca c  nhng s kin vn ha. Trng Th May xng ng vi v tr th 6 trong Top 10 gng mt VNG trong lng mu Vit 2009.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7. Hunh Thanh Tuyn&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Top 10 &amp;quot;bom tn&amp;quot; trong lng mu Vit 2009!(Phn cui), Thi trang, " src="http://www25.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-27/1261904189-IMG_7722.jpg" width="500" height="333" /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Top 10 &amp;quot;bom tn&amp;quot; trong lng mu Vit 2009!(Phn cui), Thi trang, " src="http://www25.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-27/1261904093-1247112643-Quynh--Thy---Tha.jpg" width="249" height="374" /&gt; &lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Top 10 &amp;quot;bom tn&amp;quot; trong lng mu Vit 2009!(Phn cui), Thi trang, " src="http://www25.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-27/1261904339-tuyen1.jpg" width="249" height="374" /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Khng bt ng theo chng b cuc chi th chc gi Hunh Thanh Tuyn   v tr cao hn na trong bng danh sch nhng ngi mu thnh cng nht nm 2009. Xut hin dy c trn cc tp ch trong mt thi gian di vi nhng hnh nh v cng gi cm v p mt, k c khi mi ngi u hoi nghi v cuc thi Miss Bikini m c c c lm i din ht, nhng vic ng nui tic nht vn l quyt nh kt hn ca c ngi mu c thn hnh ng h ct ny. Tuy nhin, d  tm lui vo hu trng, Hunh Thanh Tuyn vn  li trong lng ngi yu thi trang mt hnh nh p.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;8. Vit'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-5345378477379003041</id><published>2009-12-17T05:17:00.000-08:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:46.298-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><title type='text'>Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009</title><content type='html'>&lt;h2 style="font-weight: small;" class="head-noidung"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:100%;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Olivia Wilde&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;nh bi nhng tn tui nh m Angelina Jolie, Marisa Miller, Jessica Biel, v nhng thin thn ni y Victorias Secret v c bit l c o gi cm nht th gii 2008 Megan Fox, c din vin mang 2 dng mu M v Ireland - Olivia Wilde vi v p hoang di v c bit gi cm  bt ng ginh v tr cao nht trong top 10 m n nng bng nht 2009 do tp ch Maxim bnh chn.&lt;br /&gt;Olivia Wilde bc vo nghip din t nm 2000, ginh c mt s gii thng nh N din vin xut sc nht (2006),  c cho gii thng Ngi sao amh ln (2009) ti Vail Film Festival.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009, Thi trang, " src="http://www26.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-17/1261051117-olivia-wilde_l4.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;L do Olivia c bnh chn v ginh c chin thng bt ng ny c l phn ln nh b nh bom tn c ng ti trn tp ch ny hi thng 7. Ngi ng bun nht c l l Megan Fox v nhng fan hm m ca c o ny. Tuy nhin nhng con s  ni ln tt c.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009, Thi trang, " src="http://www26.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-17/1261051117-olivia-wilde_l1.jpg" width="249" height="255" /&gt; &lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009, Thi trang, " style="width: 228px; height: 252px;" src="http://www26.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-17/1261051117-olivia-wilde-topless.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Olivia Wilde tn tht l Olivia Jane Cockburn, sinh nm 1984,  kt hn cng chng l Tao Ruspoli (o din, nh sn xut phim, nhip nh gia)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Megan Fox&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Lun xut hin vi hnh nh khiu gi v lp k lc v nhng pht ngn, tin n gy sc, ngi p lng tnh Megan Fox - biu tng sex ca showbiz th gii ngm ngi dnh ngi v th 2 trong bng tng sp rt thu ht ny.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009, Thi trang, " src="http://www26.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-17/1261051411-dc5d637ed5_1246250197-Megan.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Megan Fox&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Ngi p Megan Fox sinh nm 1986 trong mt gia nh ngho ti tiu bang Tennessee nc M. 13 tui Megan bt u s nghip ngi mu v ot gii thng ti cuc thi Ngi mu ti nng ca M. Nm 15 tui c bt u tham gia vo th gii in nh v thn may mn  im, t nm 2007 Megan c nhiu ngi bit n nh vai din chnh trong b phim Transformers (2007) ca o din Michael Bay.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Bar Refaeli &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;ng  v tr th 3 l siu mu Bar Refaeli, ngi tnh mt thi khin ti t Leonardo DiCaprio iu ng. C gi c nhng m tn nhanh duyn dng ny nm nay 24 tui, l siu mu ngi Israel, s hu chiu cao 1m73, s o cc vng 89 - 61  90. a phn mi ngi ch bit rng Bar Refaeli bt u lm ngi mu khi mi 11 tui nhng thc ra c bc vo lng thi trang sm hn rt nhiu. Mi ch 8 thng tui, c nhc nh Refaeli  c xut hin trong mt qung co thng mi ca Israel.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009, Thi trang, " src="http://www26.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-17/1261051496-3-Bar_Refaeli_Hot100_l.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Siu mu Bar Refaeli&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Ngoi nhng n phm thi trang hay cataloge nng bng, gi y ngi hm m cn c th tm thy Bar Refaeli trn knh truyn hnh MTVs House of Style vi vai tr l ngi dn chng trnh yu kiu v xinh p.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Malin Akerman &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009, Thi trang, " src="http://www26.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-17/1261051496-4-malin_ackerman_l.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nm 17 tui, Akerman ot gii siu mu ti Canada&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Sinh nm 1978, Malin Akerman l din vin kim ngi mu Canada gc Thy in. Nm 17 tui, Akerman ot gii siu mu ti Canada. Lm ngi mu c mt thi gian, Akrman quyt nh n Califonia th sc vi phim trng. C  thnh cng trong hng lot vai din trong cc phim The Utopian Society (2003), Harold &amp;amp; Kumar Go to White Castle (2004) v c cng chng bit n nhiu nht qua b phim Silk Spectre.C lun tm nim c gng v khng ngng c gng.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. Mila Kunis&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009, Thi trang, " src="http://www26.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-17/1261051754-Malin.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Mila thch n hn ng gii vi Natalie Portman&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Mila l mt trong nhng siu mu ca Nga thnh cng nht ti Hollywood hin nay. S hu thn hnh mnh mai nh Kate Moss, i mt d di ca sng ng, i chn di thng tp v mt phong cch thi trang kh n tng. C gi sinh nm 1983 ny tng c mt pht ngn kh ngng cung khi th l thch n hn ng tnh ca bn din l Natalie Portman trong b phim Black Swan: &lt;em&gt;"C y tht nng bng v khi hn c y, ti cm thy nh c y l ngi ng tnh 'chnh hiu'. Ti tht s c cm xc v bay bng".&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Mila hn h vi ngi sao  nh mt mnh Macaulay Culkin t nm 2006 v vn ang tip tc trong mi quan h tt p ny.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6. Eliza Dushku&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;29 tui, nhng c o vi nhng ng cong bc la Eliza Dushku vn c coi l mt trong nhng biu tng sexy ca lng in nh M. C tng c v nh vin ngc bit ni khi xut hin cng cc ti t p trai Roberto De Niro v Leonardo DiCaprio trong b phim Thiss boy life (1993).&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009, Thi trang, " src="http://www26.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-17/1261051754-1248880850ElizaDushku1_thum.jpg" width="500" height="368" /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009, Thi trang, " style="width: 209px; height: 359px;" src="http://www26.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-17/1261051754-1248867394-eliza-dushku-02.jpg" /&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009, Thi trang, " style="width: 261px; height: 360px;" src="http://www26.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-17/1261051496-1248867394-eliza-dushku-01.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Biu tng sex ca lng gii tr M&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;ng th 6 trong bng xp hng top 10 m n nng nht 2009 ca tp ch Maxim, Eliza Dushku tng cng hin cho rt nhiu trang tp ch nhng hnh nh v cng gi m.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7. Adriana Lima&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;D va mi sinh con u lng cch y 1 thng (15/11) nhng mt trong nhng thin thn gi cm nht ca hng  lt Victoria's Secret vn gi vng v tr th 7 trong bng xp hng c nhiu ngi mong i ny.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Adriana Lima sinh nm 1981 ti Salvador da Bahia, Brazil nhng mang trong mnh n 4 dng mu: Php, Th Nh K, th dn Chu M v vng Caribbee huyn thoi. C ta sng ngay t khi 13 tui khi ginh v tr th hai trong cuc thi th gii Siu mu Ford, nhng tr thnh thin thn ca Victoria"s Secret mi thc s gip c t n nh cao danh vng (nm 2001). Adriana cng tng tham gia mt vi vai din in nh nhng cha t ti ngng thnh cng nht nh.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009, Thi trang, " src="http://www26.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-17/1261051496-7_Adriana_Lima_Hot100_l.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Thin thn ni y trong 1 show din&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;S ni ting, giu sang vi nhng hp ng tr gi hng triu  la v nhng ba tic linh nh trong th gii ngh s khng lm c qun c mong c t thu nh ca mnh: gip  nhng a tr ng ph. C l v th c  rt nhiu ln tr li qu hng, quyn gp cho nhng nh tr m ci  Brazil v lp mt qu t thin  gip  nhng em nh lang thang, c nh. C l v th trong lng ngi dn Brazil, c gi xinh p ca h ng tht l mt thin thn.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;8. Rihanna&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009, Thi trang, " src="http://www26.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-17/1261051754-RihannaGQNSFW1.jpg" width="500" height="678" /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009, Thi trang, " src="http://www26.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-17/1261051754-RihannaGQNSFW4.jpg" width="249" height="336" /&gt; &lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009, Thi trang, " style="width: 243px; height: 337px;" src="http://www26.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-17/1261051754-RihannaGQNSFW2.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009, Thi trang, " src="http://www26.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-17/1261051754-RihannaGQNSFW3.jpg" width="500" height="437" /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nhng bc nh s ng ti trn n phm GQ M thng 1/2010&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Nhng bc hnh hot ca ngi sao nhc pop Rihanna lun c sn lng. Dnh vo scandal l nh sex, b bn trai hnh hung  nhng s c ny ch khin c nng thm  mu. Chiu cao khim tn, chn th, c tay l, nhng khng h g, c vn ng v tr th 8 trong bng xp hng nhng m n thu ht nhiu n ng nht.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;9. Jordana Brewster&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009, Thi trang, " src="http://www26.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-17/1261051496-1240452556-jordana-brewster.jpg" width="500" height="672" /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;L mt trong nhng ngi sao c trnh  cao nht Hollywood v c lng gii tr (tt nghip i hc Yale nm 2003), ngi p c bit danh liu thuc m trc khi n vi in nh l mt ngi mu Barazil c ting. Ngi p ny nm nay 29 tui.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;10. Jennifer Love Hewitt&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Sinh nm 1979, n din vin kim danh ca Jennifer Love Hewitt  c n 24 nm hot ng trong ngnh ngh thut (t nm ln 5 tui). Ngi p ca phim Garfield ni ting l ngi a tinh, c tng tm s kh n hn v  khng tham gia nhng hot ng v ng phim hay chp nh kha thn nhiu hn trong thi gian t 12 n 28 tui. Jennifer k trn tp ch Health (M): &lt;em&gt;Khi cn tr, ti thy c th mnh p tuyt vi. Ti hy vng cc c gi tr hy mc bikini nhiu hn trong ma h. Hy tn dng c hi ca mnh. ng bao ngh mnh xu.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009, Thi trang, " src="http://www26.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-12-17/1261051496-10-jenniferlovehewit_Hot100.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Thng 6 va qua ngi p ny  bt tay vo vit sch t vn v cc mi quan h vi n ng. Cun sch mang tn The day I shot cupid m t gn nh l cm nang tn tnh n ng, cch yu nhau lng mn, gi quan h sau khi chia tay... Tc phm u tay ca Hewitt d kin s pht hnh vo thng 3.2010. Cn trong thi gian ny, trn khp cc mn nh hay n phm thi trang, c vn xut hin mt cch thu ht nht vi khun ngc cng trn v nhng ng cong y gi cm.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-5345378477379003041?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/5345378477379003041'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/5345378477379003041'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/12/ngam-10-my-nu-nong-nhat-maxim-2009.html' title='Ngm 10 m n nng nht Maxim 2009'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-11782706232469161</id><published>2009-12-16T18:46:00.000-08:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:46.333-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hot Girl - Scandal'/><title type='text'>Thy Top: n ng thi nay qu...thm!</title><content type='html'>Khng cn tr con nh nhnh nhng cng cha thc s nhiu tri nghim trn tnh trng, Thy Top, c gi c nhiu n ng khao kht  nhn thy n ng thi nay su sc hn v cng thm hn thi xa rt nhiu.     &lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;Nhiu ngi cho rng ch chn thi gian ny i du hc bi v ch ang tc ng pht trin con ng ngh thut ti Vit Nam, ch ni g vi h?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;H hon ton sai, hin ti l thi im pht trin tt nht ca ti, cng vic trong lng gii tr v kinh doanh ca ti u ang v cng tt p. Khi quyt nh du hc ngha l ti  phi r b rt rt nhiu c hi trc mt nh m nhc, in nh v c cng vic t chc s kin ca ti ti y. Quyt nh i v cng kh khn v phi nh i qu nhiu th, nhiu ngui cng git mnh khi ti quyt nh nh vy. Tnh ti bng lm,  quyt l phi lm bng c. Mi ngi ngh ti dng th ti s i tip v cng i cng vng hn cho mi ngi thy. Kin thc l v gi m phi khng?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;table style="text-align: left; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" id="table1" width="51%" border="0" cellspacing="1"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td rowspan="3" width="390"&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/17/02/07/091217thuytop2.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/17/02/07/091217thuytop2.jpg" width="390" border="0" height="519" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/17/02/07/091217thuytop1.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/17/02/07/091217thuytop1.jpg" width="126" border="0" height="164" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/17/02/07/091217thuytop3.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/17/02/07/091217thuytop3.jpg" width="128" border="0" height="184" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/17/02/07/091217thuytop4.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/17/02/07/091217thuytop4.jpg" width="131" border="0" height="168" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ch thy mi trng ngh thut  Vit Nam th no? &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Cng ngy mi trng ngh thut ti Vit Nam cng pht trin hn, cng i vo chiu hng chuyn nghip hn. Nhng song song vi vic  cng gy ra vic tng v s lng nhng cht lng th ch m trn u ngn tay.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ch bc vo lng gii tr v vt 'hot' rt d dng, vy s ni ting c tm quan trng th no i vi ch?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Ni thc, vic ni ting n vi ti qu t nhin. Ti khng c lm ny lm kia  ni ting m n c n t t ri khng bit ti sng trong mi trng  t lc no. Bn hi ti ni ting c quan trng i vi ti hay khng, ti cng ang cha bit phi tr li th no y. Ti ch lm nhng vic ti yu thch, ti yu ngh thut trong tng th tht ca mnh. Ti am m c sng to trong m nhc, trong din xut v tham vng ca ti l lm kinh doanh trong c lnh vc ngh thut na. C hay chng nu ti cn c sng vi am m ca mnh, vi ngh thut th  mi l iu quan trng nht.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;table style="text-align: left; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" id="table1" width="55%" border="0" cellspacing="1"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td colspan="3"&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/17/02/07/091217thuytop5.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/17/02/07/091217thuytop5.jpg" width="546" border="0" height="368" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td width="32%"&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/17/02/07/091217thuytop8.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/17/02/07/091217thuytop8.jpg" width="180" border="0" height="269" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width="32%"&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/17/02/07/091217thuytop9.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/17/02/07/091217thuytop9.jpg" width="180" border="0" height="269" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width="34%"&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/17/02/07/091217thuytop15.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/17/02/07/091217thuytop15.jpg" width="180" border="0" height="269" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;(nh: Lukas )&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;C bao gi ch cm thy ngt ngt bi v lng gii tr c rt nhiu ph phim v th phi khin mt c gi   tui nh ch b shock?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Shock ch! &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Giang h him c&lt;/span&gt; lm, ti cn non nt. Ti s hc chuyn ngnh v Communication (truyn thng) v c Acting (din xut) xuyn sut trong bn nm hc.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;Du hc tn bn nm, ch c s n lc tr v khn gi  qun mt Thy Top l ai ?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ti sao phi s nh? V khi b nh th, ch ngh th no, c chi li khng? &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ti cha bao gi ngh phi &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;chi&lt;/span&gt; li ai  tng &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;chi&lt;/span&gt; ti c, nu lm vy l mnh km, mnh bng h. M ti dy phi ni iu hay, lm iu thin sao cho khng thn vi lng tm th s khng bao gi phi hi tic. Hi b ti cha hiu c nhiu lm, sau nhiu s vic xy ra ti  thm tha cu m dy. Vic mnh mnh phi lm tht tt, mnh thnh cng v hnh phc.  chnh l s chi thnh cng nht i vi nhng ngi khng tt vi mnh.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a rel="lightbox[roadtrip]" href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/17/02/07/091217thuytop14.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 550px; Nhng nu mun tr thnh mt minh tinh ng ngha th lm ngi mu trang ba cho FHM l cch  bin "n nh" tr thnh mt ngi ph n trng thnh v hp dn hn. Tuy nhin, trong ln ln ba ny, hnh nh ca "n nh" c nh gi l vn cha   "hot".&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width="200" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="oImage" alt="o  nng bng ca cc sao Hoa ng" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/265/t265524.jpg" align="middle" border="0" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class="pSubTitle"&gt;Phm Bng Bng&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody"&gt;c bit n l mt din vin nhng nng Kim Ta ca &lt;em&gt;Hon Chu cch cch &lt;/em&gt;ch thc s ni ting khi cc b nh bt mt, n tng v a phong cch ca c c trnh lng. L gng mt quen thuc trn FHM nhng mi ln xut hin, Phm Bng Bng u mang n mt lung gi mi v v gi cm li nm  chnh nh mt ht hn ch khng phi nhng ng cong quyn r ca c.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width="200" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="oImage" alt="o  nng bng ca cc sao Hoa ng" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/265/t265526.jpg" align="middle" border="0" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class="pSubTitle"&gt;L Bng Bng&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody"&gt;y l hnh nh ca L Bng Bng trn FHM k s 9 khi c ha thn thnh mt n sinh trung hc vi hnh tng trong sng, d thng. Gi y, L Bng Bng  hon ton lt xc v ngy cng to bo trong tng vai din, t &lt;em&gt;Thin h v tc &lt;/em&gt;ti &lt;em&gt;Phong thanh. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width="200" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="oImage" alt="o  nng bng ca cc sao Hoa ng" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/265/t265537.jpg" align="middle" border="0" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class="pSubTitle"&gt;Lu V Hm&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody"&gt;Khng xut hin nhiu trn mn nh nh nhng Lu V Hm vn l mt tn tui kh ni trong lng gii tr i lc. Trong b nh chp cho FHM ny, tuy vn gi phong cch c in vn c ca mnh, nhng v gi cm kh cng ca ngi p khin cnh my ru khng th khng m say.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width="200" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="oImage" alt="o  nng bng ca cc sao Hoa ng" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/265/t265538.jpg" align="middle" border="0" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class="pSubTitle"&gt;A a&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody"&gt;Trong lng gii tr Hoa ng, A a c v nh Lady GaGa chu  bi s ph cch y sng to trong mi ln xut hin. V trong ln ln ba cho FHM ny, c  ha thn thnh mt chng trai vi b ria mp bnh bao nhng iu  ch cng lm tng thm v gi cm cho ngi p m thi.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width="200" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="oImage" alt="o  nng bng ca cc sao Hoa ng" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/265/t265542.jpg" align="middle" border="0" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class="pSubTitle"&gt;Gi Tnh Vn&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody"&gt;Sau khi ly chng, Gi Tnh Vn tm rt lui khi lng gii tr  chuyn tm chm sc gia nh v con ci. Trc khi cuc hn nhn  v 1 nm, c quyt tm quay tr li vi s xut hin y mi l trn FHM s thng 2/2008. Khng n vn h hang nhng trng Gi Tnh Vn vn tht hp dn v tao nh.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width="200" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="oImage" alt="o  nng bng ca cc sao Hoa ng" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/265/t265543.jpg" align="middle" border="0" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class="pSubTitle"&gt;Thm Ngo Qun&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody"&gt;Ni ting vi hnh tng ngy th hn nhin, trc khi ly chng, Thm Ngo Qun  lm cc fan phi bt ng trong b nh sexy gi cm sau khi ln ba cho FHM. Bi cnh l nhng bc tng th rp nhng khng giu ni v sexy rt t nhin ca Ngo Qun.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width="200" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="oImage" alt="o  nng bng ca cc sao Hoa ng" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/265/t265572.jpg" align="middle" border="0" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class="pSubTitle"&gt;ng Dao&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="pBody"&gt;Nng ng Dao hay cn c gi l Tiu Chng T Di ni ting vi v scandal cng con trai ca Trng Quc Lp. Nhng ngi p  khin d lun nhanh chng qun i tai ting ny khi xut hin y quyn r trn FHM s thng 7/2007. Bt ng gp Minh Th ti H Ni, vi b  en gin d v cp mt knh to khng giu i v ngi sng ca n din vin xinh p. &lt;/div&gt;    Thng thn trc mi chuyn nhng ring tin n  ly chng v sinh em b th ch li phn ng kiu nc i...&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/10/10/31/091210minhthu1.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/12/10/10/31/091210minhthu1.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center; va bm my, Qu c tui dn - Minh Th nhn vai c gi tui cp, gii v v... manly. c bit gp mt trong nhm qu c tui dn, bn cnh Gi nhy Minh Th cn c Anh Th v Kim Th...&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Kch bn phim th hai khin Minh Th khng cng li c l Anh em nh bc s phin bn Vit ca o din Minh Cao. B phim s khi quay t u thng 1/2010. Vai din ny ca ch s ng cp vi nhn vt ca Chi Bo. Mt vai din khc na, d bn vt chn ln c nhng Th vn gt u tham gia trong thng 1 ti l vai phn din trong 30 tp phim Phin ch s ca o din Minh Hin.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Thi gian ny, ti bn lm. type='text'>Siu mu 9x Ngc Thch sexy ngoi ph!</title><content type='html'>Vi nh mt sc lm, cng nhng bc chn iu luyn m c ngi mu 9x ny nhanh chng chim c cm tnh ca gii chuyn mn cng nh thng tin ghi im trong lng cng chng.     &lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Sinh nm 1991, l th sinh nh tui nht vo vng chung kt Siu mu Vit Nam 2009  li nhiu n tng, siu mu 9x Ngc Thch chia s k nim - &lt;span width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-4507822551393930387?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/4507822551393930387'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/4507822551393930387'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/11/giang-my-chi-tien-ti-to-chuc-sinh-nhat.html' title='Ging My chi tin t t chc sinh nht'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-2360892054952170560</id><published>2009-11-11T23:36:00.000-08:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:47.948-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><title type='text'>Hoa Hu Ng Phng Lan: p khng t vt</title><content type='html'>c xem l Hoa Hu ton din nht v sc p, tri thc v tm lng t thin hng n cng ng, chnh nhng vic lm t thin s cng tn vinh v p ca mt Hoa Hu.     &lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Ngy mai (13/11), Hoa Hu &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Phng Lan&lt;/span&gt; s n thm cc bnh nhn ti Bnh vin Nhi Trung ng, chuyn thm nm trong chui tin s kin &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Cuc chy v tr em H Ni 2009 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;c t chc vi mc ch t thin, nhm gy qu dnh cho tr em ngho, gp phi cc vn  v sc kho, ang iu tr ti &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Bnh vin Nhi Trung ng&lt;/span&gt; v&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt; Bnh vin U Bu H Ni&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/07/091112anh1phuonglan.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 251px; height: 195px;" src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/07/091112anh1phuonglan.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/07/091112anh2phuonglan.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 249px; height: 194px;" src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/07/091112anh2phuonglan.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Ng Phng Lan c v p ca mt c gi thun Vit hng thin,&lt;br /&gt; hi ha v &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;c gng mt sang trng. (nh: Hang H&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ngay sau chuyn i t thin trn, Hoa hu &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Phng Lan&lt;/span&gt; s bt u c mt ti Vng Tu  lm vic vi cng v MC ca cuc thi &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Hoa Hu Qu b Th gii (Mrs World 2009) &lt;/span&gt;t ngy 15 -  23/11 ti Cung trnh din Nh thi u a nng tnh B Ra - Vng Tu.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="float: right; margin-left: 10px; font-style: italic; text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;table style="border: 1px solid rgb(144, 144, 144); margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 204); text-align: left;" width="300" cellpadding="10"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Cuc chy v tr em H Ni 2009 &lt;/span&gt;c&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt; tin thn l Cuc chy Terry Fox, t chc thnh cng trong sut 10 nm qua, thu ht hn 60.000 ngi tham gia. S din ra t 7h30  10h ngy 22/11 ti H Thin Quang.  i s Qun Canada phi hp cng Lin Hip Cc T Chc Hu Ngh Vit Nam v Hip Hi Cc Doanh Nghip Canada ti Vit Nam (Cancham) ng ra t chc. n v t chc l cng ty Starmesas.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Phng Lan&lt;/span&gt;  khng ph lng nhng ngi  tin tng v t ln vai c mt trng trch ln ca Hoa Hu. &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Phng Lan&lt;/span&gt;  bit lm chic vng min ca mnh ta sng, ngoi tm giy chng nhn &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Hoa Hu Th Gii Ngi Vit 2007 &lt;/span&gt;c trang trng treo ln tng, bn cnh n gi y cn c tm bng tt nghip xut sc ca i hc Genve. Trong thi gian c ng quang cng chnh l thi gian &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Phng Lan&lt;/span&gt; ang hc nm th 3 i hc ti Thy S nhng bt c khi no c dp v nc, c cng mit mi tham gia nhit tnh cc hot ng x hi. C tham gia cc hot ng gip  cc tr em kh khn; cu tr ng bo bo lt Theo ngun tin mi nht c chia s t Hoa &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Hu Ng Phng Lan&lt;/span&gt;, hin ti c ang l &lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;Ch tch qu t thin Sao Bin.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Trong m chung kt cuc thi &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Hoa hu Th gii ngi Vit 2007&lt;/span&gt;, vi u th v vn ling kh n v ngn ng m ( cc c gi sinh sng  nc ngai thng ni ting Vit nh ting Ty), s t tin ca mt sinh vin ngnh ngoi giao  gip &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Phng Lan&lt;/span&gt; ginh c chic vng min &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Hoa Hu Th gii ngi Vit&lt;/span&gt; ln u c t chc.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/08/091112anh8phuonglan.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/08/091112anh8phuonglan.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/08/091112anh9phuonglan.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/08/091112anh9phuonglan.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Phng Lan&lt;/span&gt; trong mt chuyn t thin (nh: Hong H&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Phng Lan&lt;/span&gt;   li n tng kh qun trong lng khn gi bi phong thi v kh cht ca con nh tng (cha c, ng &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Quang Xun&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Ph Ch nhim y ban i ngoi Quc hi Vit Nam&lt;/span&gt;, tng l &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;i s Vit Nam&lt;/span&gt; ti Thy S) v suy ngh chn chn ca c gi tui i mi (c sinh nm 1987). &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Phng Lan &lt;/span&gt; ginh lun gii phn thi ng x hay nht ti m chung kt. Cu hi: "&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;V sao cc hot ng ca Hoa hu thng gn lin vi vic lm t thin&lt;/span&gt;", &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Phng Lan&lt;/span&gt; tr li: "&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Ci p,  chnh l ci thin. Chn, Thin, M l phm cht cao c nht ca ngi con gi, cng l nh cao kht vng m con ngi vn ti. Khi ci p c th gn lin vi s ho tm, tri tim nhn hu, s chn thnh th ci p  c tn vinh rt nhiu. Nn nhng vic lm t thin s cng tn vinh v p ca mt ngi Hoa hu".&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;table id="table2" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: left;" width="59%" border="0" cellspacing="1"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="vertical-align: top;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style="vertical-align: top;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/15/091112anh3phuonglan%20%282%29.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 241px; height: 375px;" src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/15/091112anh3phuonglan%20%282%29.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/15/091112anh4phuonglan.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 250px; height: 376px;" src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/15/091112anh4phuonglan.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;table id="table3" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: left;" width="59%" border="0" cellspacing="1"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/17/091112anh5phuonglan.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 182px; height: 243px;" src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/17/091112anh5phuonglan.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td rowspan="2"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/17/091112anh7phuonglan.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 316px; height: 496px;" src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/17/091112anh7phuonglan.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td height="24"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/17/091112anh6phuonglan.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 188px; height: 263px;" src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/17/091112anh6phuonglan.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;Vi thnh tch hc tp ng n, u t ti ton phn  Php, ni lu lot ba th ting: ting Vit, ting Anh, ting Php, v  tt nghip ngnh Quan h quc t  &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;i hc Genve&lt;/span&gt; vi bn lun vn xut sc v c nh gi rt cao v  ti vn ha - lch s. &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Phng Lan&lt;/span&gt; hng mnh tr thnh mt nh ngoi giao  cng hin cho t nc hoc l mt nh hot ng x hi trong mt t chc quc t no  ti Vit Nam nhm gip  nhng ngi ngho kh, v nhng hon cnh o le trong cuc sng.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/23/091112anh12phuonglan.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 250px; height: 187px;" src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/23/091112anh12phuonglan.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/23/091112anh11phuonglan.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 250px; height: 187px;" src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/23/091112anh11phuonglan.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;B m ca &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Phng Lan&lt;/span&gt; lm trong ngnh ngoi giao nn t b, c  theo b m n sng v hc tp ti nhiu nc. Vo nm 1993, cha ca &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Phng Lan&lt;/span&gt; lm &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;i s Vit Nam ti Lin hip quc&lt;/span&gt;, c  theo ba sang M v hc tiu hc ti trng Tiu hc New York (lp 1-7), vi thnh tch hc tp n tng, &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Phng Lan&lt;/span&gt;  tng c bng khen ca Tng thng Hoa K &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Bill Clinton&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/24/091112anh13phuonglan.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/12/10/24/091112anh13phuonglan.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="font-style: italic; text-align: center;"&gt;nh: Phm Hoi Nam&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Phng Lan&lt;/span&gt; c nh gi l Hoa Hu c v p ca mt c gi thun Vit hng thin, hi ha v c gng mt sang trng. &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Ng Phng Lan&lt;/span&gt; l hoa hu p ton din khng t vt.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Anh Tun Anh&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-2360892054952170560?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/2360892054952170560'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/2360892054952170560'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/11/hoa-hau-ngo-phuong-lan-ep-khong-ti-vet.html' title='Hoa Hu Ng Phng Lan: p khng t vt'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-7040525130650641335</id><published>2009-11-03T19:20:00.001-08:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:48.417-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><title type='text'>Nhng tit l th v v i din Miss World Vit Nam</title><content type='html'>&lt;div class="detail_sapo"&gt; Mt cu sinh vin tng hc cng Hng Giang chia s i din Miss World Vit Nam 2009 l mt c gi ton vn 'p ngi p nt'! &lt;/div&gt;    Khi ti ang l sinh vin Khoa Bo ch - H Quc gia H Ni, mt ngy u thu, phng k tc x cht xn xao, cc bn n sinh vin Khoa Quc t ko sang r r: "i xem c b sinh vin mi ca khoa bn tao i" Ln u tin bit n Hng Giang l mt cu chuyn vui vui, m cht sinh vin nh vy.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Bt u t ng hc hnh&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Thi im Giang vo k tc x M Tr ging nh mt s kin ca tt c cc sinh vin, bi v ai cng t m trc thng tin: "Nm nay, Khoa Quc t hc c mt em chn di, xinh lm". Sau cuc thi Hoa hu Vit Nam 2006, Hng Giang lt vo top 10 th sinh p nht. Tr v, Giang vn tip tc cuc sng ca mt sinh vin, n mc gin d, li ni chuyn nh nh, tnh cch hin lnh. C v nh nhng cuc thi sc p, nhng vy o la l, son phn xa hoa  'b' Giang b qua mt bn,  c sng ng np sng thng ngy ht sc chn cht ca mnh. Sau ny v mt s l do, Giang vo TP H Ch Minh sinh sng, Giang chuyn sang Khoa Bo ch  H Quc gia TP H Ch Minh hc. Hin nay, c ang chun b tt nghip c nhn bo ch.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/08/37/311huonggiang1.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/08/37/311huonggiang1.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Do ln trc tui v thng minh t b nn Giang hc 'vt'.&lt;br /&gt;Bi vy, Giang tt nghip i hc sm so vi  tui.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Hng Giang  c mt lch trnh hc hnh nh vy, tri vi suy ngh m nhiu ngi hnh dung chuyn hc hnh ca ngi mu l chuyn 'thm mm thm mui' lm p ci tn ca mnh, rng chn di th ln xe xung nga, vi nhng hnh nh ho nhong, bng by, sang trng. Cng vic ngi mu vi Giang thi gian u ch l kiu 'lm thm'  ri khi gn b th am m v c  bin tnh yu y thnh kt qu cng vic vi nhng tm hnh a sc, nhng bc chn chuyn nghip, t tin si di trn sn catwalk.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;C hoa hu gin d&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Thc ra, vic tham gia Hoa hu Hi Dng ca Giang cng l do m c ng k. M Giang lm  Bu in TP Hi Dng, c cc ng nghip, cc t chc on, i 'khuyn' nn cho c con gi t tham d, th l b m 'c n' V nh chun b mi th  con gi yu t tin bc vo cuc. Ginh gii Hoa hu Hi Dng, Giang bt u mnh dn th sc  cuc thi sc p mang tnh cht quc gia: Hoa hu Vit Nam. C nhiu l do  Giang la chn, nhng mt trong nhng 'b mt' m Giang 'bt m'  l s thch du lch, khm ph v tm hiu vn ha mi vng min ca c gi tr ham hiu bit.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; TP HCM, hin nay, Giang vn  nh thu, i xe my i lm. Trong gii ngi mu, Giang cng l mt trong nhng chn di cha tng dnh scandal, tin n rm beng no. Chuyn cp k i gia li cng khng c. Mi ngi u n tng v Giang l c gi d mn, n hu v ht sc khim nhng, t tn.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/08/37/311huonggiang3.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/08/37/311huonggiang3.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Tui th vt v&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Hng Giang chn chn so vi bn ng nin, ng la cng bi phn no tui th vt v m c  tri qua. B Giang b i theo ngi ph n khc,  ba m con Giang li trong nhng thiu thn vt cht. M Giang k rng, lc hai ch em Giang cn nh, cha bao gi trn mm cm c  3 mn n. Bui sng m i lm, hai con gi i hc, c ba m con u khng n sng.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Tra v m bc bt cm vi da c, c vi ngy mi 'dm' ci thin bng mt ba n mn. Cc con thng m vt v nn c hai ch em u  thc hc hnh, chm ngoan v hiu tho. Con nh ngi khc th hc thm ch ny ch kia, hai ch em Giang sau khi hc  lp, v nh m dy hai con, ch dy em n bi. Hng Hnh, ch gi Giang, c nng khiu v cc mn t nhin, Giang thin hng v cc mn x hi.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/08/37/311huonggiang4.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/08/37/311huonggiang4.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Hnh tt nghip th khoa 'u ra' Trng Hc vin Bu chnh Vin thng, hin ang lm cho mt t chc phi Chnh ph, thu nhp kh. Chnh thi gian Giang vo TP H Ch Minh lp nghip, Hnh l ngi 'chi vin' cho c em,  n thay m. Kh nhc l th nhng ch em Giang sng y yu thng, chan ha v bit gip  ngi khc t nh. M Giang nh mi mt ln vo ma ng rt mt, khi c i lm v, thy Hnh v Giang c ln lt nhn nhau, m hi c chuyn g, Giang thnh tht k li: "C c b i ngang qua, trng c lnh lm, m khng c g che chn, con cho c ci chn bng, nhng nng qu, c khng mang i c, con li cho c ci v chn ri".&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Chnh m Giang l mt tm gng tt cho hai c con gi noi theo. Mt thn mt mnh tng tim nui hai con nn ngi, hc hnh ng hong, t t. Cch sng ca ngi m  nh hng mnh m n tnh cch nhng ngi con. Hai ch em Giang  lun ngng cao u, sng vng vng y kiu hnh v t trng. Nu khng c mt nn mng vng chi t s gio dc ca ngi m th d u c mt ngi p cng ci, bn lnh v sng gin d, chng mc n nhng y.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/08/37/311huonggiang5t.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/08/37/311huonggiang5t.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Mt Hng Giang trng thnh&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Trc thng tin Giang l i din ca Vit Nam ti cuc thi Hoa hu Th gii 2009, c nhiu  kin tri ngc nhau. C khng t nhng li chc mng, ng vin, ngi khen, ng h, nhng cng c nhng  kin phin din v ch quan, thm ch l hn hc, cay c. Hi Giang c t i khng, tm l c b nh hng khng, Giang vn nh nhng ci t tn ni: "Em ngh ngi ta cha tip xc vi em nn cha hiu em thi.Vi li nhng  kin a chiu cng gip mnh hc hi c nhiu kinh nghim".&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Hin ti, Giang ang rt bn rn chun b hnh trang cho vic ln ng sang Nam Phi tham gia u trng sc p ln hng u th gii. Vi s o hnh th chun, gng mt phc hu, n ci ta sng, kinh nghim tch ly c t cc cuc thi nhan sc trc, phong cch trnh din ca mt ngi mu hng A, kh nng ting Anh lu lot v s t tin cng nh kh nng giao tip ca mt c nhn bo ch, hy vng Hng Giang s lm nn chuyn.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;Chc Hng Giang may mn!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Theo &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;Php lut x hi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-7040525130650641335?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/7040525130650641335'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/7040525130650641335'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/11/nhung-tiet-lo-thu-vi-ve-ai-dien-miss.html' title='Nhng tit l th v v i din Miss World Vit Nam'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-7587207472396379838</id><published>2009-11-03T19:20:00.000-08:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:48.400-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hot Girl - Scandal'/><title type='text'>H Anh: Ti v Henry Hubert ch l bn</title><content type='html'>&lt;div class="detail_sapo"&gt; Lun thy H Anh xut hin cng chng trai da en Henry Hubert (mt stylist ni ting trong gii ngi mu, tng gn b vi ngi mu Bo Ha). Nhng vi &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Ni bnh yn&lt;/span&gt;, album  lt t cm xc chn tht ca ngi n b tui 40, vn y khao kht vi cc cung bc trong tnh yu, khi th trong sng, hn nhin, lc li d di, chy bng hoc c lc li khc khoi, trng vng khi n ci.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/04/17/091104anh3thanhlam.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/04/17/091104anh3thanhlam.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Gi y, s bnh yn, cn bng n vi &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Thanh Lam&lt;/span&gt; bi c rt bit pht huy u im ca mnh, xut hin  nhng ba tic nh m, khoe nhng ch nn khoe cng nhng pht ngn mnh mm lin quan n "&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;i g bng o&lt;/span&gt;".&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/03/51/091104anh1phale.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/03/51/091104anh1phale.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/03/51/091104anh2phale.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 250px; trong b phim &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Lp trnh tri tim&lt;/span&gt;. &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;V V&lt;/span&gt; ca &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Qunh Nga&lt;/span&gt; trong phim liu  i n mt trnh  'siu ng' (?!).&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/04/00/091104anh2quynhnga.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/04/00/091104anh2quynhnga.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/04/00/091104anh3quynhnga.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/04/00/091104anh3quynhnga.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/04/00/091104anh4quynhnga.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/04/04/00/091104anh4quynhnga.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Gng mt xinh xn, ln da trng tro, &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Qunh Nga&lt;/span&gt; thuc nhng cng khng h l lm vi lng gii tr Vit.  l Hng Kim Hnh  n din vin ca Em mun lm ngi ni ting, Ma ci, Tri tim b bng.     Thi gian ny gp &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Lam Trng &lt;/span&gt;qu l rt kh. Anh ang tt bt vi album mi v cng vic hin ti l quay video clip.  lu khng ra album mi nn trong d n m nhc ti y, &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Lam Trng&lt;/span&gt; ang rt c gng  to ra nhng sn phm hon ho nht c th.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/02/00/25/091102ltruong1.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/11/02/00/25/091102ltruong1.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Hnh nh mi trong video clip ca Lam Trng&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;Nhng ai  tng xem video clip ca &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Lam Trng&lt;/span&gt; khng th qun c nhng cu chuyn, nhng hnh nh v cng lng mn v y tnh ngh thut. L mt ngi rt vui v nhng ring trong cng vic, &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Lam Trng &lt;/span&gt;l li rt k tnh. Mi MV ra mt l mt sn phm m anh v c ekip ca mnh  phi la chn, tnh ton phng n tt nht. Trong , tm din vin din chung vi anh Hai cng l mt cng vic khng h d dng.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;My ngy qua, &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Lam Trng &lt;/span&gt; thc hin video Clip &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;My&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;v &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Cm n em&lt;/span&gt;. y l hai ca khc rt lng mn vi mt kch bn rt hp dn. Trc khi tr thnh din vin, &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Kim Hnh&lt;/span&gt;  tng nui mng ca s. C  phi vt qua rt nhiu gng mt tn tui  c c c hi ng chung clip vi anh Hai &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Lam Trng&lt;/span&gt;.
