Trc Dim th l.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="fl op news-content"&gt;&lt;div class="newsdetailsource fr"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Bt khc m vn phi din&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Thi gian ny Trc Dim  tr li rm r, vy khong lng trc y l v sao?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ti  dnh mt thi gian di im ng  tp trung hon ton cho vic nng cao kin thc ca mnh. V khong lng ny cng l lc  ti nhn li qung ng mnh  i v vch ra con ng mnh s i trong tng lai. Dng li nh hng  bc tip  m.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img src="http://xinhxinh.com.vn/UserFiles/Image/2009/102009/19/Truc%20Diem/2009101910626-6.jpg" alt="" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Vai din trong "Nht k Bch Tuyt" l mt vai rt kh, ln u ng phim nha, v sao ch li dng cm v hng th vi vai ny?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ngy u tin c o din L Bo Trung mi n casting cho vai din ti  chun b tinh thn l ch i cast  ly kinh nghim v th sc mnh. Nhng sau khi c kch bn tht s ti rt ho hng v hy vng s ginh c vai.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Kch bn kh l so vi nhng b phim Vit Nam v nhn vt Bch Tuyt cng l mt vai l, phc tp. c th thch mnh vo mt vai kh nh vy l mt c hi rt ln  ti nng cao kh nng din xut.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img src="http://xinhxinh.com.vn/UserFiles/Image/2009/102009/19/Truc%20Diem/2009101910626-Truc%20Diem.jpg" alt="" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Nghe ni, trong sut qu trnh quay phim ch  b bm dp theo ngha en bi nhng cnh quay nguy him, ch c th chia s ci cm gic ri t trn cao xung?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Tht s, khi thc hin nhng cnh quay , ti rt lo s, c khi s qu bt khc m vn phi tip tc din cho tht t. Tuy iu kin khng tt, nhng cc anh ch cascadeur  rt nhit tnh gip  v bo v nn ti cng yn tm phn no.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;C nhiu li mi ch tham gia phim truyn hnh nhng ch t chi, c phi v ln mn nh nh th khng... sang trng?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Tht bt ng v ngay sau khi hon thnh vai Bch Tuyt, kh nhiu o din mi ti tham gia, c in nh v truyn hnh. C mt s vai rt hay nhng trong thi im ny, Dim ang mun tp trung ton lc  thc hin CD.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ti rt tic khi phi t chi cc vai din hay, hi vng sau ny s c c hi tr li vi phim trng mt ln na.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Cng thi im phim ra rp ch c  nh pht hnh album lun ch?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Tt nhin, ti ang c gng ht sc v hi vng sau khi thy mt Trc Dim... ln ln trn mn nh rng th khn gi c th tip tc hng th vi mt Trc Dim tht khc l trn sn khu ca nhc.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;C nhng lc tng nh khng th chu ng hn c na&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Dim c tng ngh mnh s t b ngh thut do qu nhiu p lc ca gii showbiz?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; chp nhn bc vo showbiz c ngha l cng chp nhn vic phi sng vi p lc t nhiu pha. C nhng lc ti tng chng nh tt c qu sc vi mnh v khng th chu ng thm c na.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Th nhng c sng v lm vic trong mi trng ngh thut l tt c nhng g ti mong i, ch c  y ti mi c l chnh mnh. V th trong ti s mi khng c hai ch: T b.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Thnh cng s ch n vi nhng ai bit vt qua kh khn.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img src="http://xinhxinh.com.vn/UserFiles/Image/2009/102009/19/Truc%20Diem/200910191068-1.jpg" alt="" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Ngi mu th h ch gn nh  lui vo hu trng  lp gia nh, iu  c khin ch thy n c?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Cu tr li ca ti l: Khng.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Sau nhng g  tri qua, ch thy mnh c g t nhng nm thng trong ngh ngi mu?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Chng ng ngi mu ca ti tuy khng di nhng  l bc khi u quan trng nht trong s nghip. Nhng k nim vui bun, nhng vp ng v thnh cng u xut pht t .&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Quan trng nht, t nhng nm thng lm ngi mu, ti hc c cch chp nhn kh khn, vt qua th thch v tin n thnh cng.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img src="http://xinhxinh.com.vn/UserFiles/Image/2009/102009/19/Truc%20Diem/200910191068-2.jpg" alt="" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;iu g gip ch khng b ri vo "by" ngi p ca nhng scandal?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;S tnh to. Ti c gio dc v chun b kin thc y   hiu iu g tt, iu g xu, ci g nn lm hoc khng nn lm. Ti l ngi theo o nn cng khng bao gi mun lm g  b xung a ngc u... (ci).&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Sau ny xut hin trn sn khu, ch thch c coi l ngi p ht hay l mt ca s?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Vi ti, m nhc l tr v vi c m ngy xa ch khng ch l mt cuc do chi,  ton tm dnh ht sc cho s nghip ny, ti khng bao gi mun ch t n trnh  ca mt ngi p ht m phi l mt ngi ht p.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Phi l ngi n ng thc s yu ti&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img src="http://xinhxinh.com.vn/UserFiles/Image/2009/102009/19/Truc%20Diem/200910191068-3.jpg" alt="" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Bn b cng la vi ch hu ht  c bn , ch c st rut khi vn rong rui theo nhng am m ngh thut?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Khng ai c th on trc c vic g ht, ti ngh mnh s lp gia nh khi n thi im chn mui, c s nghip v tnh yu u thng hoa. Ti mong sau ny gia nh ca ti s phi tht s t ho v mnh, ti phi c nhiu iu  k li cho con ci ca mnh na.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Mt ph n xinh p v ti nng th cn g  mt ngi n ng?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Mt ngi n ng thnh t, yu thng v c kh nng che ch cho mnh. Quan trng nht vn l tnh yu m ngi y dnh cho ti.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img src="http://xinhxinh.com.vn/UserFiles/Image/2009/102009/19/Truc%20Diem/200910191068-5.jpg" alt="" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Ch c dm hy sinh nhiu cho tnh yu, v nh t b nhng am m ngh thut ca mnh?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Nu tnh yu   ln lao v nu ngi y cng sn sng hy sinh tt c v mnh, ti cng c th hy sinh tt c cho ngi . Nhng chc chn ngi yu ti phi l ngi thng cm v thu hiu cho cng vic ca ti nn iu  s khng xy ra u.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Hnh phc hin gi ca ch l g?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;c lm nhng g mnh mun, c nhng pht giy vui v vi gia nh, bn b. c sng trn vn vi tui tr ca mnh, nhn c s yu thng t nhiu ngi, c cng hin ht mnh cho ngh thut.  l tt c nhng hnh phc hin ti ca ti.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Theo Tin phong&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-4542636527777100354?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/4542636527777100354'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/4542636527777100354'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/10/truc-diem-muonboc-chay-ca-man-anh-lan.html' title='Trc Dim mun...bc chy c mn nh ln m nhc'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-7167630541551553054</id><published>2009-10-16T23:23:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:50.424-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hoa Hu - Siu Mu'/><title type='text'>6 kiu n c b ngc p nht x Hn</title><content type='html'>&lt;div class="detail_sapo"&gt;  &lt;span style="font-size:100%;"&gt;Hotgirl nh m Thy Top ang chun b vic hc di hi ti M vi rt  nhiu d nh honh trng. C cho bit, ang vit t truyn v nhng g  mnh  v s tri qua.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;    &lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;Cho Thy, Cuc sng bn M th no?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Thy&lt;/span&gt; thy yn bnh v cng, thch v  thy thoi mi lm. Chng b ai xt nt iu g, ch hc v lm nhng g  mnh mun.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;Lc  rnh ri, Thy thng lm g?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Thy &lt;/span&gt;vit t truyn. Tht y, nhng chc nm 40 tui mi  xut bn.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;i  tri!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Sao li i tri, s hay ch. C nhiu chuyn mt  mi v p lc, th nn vit l cch  cho u c bt cng thng.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/10/05/16/43/a1%20%282%29%20%283%29.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/10/05/16/43/a1%20%282%29%20%283%29.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;Khng,  l n nm 40 tui mi xut bn th lu  qu. M Thy tuyn b th s c i ngi git mnh?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;(Ci)  s c nhiu ngi c tn trong nhng cu chuyn ca&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt; Thy Top. Thy &lt;/span&gt;vit tht lm. Nhiu  lc cng n o, khng bit vit tht th c s khng. Nhng ngh li,  khi 40 tui ri th cn s g na. Lc  l b gi ri m. &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Thy&lt;/span&gt; s k li cu chuyn cuc i y  kch tnh ca mnh.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;Nhng lc  gi,  hot khng cn, bn t truyn cho ai?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Vit  cho ring mnh m, sng u c phi cho ngi khc, sao khng lm iu  g  cho bn thn c? Nn nu ch vit linh tinh  cho hot,  bn  th &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Thy &lt;/span&gt;u cn. M tui ny   lm g nhiu tri nghim  c th ra t truyn. Khi ln hn, lc   mi c th tng kt li lm sao  mnh c li khng thy thn ch.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/10/05/16/44/a2%20%282%29.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/10/05/16/44/a2%20%282%29.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;Nhng nu vit ra m khng cn bn th c  ngha g?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Thc  ra, nhiu ngi vit t truyn cng u c nhiu ngi mua, nhng ti  sao ngi ta mun pht hnh? V ngi ta mun nh du mt bc tin,  hoc mt mc trong cuc i mnh ch khng hn l v tin.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;Vi t truyn, nhiu khi  vit chnh l  gii ta?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Mi ngi c mt l do  ngi  t mn tng cu tng ch. &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Thy &lt;/span&gt;s  nht l nhiu khi ngi ngm ngh nh li nhng g xy ra vi mnh, git  mnh v c qu nhiu chuyn, v thy n rt l ly k. &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Thy &lt;/span&gt;s b qun tt c nhng th y,  s qun nhng ngi thn thng tng  cnh mnh, s b qun cm gic  thch th v iu g . s qun nhng ngi tng tt vi mnh...y, v  vn l do khin mnh mun vit.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/10/05/16/45/a3%20%282%29.jpg" rel="lightbox[roadtrip]"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.2sao.vietnamnet.vn/2009/10/05/16/45/a3%20%282%29.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;Nghe Thy  ni, khng h thy "nng" nh vi ngi vn tng?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Th ha  ra mi ngi vn tng th . Kh nh,  th &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Thy &lt;/span&gt;"nng" cng c, nht nha cng c. Gi &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Thy &lt;/span&gt;khng mun l ngi ca cng  chng na, mun l ngi bnh thng c sng vui v, hnh phc thi.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: normal;"&gt;Theo&lt;/span&gt; Tin Phong&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-2774506835609736378?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='related' href='http://www.vnbook.us/2009/10/thuy-top-nam-40-tuoi-se-xuat-ban-tu.html' title='Thy Top: Nm 40 tui s xut bn t truyn!'/><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/2774506835609736378'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/2774506835609736378'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/10/thuy-top-nam-40-tuoi-se-xuat-ban-tu.html' title='Thy Top: Nm 40 tui s xut bn t truyn!'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-686188484468753978</id><published>2009-10-03T18:54:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:52.362-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hoa Hu - Siu Mu'/><title type='text'>Top 10 siu mu 'sexy' nht lng thi trang (P3)</title><content type='html'>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Heidi Klum &lt;a href="http://www.vnbook.us/2009/10/top-10-sieu-mau-sexy-nhat-lang-thoi.html"&gt;(Phn 2)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Li mt gng mt na trong  tui ngi mu thp nin 90 ghi tn trong danh sch top 10 siu mu gi cm nht th gii,  l Heidi Klum. Cng vi nhng ci tn nh m khc nh Elle Macpherson, Evangelista, Christy Turlington, Naomi Campbell, Cindy Crawford... Nhng ng cong "cht ngi" cng n ci rng r, to nng, khng g c th ngn cn Heidi tr thnh ngi ph n quyn r nht th gii. Ngoi vai tr l mt siu mu ni ting trong gii thi trang, chn di gc c ny cn thnh cng trong cc lnh vc khc nh nh sn xut chng trnh truyn hnh, nh thit k, mt din vin, nh kinh doanh, vit sch... Chng th m, tn tui ca Heidi ngy cng ni danh trn khp th gii vi nhiu k lc.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;K lc v ngi c i chn c bo him t nht th gii, l siu mu ng th 2 trong top nhng siu mu giu nht th gii, ngi k hp ng qung co vi nhn hiu ni y Victoria"s Secret vi s tin ct-s khng l, l ngi dn chng trnh truyn hnh vi s lng ngi xem ng o nht... v ng thi cng l chn di... mang thai nhiu ln nht trong lng mu th gii. D ang  tui mn m, Heidi vn l biu tng thi trang gi cm m hng triu ph n trn th gii m n.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Hin chn di ngi c ny ang mang bu a con th 4, song Heidi vn c coi l ngi p khng tui, lun tr trung, hin i.  c tot ln phong cch ca mt siu mu hin i mc d  qu tui  si bc trn sn catwalk.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Khi chuyn sang kinh doanh v ly bit danh ny lm nhn hiu cho cc trang phc lt v m phm ca mnh, Elle Macpherson cng rt thnh cng. Theo tp ch kinh t M Forbes, tr gi ti sn ca c hin l 110 triu USD. D  46 tui, song Elle Macpherson vn c c th gii xem l ngi p khng tui bi c s hu mt thn hnh cc chun khin cc c gi tr cng phi thm mun.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Khun mt xinh p cng s o ba vng 92-62-89, Elle cng vi Evangelista, Christy Turlington, Naomi Campbell, Cindy Crawford c coi l th h u tin ca cm t siu mu. Chn di ngi c ny cng tng c bu chn l ngi mu p nht mi thi i.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" width="490"&gt;     &lt;tbody&gt;         &lt;tr&gt;             &lt;td colspan="2"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Top 10 siu mu 'sexy' nht lng thi trang (P2), Thi trang, " src="http://www21.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-10-03/1254530382-Elle_-Macpherson_200910.jpg" width="490" height="306" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;         &lt;/tr&gt;         &lt;tr&gt;             &lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Top 10 siu mu 'sexy' nht lng thi trang (P2), Thi trang, " src="http://www21.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-10-03/1254530382-Elle_-Macpherson_200901.jpg" width="245" height="350" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;             &lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Top 10 siu mu 'sexy' nht lng thi trang (P2), Thi trang, " src="http://www21.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-10-03/1254530382-Elle_-Macpherson_200902.jpg" width="245" height="353" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;         &lt;/tr&gt;     &lt;/tbody&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt; &lt;em&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;Nhng ng cong nng bng ca Elle Macpherson tng lm m m lng ngi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" href="http://www.24h.com.vn/news.php/456/253975/Video-Nu-hoang-bikini-dua-nang.24h"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;Xem video: 'N hong' &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;bikini... a nng&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. C  3 nm lin tip xut hin trn tp ch o tm danh ting Sports Illustrated. Gisele s hu mt thn hnh hon ho hi ra tin. Ring nm 2008, l nm chn di ngi Brazil ny xut hin nhiu nht trn cc ba tp ch v phn ln trong s  l nhng b nh ngc trn. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;table align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" width="490"&gt; Tuy nhin, tp ch FHM vn khng th khng a tn c vo danh sch nhng siu mu gi cm nht lng thi trang. Ti khng th l Gisele c.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 206px; height: 305px;" src="http://nhacvietplus.vietnamnet.vn/Library/Images/23/2009/10/2/m%20nhan1/32.jpg" /&gt;  &lt;img style="width: 192px; height: 305px;" src="http://nhacvietplus.vietnamnet.vn/Library/Images/23/2009/10/2/m%20nhan1/33.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img src="http://nhacvietplus.vietnamnet.vn/Library/Images/23/2009/10/2/m%20nhan1/34.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-8458590777279789364?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/8458590777279789364'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/8458590777279789364'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/10/10-mi-nhan-kho-cuong.html' title='10 m nhn &amp;quot;cong&amp;quot; kh cng'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-2402453199179903543</id><published>2009-10-01T23:07:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:52.738-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><title type='text'>Top 10 sao 'teen' hot nht Hollywood</title><content type='html'>&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Miley Cyrus bt u ni ting sau series phim Hannah Montana ca knh Disney. Tng c d on l s chim ngi Britney Spears, Miley tr thnh ngi sao teen c yu thch nht v mt trong s cc ngi sao giu nht. Miley  c dng hai tng sp ti bo tng Madame Tussaud.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-26/1253922731-Miley-cyrus-sao-teen-1.jpg" alt="Top 10 sao 'teen' hot nht Hollywood, Phim, Vanessa Hudgens, Miley Cyrus, Emma Watson, Hayden Panettiere, Blake Lively, Taylor Swift, Selena Gomez, Kristen Steward, Dakota Fanning, Jordin Sparks, sao teen" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Miley Cyrus.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Trong nm 2009, c dnh ba gii thng ca Teen Choice Awards: N ca s xut sc, B phim hi c yu thch nht, N din vin phim hi xut sc. Theo xp hng ca tp ch Forbes, Miley xp  v tr th hai sau Daniel Radcliffe trong danh sch 10 ngi sao di 19 tui c nh hng ln nht.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Vanessa Hudgens bt u ng phim t lc b, c bt u ni ting trong b phim High School Musical. Sau  cn tham gia nhiu phim khc, trong  phn ln l cc b phim truyn hnh nhiu tp.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-26/1253922870-Vanessa-hudgen-sao-teen-1.jpg" alt="Top 10 sao 'teen' hot nht Hollywood, Phim, Vanessa Hudgens, Miley Cyrus, Emma Watson, Hayden Panettiere, Blake Lively, Taylor Swift, Selena Gomez, Kristen Steward, Dakota Fanning, Jordin Sparks, sao teen" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;Vanessa Hudgens.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Vanessa tng  l nh kho thn c gi cho bn trai c vo nm 2007. S vic trm trng n mc hng Disney nh ct hp ng v khng cho c tip tc ng phim. Tuy nhin, Vanessa  t ng ln bng chnh i chn ca mnh, vt qua c nhng iu ting ca d lun v khng nh ti nng din xut qua phn ba ca High school musical.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Emma Watson c bit n nhiu qua vai din Hermione Granger, mt trong ba vai chnh ca lot phim Harry Potter. Trc khi c chn vo vai Hermione  tui ln 9, Watson cha tng din xut chuyn nghip m ch tham gia mt s v kch ca trng.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-26/1253922731-Emma-watson-sao-teen-1.jpg" alt="Top 10 sao 'teen' hot nht Hollywood, Phim, Vanessa Hudgens, Miley Cyrus, Emma Watson, Hayden Panettiere, Blake Lively, Taylor Swift, Selena Gomez, Kristen Steward, Dakota Fanning, Jordin Sparks, sao teen" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;Emma Watson.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Vai din Hermione trong Harry Potter  em li cho c khon doanh thu khng l, nm 2009 c c xp th 6 trong danh sch Cc ngi sao tr quan trng nht do tp ch Forbes bnh chn.  Mc d kim c nhiu tin t cng vic din xut, nhng Emma Watson khng nh s khng b vic hc  ch tm hon ton vo nghip din vin. Theo c, trng lp em li cm gic c gn gi vi thc t v mi ngi xung quanh.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Hayden Panettiere bt u lm ngi mu khi mi bn thng tui, v ln u tin xut hin trong mt phim qung co cho Playskool khi 11 tui. Vai din u tin ca c l Sarah Victoria trong phim One Life to Live. Hayden tng c  c gii Grammy vi vic lng ting cho nhn vt Dot trong phim A Bug's Life.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-26/1253922731-Hayden-Panettiere-sao-teen-.jpg" alt="Top 10 sao 'teen' hot nht Hollywood, Phim, Vanessa Hudgens, Miley Cyrus, Emma Watson, Hayden Panettiere, Blake Lively, Taylor Swift, Selena Gomez, Kristen Steward, Dakota Fanning, Jordin Sparks, sao teen" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Hayden Panettiere.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Blake Lively sinh ra trong mt gia nh ton din vin. M c l nh qun l ti nng tr, b l din vin kim o din Ernie Lively. N din vin cao 1,78m tng c tp ch Askmen xp th 80 trong danh sch 99 ph n p nht th gii vo nm 2006 v ng th chn trong top 100 ph n hp dn th gii nm 2008 ca tp ch FHM. C gi tc vng  tham gia vo series phim truyn hnh ni ting c M Gossip Girl. Blake va hon thnh vai din mi nht trong b phim New York, I Love You, ng cng Shia LaBeouf v Natalie Portman.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-26/1253922731-Blake-lively-sao-teen-1.jpg" alt="Top 10 sao 'teen' hot nht Hollywood, Phim, Vanessa Hudgens, Miley Cyrus, Emma Watson, Hayden Panettiere, Blake Lively, Taylor Swift, Selena Gomez, Kristen Steward, Dakota Fanning, Jordin Sparks, sao teen" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;Blake Lively.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Taylor Swift l n ca s ti danh, nhng c cuc sng ring t khng cht tai ting  Hollywood.  T New York Times miu t Taylor l "mt trong nhng ngi sng tc nhc pop hay nht, ngi theo ch ngha thc t u tin ca dng nhc ng qu v lin h vi i t ca mnh hn nhiu ngi ln khc". Theo Forbes, Taylor Swift xp th 69 trong nhng ngi ni ting quyn lc nht vi thu nhp 18 triu USD trong nm 2009.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-26/1253922870-Taylor-swift-sao-teen-1.jpg" alt="Top 10 sao 'teen' hot nht Hollywood, Phim, Vanessa Hudgens, Miley Cyrus, Emma Watson, Hayden Panettiere, Blake Lively, Taylor Swift, Selena Gomez, Kristen Steward, Dakota Fanning, Jordin Sparks, sao teen" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Taylor Swift.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Selena Gomez l mt din vin kh ni ting trong dn sao teen ca knh Disney. C  c Disney pht hin trong mt cuc tm ti nng ton quc khi c ln 12 tui. T thi im  n nay, Selena c mt s lng phim ng n cho knh truyn hnh dnh cho tui teen.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-26/1253922870-Selena-gomez-sao-teen-1.jpg" alt="Top 10 sao 'teen' hot nht Hollywood, Phim, Vanessa Hudgens, Miley Cyrus, Emma Watson, Hayden Panettiere, Blake Lively, Taylor Swift, Selena Gomez, Kristen Steward, Dakota Fanning, Jordin Sparks, sao teen" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Selena Gomez.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Kristen Steward ni ln t sau b phim kinh d Panic room bn cnh n din vin Jodie Foster. C b m mn lt sng v thch n sushi ny c m c ln ln s tr thnh nh vn. Ln u xut hin trc khn gi ca c b l trong Thirteenth year khi Kristen mi 9 tui. Kristen tng c  c gii N din vin tr ti nng trong h thng gii dnh cho Din vin tr.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-26/1253922731-Kristen-stewward-sao-teen-1.jpg" alt="Top 10 sao 'teen' hot nht Hollywood, Phim, Vanessa Hudgens, Miley Cyrus, Emma Watson, Hayden Panettiere, Blake Lively, Taylor Swift, Selena Gomez, Kristen Steward, Dakota Fanning, Jordin Sparks, sao teen" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Kristen Steward.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Dakota Fanning l n din vin tr ti nng ca M. Fanning  c vai din t ph trong b phim Ti l Sam vo nm 2001. Tnh n nm 2007, c  ng cc b phim ni ting nh War of the Worlds v Charlotte's eb. C dnh kh nhiu gii thng in nh, v hin ti ang gi v tr l din vin nh tui nht tng c  c cho gii thng Screen Actors Guild.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-26/1253922731-DAkota-fanning-sao-teen-1.jpg" alt="Top 10 sao 'teen' hot nht Hollywood, Phim, Vanessa Hudgens, Miley Cyrus, Emma Watson, Hayden Panettiere, Blake Lively, Taylor Swift, Selena Gomez, Kristen Steward, Dakota Fanning, Jordin Sparks, sao teen" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Dakota Fanning. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Jordin Sparks l n ca s nhc pop ngi M. Nm 2007, c tr thnh ngi chin thng ca cuc thi m nhc American Idol ln th 6 khi mi 17 tui v tr thnh th sinh tr tui nht ng quang trong lch s cuc thi. Sau khi cuc thi kt thc, Sparks  tham gia nhiu chng trnh truyn hnh cng nh xut hin trn nhiu trang ba tp ch.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-26/1253922731-Jordin-sparrk-sao-teen-1.jpg" alt="Top 10 sao 'teen' hot nht Hollywood, Phim, Vanessa Hudgens, Miley Cyrus, Emma Watson, Hayden Panettiere, Blake Lively, Taylor Swift, Selena Gomez, Kristen Steward, Dakota Fanning, Jordin Sparks, sao teen" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; V p gi cm cng khun mt gc cnh c tnh ca Olga lun c nhc n nh biu tng n hong sc p t im cho nhng thc phim hnh ng gay cn.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="10 tuyt sc giai nhn th gii (P1), Phim, Monica Bellucci, Olga Kurylenko, Penelope Cruz,Keira Knightley,Noriko Sakai" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-10-01/1254389914-Olga-Kurylenko-5.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;Khi nghip vi t cch l mt ngi mu chuyn nghip t nm 13 tui, mi n nm 2005, Olga mi thc s bc chn vo lng in nh vi nhng vai din u tin bnh hoa di ng. Sau ny, ngi ta bit n v yu thch c nhiu hn sau b phim 007 vi vai din n tng - ngi tnh James Bond.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="10 tuyt sc giai nhn th gii (P1), Phim, Monica Bellucci, Olga Kurylenko, Penelope Cruz,Keira Knightley,Noriko Sakai" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-10-01/1254389914-Olga-Kurylenko-1.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Olga hi t nhng nt p c sc ca ph n Ukraine&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;Nhng nt p c sc nht ca ph n Ukraine hi t trn khun mt v c th c  to nn bc t ph trong cng cuc ch to ngi sao th h mi ti Php. Nhn c nhng t cht tim n t c ngi mu tr tui v c tnh ny, cc nh qun l  nh hnh mt ngi sao mi vi phong cch khc hn vi nhng bc n ch trc .&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;i mt su, to trn mu ht d; mi tc ngn v nng ng; thn hnh nng bng nhng khng mt i v khu cc, Olga chinh phc hon ton nhng khn gi kh tnh nht.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ty Ban Nha: Penelope Cruz:  Mi hng  lu m say lng ngi&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="10 tuyt sc giai nhn th gii (P1), Phim, Monica Bellucci, Olga Kurylenko, Penelope Cruz,Keira Knightley,Noriko Sakai" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-10-01/1254390201-Penelope-Cruz-3.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;"N thn tnh i" ca t nc Ty Ban Nha&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;n tng v t nc Ty Ban Nha xa xi trong lng bn l g? iu nhc latinh si ni cng nhng v cng c vng ba bc la? L nhng trn u b tt cung nhit hay n gin ch l chng cu th Raul in trai vi nhng ng bng iu luyn? Ring ti, sc thu ht diu k t th ngn ng c m vc su lng  lun l iu m nh trong suy ngh mi khi ct ting c Ty Ban Nha.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="10 tuyt sc giai nhn th gii (P1), Phim, Monica Bellucci, Olga Kurylenko, Penelope Cruz,Keira Knightley,Noriko Sakai" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-10-01/1254390201-Penelope-Cruz-4.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Mi hng  lu m say lng ngi&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="10 tuyt sc giai nhn th gii (P1), Phim, Monica Bellucci, Olga Kurylenko, Penelope Cruz,Keira Knightley,Noriko Sakai" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-10-01/1254390201-Penelope-Cruz-1.jpg" width="500" height="366" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;S la chn s 1 ca cc o din Hollywood&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;Xut hin trn mn nh vi hu ht nhng vai din gi cm nng bng, phn ng ngi hm m nh n c bi i g bng o n nang v nh nhn thiu t mn nh. Nhng him ai bit rng, ngi p Ty Ban Nha ny cn c nhiu ti l ng khen ngi khc: v o iu luyn nhiu ln ot gii, cng lc s dng thnh tho 3 ngn ng: Anh, Php, Ty Ban Nha, ging ca khn c tnh v m hoc lng ngi.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Anh: Keira Knightley: Bng mu n ang k n r&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="10 tuyt sc giai nhn th gii (P1), Phim, Monica Bellucci, Olga Kurylenko, Penelope Cruz,Keira Knightley,Noriko Sakai" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-10-01/1254390371-Keira-Knightley-4.jpg" width="500" height="467" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;C din vin con nh ni Keira Knightley &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;C din vin con nh ni Keira Knightley  c c hi tip cn trc ng knh my quay t nm ln 9 vi vai din Moira Armstrong trong b phim in nh &lt;em&gt;A Village Affair&lt;/em&gt; nm 1994. M ca Keira l nh bin kch Sharman Macdonald, l ngi u tin a Keira n vi ngh thut th 7 nhng cha bao gi b hi lng v nhng thnh tch m Keira c c. Nm 1999, Keira lm th thn cho n hong Padme Midala-vai din trong b phim &lt;em&gt;Star Wars: Episode I-The Phantom Menace.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="10 tuyt sc giai nhn th gii (P1), Phim, Monica Bellucci, Olga Kurylenko, Penelope Cruz,Keira Knightley,Noriko Sakai" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-10-01/1254390371-Keira-Knightley-5.jpg" width="500" height="375" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nt tr trung v hin i&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;Sau ny, nhng vai din tip theo ca c trong &lt;em&gt;The Hole&lt;/em&gt;(2001) hay&lt;em&gt; Bend it like Beckham &lt;/em&gt; chim c cm tnh ca ng o khn gi hm m. Cng k t khi , trn thm  ca cc lin hoan phim quc t s c thm mt khun mt rc r ti sng- a mu n ang k n r Keira Knightley.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="10 tuyt sc giai nhn th gii (P1), Phim, Monica Bellucci, Olga Kurylenko, Penelope Cruz,Keira Knightley,Noriko Sakai" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-10-01/1254390371-Keira-Knightley-3.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nng bng...&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="10 tuyt sc giai nhn th gii (P1), Phim, Monica Bellucci, Olga Kurylenko, Penelope Cruz,Keira Knightley,Noriko Sakai" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-10-01/1254390371-Keira-Knightley-2.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;... v sexy&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;Mt phong cch tr trung v ti mi vi nhiu ph cch trong tiu chun nh gi nt p ca mt m n quen thuc. Keira c nt ni bt nht l khun mt thanh mnh v ln mi mm t gi cm. Hu ht nhng ngi yu mn Keira u thuc hai thi cc: Mt l v cng n tnh v thy m v na cn li l nng ng v c tnh. Mi ln nhn thy c li c th cm nhn c nhng nt p khc nhau, hi t ca ti nng v t cht ngh s phong cch.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nht Bn: Noriko Sakai&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="10 tuyt sc giai nhn th gii (P1), Phim, Monica Bellucci, Olga Kurylenko, Penelope Cruz,Keira Knightley,Noriko Sakai" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-10-01/1254390581-Noriko-Sakai-2.jpg" width="500" height="375" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;"Ngi sao may mn" Noriko Sakai&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana;"&gt;Ngi ph n no s mang n s yn bnh v th thi nht cho cnh my ru? &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Siu mu v l v hin nay ca Briatore - Elisabetta Gregoraci (24)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-1608664144110803830?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/1608664144110803830'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/1608664144110803830'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/09/nhung-chan-dai-qua-tay-bo-gia-f1.html' title='Nhng chn di  qua tay b gi F1'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-3333760720914000859</id><published>2009-09-27T20:52:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:53.439-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hoa Hu - Siu Mu'/><title type='text'>Siu mu Sophie: "Ti bn sex vi gi 15.000 bng/gi"</title><content type='html'>&lt;a onblur="try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}" href="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/28/anderton-scan.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="float: left; margin: 0pt 10px 10px 0pt; cursor: pointer; width: 200px; height: 200px;" src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/28/anderton-scan.jpg" alt="" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Trong bui  ni chuyn vi truyn hnh Anh hm 27/9 va qua, siu mu nh m  Sophie Anderton  tit l i t ca mnh bng nhng cuc phiu lu  tnh i v thuc phin ht sc gy sc. C  tng bn 'sex' vi gi  15.000 bng Anh mt gi.&lt;/strong&gt;        &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Sophie,  32 tui l mt trong nhng ngi mu gy nhiu scandal nht trong gii  ngi mu hin nay. Khng ch gy sc vi li sng bung th ru v  cht gy nghin, Sophie cn c nhiu nhng scandal tnh i trong  c  sex l ni bt nht.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Khng mt cht  ngng ngng, ngi p scandal ny  tit l trn i truyn hnh Anh  v gii thi trang rng  b cun i cng vi cc c gi tham gia vo  nhng cuc chi try lc  trong  c c nhng ng nghip cng lm  ngi mu.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="Siu mu Sophie:  &amp;quot;Ti bn sex vi gi 15.000 bng/gi&amp;quot;, Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/28/sophie-anderton-scandal-15.jpg" width="470" height="368" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;Siu  mu nh Sophie Anderton&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cuc  phiu lu ca... sex&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Tr  thnh gi gi cao cp, v c ting tm trong nhiu scandal sex trn bo  ch, siu mu nh Sophie khng h ngng ngng hay che giu thn phn  ca mnh. Trong gii bui ni chuyn trn i truyn hnh Anh ngy hm  qua, Sophie  h l cuc i nhng cuc phiu lu tnh i ca mnh. C  khng nh rng, c l mt gi gi cao cp v tng bn dm vi gi  15.000 bng Anh cho mt ln.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;"Ti  khng che giu s thc ny. Ch trong mt thi gian ngn ti  bn  mnh  i li c nhn rt nhiu tin. Ti khng h t ho v iu  .&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;K v qu kh nh nhp ca  mt c gi lang thang: &lt;em&gt;"Ma h ca nm 2004 ti  ung rt nhiu,  phi mt mt chai ru vodka trong mt m v s dng cocaine c ban  ngy na.&lt;/em&gt; &lt;em&gt;Th rt tin mt ca ti  b hy v ti bit ti  rt cn tin lc ny&lt;/em&gt;, Sophie c gii thiu n mt lp hc   tr thnh gi gi cao cp.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width="490" align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;    &lt;tbody&gt;        &lt;tr&gt;             &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Siu mu Sophie: &amp;quot;Ti bn sex vi gi 15.000  bng/gi&amp;quot;, Thi trang, " style="width: 245px; height: 302px;" src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/28/sophie-anderton-sex-scandal-02.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;             &lt;td&gt;            &lt;p&gt;  &lt;img alt="Siu mu Sophie: &amp;quot;Ti  bn sex vi gi 15.000 bng/gi&amp;quot;, Thi trang, " style="width: 245px; height: 296px;" src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/28/sophie-anderton-sex-scandal-03.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;             &lt;/td&gt;        &lt;/tr&gt;    &lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt; Sophie lm ngi mu ni y cho nhn hiu La Senza.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt; tr thnh gi gi cao cp, Sophie   c mt ngi ng nghip t vn cho cch  thu ht nhng ngi n  ng giu c: &lt;em&gt;Ti c t vn cch n mc v trang im thnh mt  qu c xinh p v thnh t. H ni vi ti rng, ti phi mc nhng  chic vy thanh lch v tao nh, nhng phi tht gi cm. Khun mt lun  lun phi gi cho ln da c ti tn&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;"Ngi ph n t vn cho ti cn t ci gi kh cao,  khong 10.000 bng cho n 15.000 bng Anh mt ln i khch". &lt;/em&gt;Sophie  dnh phn ln thi gian cho vic kim c nhiu tin bng cch phi  mc nhng b qun o tht gi cm, i i giy cao gt tht quyn r v  nhng b vest thanh lch  thu ht nhng ngi n ng giu c.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;C k v ln u tin hnh ngh gi gi vi  mt ngi n ng: &lt;em&gt;Ti nh cm thy mnh b m trc ci ln u  tin y. Nhng ti t nh thm vi mnh rng ti ang b km kp; ti   bt taxi n khch sn Knightsbridge, pha Ty London v ln phng ca  mt ngi n ng. Ti c t to cho mnh mt v ngoi quyn r theo  cch ca mnh. Ti mc mt chic vy en  hiu ca Dolce &amp;amp;  Gabbana, i i giy cao gt 12cm hiu Louboutin. Ti trng kh nghim  tc v thnh t, theo nh cch thng thng ca v b ngoi.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width="490" align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;     &lt;tbody&gt;        &lt;tr&gt;            &lt;td colspan="2"&gt;&lt;img alt="Siu mu  Sophie: &amp;quot;Ti bn sex vi gi 15.000 bng/gi&amp;quot;, Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/28/sophie-anderton-scandal-11.jpg" width="470" height="392" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;        &lt;/tr&gt;        &lt;tr&gt;            &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Siu mu Sophie: &amp;quot;Ti bn sex vi gi 15.000 bng/gi&amp;quot;,  Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/28/sophie-anderton-scandal-10.jpg" width="245" height="196" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;            &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Siu mu Sophie:  &amp;quot;Ti bn sex vi gi 15.000 bng/gi&amp;quot;, Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/28/sophie-anderton-scandal-09.jpg" width="245" height="196" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;        &lt;/tr&gt;    &lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt; &lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;V p khiu gi ca Sophie&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ti  vo phng ca mt ngi n  ng. Ti ni vi ngi bn ca ti rng, ti rt gh tm nhng ngi n  ng bo v gi. Tuy vy, khi m ca ti li thy bt cng thng. Sau  40 pht ni chuyn, ti quyt nh thay i t th ng ca mnh khi  nhn vo chic vy en v tut n ra. Ti y ng ta ln ging trong  khi ng ta nhn ti mt cch hng hi. Ti nhm mt v nhanh chng ci  chic 'underwear' ca ng y. Ti t iu khin cm gic ca mnh v lm  rt nhanh. ng ta a cho ti chic th rt tin mt.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;"Ti tr v khch sn, ni ti ang   v t thng cho mnh bng cch vo phng tm th gin, nhm nhi thanh  socola, ung ru sm-panh v ngm nhng bng hoa. Nm di trn ging  vi chic qun lt t tin. Chng s lm hi lng nhng v khch kh  tnh nht".&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Sophie li nhanh  chng tm n mt thng gia ngi Anh giu c. C th l: &lt;em&gt;Ti   nhy mt vi anh ta, v anh ta ni vi ti rng: Sophie, ti sao mt c  gi p nh c li lm ci ngh ny? Ti khng th bit c &lt;/em&gt;ti  ni. &lt;em&gt;"Nhng 'sex' l mt ci g  tht m hoc, vo cc bui sng  ti thng dy rt sm, tm chic ti hiu Christian Dior v ly cun s  ghi chp. Ti ghi nhng ln bn thn ca mnh vo quyn s ny v s  tin m ti kim c.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;T ,  Sophie lun c cc triu ph yu mn. C tng quyn r c mt nh  vn ngi , ng l mt trong s cc triu ph ni ting ti chu u.  Theo quy lut, c ch qua m vi nhng thng gia giu c, nhng ngi  c th tr 20.000 bng Anh khi qua m vi c ti London.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="Siu mu Sophie: &amp;quot;Ti bn sex  vi gi 15.000 bng/gi&amp;quot;, Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/28/sophie-anderton-scandal-07.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;L ngi mu nh cho cc tp ch  n ng&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;C k v ngi  mt ngi n ng : &lt;em&gt;ng ta bo ph, v c nh mt rt dm ng.  Ti cm thy gh tm. Khun mt ca ng ta m m hi v i mt hau  hu, ging nh mt con mo ang rnh m ming bnh kem. Ln u tin,  ti cm thy nh ang lm "chuyn " vi mt cc tht vy.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Tuy nhin vi ngh gi gi, Sophie  kim  c kh nhiu tin, c tit l: &lt;em&gt;Ti tng ng vi 5 ngi n ng  v kim c hn 50.000 bng Anh. S tin ny ti ch yu dng  mua  thuc phin v tr tin thu phng.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;C ni:&lt;em&gt; Nh mt ngi mu, thn hnh ca bn c th v  nh mt mn hng. Ti  bt u ngh rng n c thanh ton bng 'sex'  th cng khng c s khc bit nhiu lm. &lt;/em&gt;V tit l thm: &lt;em&gt;Ti  khng c n khi i mt mnh trn con ng ny.  l con ng ti  tm bn cnh nhng ngi mu nh trn th gii. V cng c t nht 2  siu mu cng cng vi ti lao vo cuc chi ny.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="Siu mu Sophie: &amp;quot;Ti bn sex  vi gi 15.000 bng/gi&amp;quot;, Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/28/sophie-anderton-candal-12.jpg" width="470" height="392" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;9  tui dnh vo ma ty...&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;...  V s dng ma ty nm ln 9 tui&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Sophie cng rt trung thc khi ni v chuyn ring t:&lt;em&gt;  Ti sinh ra  l mt ngi nghin. Ln u tin ti chi thuc phin  vo nm ti 9 tui". &lt;/em&gt;Sophie  mt trinh tit t nm c ln 14 tui  v tr thnh mt c gi quan h ba bi. C chin thng trong mt cuc  thi ngi mu dng 'modelling' khi ln 15 tui v chuyn n London nm  17 tui.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;C k: &lt;em&gt;Ti ht thuc   mi ni, nht l khi m v, ti tng b 2 ngi n ng cng ot".&lt;/em&gt;  C tng k vi bn trai ca mnh rng  quan h tnh dc khi mi  &lt;span class="VietAdTextLink" id="link0" style="text-decoration: underline; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 1px; white-space: nowrap;"&gt;tui teen&lt;/span&gt;. Sophie ni: &lt;em&gt;Anh y  rt lo lng cho  ti. Anh gi ti l 'Sophie Trophy'. Anh tng lc vo mt ba tic sex  ca tui teen.  l mt ni nh nhp v bn thu. Ti c mt trong b  ba c gi v ti cng tht ng h thn v iu .&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ti tng cm gic mnh c bu. Ti s  hi bi mnh ang dng thuc phin, v vy ti  b sy thai. Ti khng  th lm g hn khi mi ch l mt c gi;&lt;/em&gt; &lt;em&gt;"Ti  tng iu  khin bn thn mnh. Ti c 'ng h' trong ti khon vi s tin  10.000 bng Anh cho mt ln i ch tnh dc. Ti phi tr t nht 20.000  bng Anh cho cocaine&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="Siu mu Sophie: &amp;quot;Ti bn sex vi gi 15.000 bng/gi&amp;quot;,  Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/28/sophie-anderton-sex-scandal-04.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;V l chn di nh m vi cc  scandal trn mt bo&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cuc  sng hin ti...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Sophie,  hin ang sng ti Chelsea, pha Ty London: &lt;em&gt;Vo nm 2007, ti mi  bt u thm nhp vo con ng gi gi. Ti b bt v kh nhiu cc t  bo  tch ly t liu v cuc sng ca ti. Tun trc, trn Thesun   ng ti mt clip ti ht thuc". &lt;/em&gt; l on bng t hi thng 7,  thc hin bi chnh ngi bn trai ca c Ed Buxton.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Sophie, cng tng hn h vi ngi sao bng   Mark Bosnich, c ni: &lt;em&gt; l mt khong thi gian di, t nng n  cho n khi phc hi li mi quan h. &lt;/em&gt;Nhng cui cng ti vn  mun  li tt c nhng ngi bn cnh ti  pha sau.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="Siu mu Sophie: &amp;quot;Ti bn sex  vi gi 15.000 bng/gi&amp;quot;, Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/28/sophie-anderton-scandal-18.jpg" width="470" height="368" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span&gt;Thi  trang vn l tnh yu ln i vi ti...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Thi trang vn l tnh yu ln i vi  ti, v ti  ln k hoch cho chng trnh &lt;span class="VietAdTextLink" id="link1" style="text-decoration: underline; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 1px; white-space: nowrap;"&gt;qung co&lt;/span&gt;  lt cho trang phc ng ph; "Hin ti  ang c bn trai mi v hy vng s c mt gia nh. Ti s lm tt c  mi th  chm dt vi cocaine. Ti bit  l mt con ng ti v ti  c th kit sc nu t b n.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;                 &lt;!-- qc ngu canh 1900 --&gt;            &lt;!-- qc ngu canh 1900 --&gt;&lt;p align="right"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Theo &lt;b&gt;24h.com.vn&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-3333760720914000859?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/3333760720914000859'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/3333760720914000859'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/09/sieu-mau-sophie-ban-sex-voi-gia-15000.html' title='Siu mu Sophie: &amp;quot;Ti bn sex vi gi 15.000 bng/gi&amp;quot;'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-4215779389405851229</id><published>2009-09-26T18:44:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:53.693-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><title type='text'>Hoa hu v nhng scandal... sc!</title><content type='html'>&lt;strong&gt;  ng sau nh ho quang, cc ngi p cn phi i mt vi d lun ca  cng chng. Nhng scandal xut pht t chnh hnh ng m h to ra... &lt;/strong&gt;         &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hoa hu Singapore b  nghi l less?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Rachel Kum  i din cho t nc Singapore tham d cuc thi hoa hu Hon v nm  2009 va qua ti Bahamas. C cng c bu chn l mt 3 ngi p (cng  vi Hoa hu Vit Nam v Philippin) ni tri nht cho khu vc chu   trong cuc thi ny.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width="490" align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;    &lt;tbody&gt;        &lt;tr&gt;            &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Hoa hu v nhng scandal... sc!, Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/27/Rachel-Kum-0902.jpg" width="245" height="329" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;            &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Hoa hu v nhng scandal...  sc!, Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/27/Rachel-Kum-0903.jpg" width="245" height="329" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;        &lt;/tr&gt;        &lt;tr&gt;            &lt;td colspan="2"&gt;&lt;img alt="Hoa hu v nhng scandal... sc!, Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/27/Rachel-Kum-Miss-Singapore-0.jpg" width="470" height="753" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;        &lt;/tr&gt;    &lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;Rachel Kum i din cho t nc  Singapore tham d cuc thi hoa hu Hon v nm 2009 vo thng 8 va qua  ti Bahamas&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Tuy nhin mt  trong nhng b mt ngoi i t ca ngi p Singapore ny  b dn  c mng bn tn by lu nay.  l nhng bc nh ht sc khim nh ca  ngi p ny  c pht hin ti mt din n. Bc nh Rachel Kum  chp chung vi mt vi c gi khc trong t th rt... khng bnh  thng.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width="490" align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;    &lt;tbody&gt;        &lt;tr&gt;            &lt;td colspan="2"&gt;&lt;img alt="Hoa hu v nhng scandal... sc!, Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/27/Rachel--Kum--Miss--Singapore-2602.jpg" width="470" height="307" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;        &lt;/tr&gt;        &lt;tr&gt;            &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Hoa hu v nhng scandal... sc!, Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/27/Rachel--Kum--Miss--Singapore-2601.jpg" width="245" height="327" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;            &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Hoa hu v  nhng scandal... sc!, Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/27/Rachel--Kum--Miss--Singapor.jpg" width="245" height="327" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;        &lt;/tr&gt;    &lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nhng bc nh khim nh trong din  n ca hoa hu Singapore b n thi l c b... less?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width="490" align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;     &lt;tbody&gt;        &lt;tr&gt;            &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Hoa hu v nhng  scandal... sc!, Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/27/1254016083_Rachel--Kum--Miss--Singapor.jpg" width="245" height="327" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;            &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Hoa hu v  nhng scandal... sc!, Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/27/Rachel-Kum-Miss--Singapore-.jpg" width="245" height="327" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;        &lt;/tr&gt;    &lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;Hai trong s bc nh rt khim nh  ca Hoa hu Singapore&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Ngi  hm m cho rng, c gi Rachel trong bc nh khim nh ny v hnh  chung  gy nh hng n hnh nh ca mt hoa hu. Nhiu comment cn  nghi ng rng c c vn  v gii tnh, nhn qua nhng bc nh tc tu  ca ngi p Singapore cng gy nhiu tranh ci. V phn ln cu hi  t ra cho ngi p ny vn cn b lng liu Rachael Kum c phi l mt  'lesbian'? &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hoa hu o  Rhode chp nh bn nuy trn tp ch Maxim&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Khng ch c hoa hu bang California (M)  Carrie Prejean lm xn xao d lun vi cu tr li phn i hn nhn  ng tnh gy nhiu tranh ci trong gii truyn thng. Carrie Prejean  cn b pht hin nhng bc nh nng bng m c chp trc   vp phi  nhiu s phn i ca cng chng vi cng v ca mt hoa hu bang.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="Hoa hu v nhng scandal... sc!,  Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/27/Alyssa_-Nude-_Maxim-0902.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="Hoa hu v nhng scandal... sc!,  Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/27/Alyssa_-Nude-_Maxim-0903.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;Alysha Castonguay - Hoa  hu o Rhode bn nuy trn tp ch Maxim&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Gp thm mt scandal na cho v chp nh  nuy, ngoi Carrie Prejean, cn c mt ngi p ca o Rhode, Alysha  Castonguay cng gy ch  bng nhng bc nh bn nuy trn tp ch n  ng ni ting Maxim. N chng c  ngha g c&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Tuy nhin Angie Beasley mt thnh vin trong ban gim kho  phn bc li rng: &lt;em&gt;Tt c cc c gi  rt thnh cng khi nh n  s ng h ca cng chng nhng t Top 15 tr i, ban gim kho l ngi  quyt nh kt qu cui cng. V cc th sinh, h phi c mt cch nhn  tng qut khi ng trn sn din h, phi th hin c ci p c v  ngoi hnh ln phm cht ca mnh&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="Hoa hu v nhng scandal... sc!, Thi trang, " src="http://media.tinmoi.vn/2009/09/27/Rachel--Christie-hoa-hau-Anh-05.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;Rachel Christie vinh d bc ln  ngi v n hong sc p Anh&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Khi  vo n top 15, cc bn khng th nh n nhng l  phiu bu ca cng chng, bn tht s phi l ngi &lt;span class="VietAdTextLink" id="link0" style="text-decoration: underline; rc la'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-8916212817425740845</id><published>2009-09-25T18:56:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:53.908-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hoa Hu - Siu Mu'/><title type='text'>Gi cm tng milimet</title><content type='html'>&lt;p class="pHead" align="justify"&gt;Mt gng mt gi l trang im p khi  i su vo tng chi tit: ln da, i mi, nh mt v chic mi...  ngi ta thy p v hon ho n tng milimet.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="pHead" align="justify"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;table style="border-collapse: separate;" width="40" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;  &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img style="border-width: 0px;" src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/77/t77259.jpg" alt="ep tng milimet" hyperlink="" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" class="lImage" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="pBody" align="justify"&gt;Mi  bn cng chng ti "rinh" v cho mnh mt vi "b kp" cng Quch An  An:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="pSubTitle" align="justify"&gt;MT&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="pBody" align="justify"&gt;Trc khi chai mascara, hy dng dng c un mi,  mascara, nu hoc trong s gip bn c mt hng mi t nhin v quyn r.  Cch s dng mascara: Lc u  mascara khng b vn cc, sau  vut  nh lng mi t trong ra ngoi.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="pBody" align="justify"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;table style="border-collapse: separate;" width="40" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img style="border-width: 0px;" src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/77/t77260.jpg" alt="ep tng milimet" hyperlink="" onclick="return showImage(this.src)" class="lImage" hspace="0" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="pBody" align="justify"&gt;Anh  mt la tm im cua gng mt. Mun co nhng ng vin m  mt sc sao, hay dung ch ke mt en, keo dai phn ui se  lam i mt tr nn c bit. Gn lng mi gia khi mi cua ban  qua ngn, khng c cong va tha. Mun mi nhn t nhin, ng  gn ca mi gia ln mt ma hay ct mi gia thanh tng ming  nho, dung keo gn ln phn mi  ui va gia m.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="pBody" align="justify"&gt;S dng contaclens khi bn mun gng mt  tht hon hao. Mu contaclens d chu thng l: nu, xm...&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="pBody" align="justify"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MI&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="pBody" align="justify"&gt;Mi ng  nht i vi cc chuyn gia trang im c l  l i mi cua ngi sao Angelina Jolie. Tuy nhin, nhng cp mi tri  cho y ch gp c  rt t ngi. Nu mi bn qu mong hoc hi  rng, hy n gian  to mt n ci chm chm bng cch dng ch ke  vin mi. Ke tht kho  ng vin khng qu th, lm i mi mt t  nhin. T son bng c v lm mn mi bng cch y c nh nhng, u tay   khe mi v phn khut bn trong mi. Nu mi bn y n, vn nn  dng ch  thu gn bng cch v vin mi nho li. Nn t son dng  nu da mi kh v nt. (Phn 2)</title><content type='html'>&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Tt nhin ni n ngh lm ngi mu l khng th khng nhc n nhng hp ng qung co, hp ng din show, hp ng vi cc tp ch thi trang... Tuy nhin,  tr thnh mt trong nhng ci tn ng u danh sch nhng siu mu giu c nht th gii khng ch da vo ngh chnh m cc ngi sao sn catwalk ny cn nh n ngh tay tri v cc yu t khch quan khc...&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Kate Moss - 8 triu la/1 nm&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Kate Moss, chn di ngi Anh ny c cho l mt trong nhng ngi mu c chiu cao khim tn, khng xinh p m li rt gy Tuy nhin, ngi Anh li c th t ho v c l mt siu mu duy nht c c tng vng v l ci tn th 3 trong danh sch nhng siu mu giu nht th gii nm 2009.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="490" align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;     &lt;tbody&gt;         &lt;tr&gt;             &lt;td colspan="2"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="8 triu /nm - Tin t u ra? Trong  c nhiu nh kha thn khi c   tui i mi. Bc nh gy tranh ci do Corrine Day chp cho Vogue nm 1993 - c ngi mu 19 tui mc qun lt, o hng khot su, bao quanh c l n nhp nhy - mang v 6.600 bng.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="8 triu /nm - Tin t u ra? Song b bi ca c qu ln, n ni sau khi cai nghin v, hp ng ca c li tng ln gp i.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Adriana Lima  8 triu  la/1 nm&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Adriana Lima - l mt trong s 10 "thin thn" ca nhn hiu  lt danh ting nc M Victoria's Secret. Vi chiu cao v v p ht hn siu mu ngi Brazil ny  rt thnh cng trong s nghip ngi mu ca mnh. Ch nh vo cc show din thi trang, qung co v k hp ng lm vic cng cc tp ch thi trang... l ngun chnh trong qu thu nhp ca mnh. Siu mu ny vn duy tr v tr th 4 trong cuc bnh chn ca Forbes nhng thu nhp ca c tng 1 triu  la so vi nm 2008.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="490" align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;     &lt;tbody&gt;         &lt;tr&gt;             &lt;td colspan="2"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="8 triu /nm - Tin t u ra? Khng ch thnh cng trn sn catwalk, chn di ny cn c lt vo top 100 ngi ph n gi cm nht th gii. Chng nhng vy m hu ht cc nhn hiu thi trang danh ting th gii lun chn c lm ngi mu qung co t gi cho h.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="490" align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;     &lt;tbody&gt;         &lt;tr&gt;             &lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="8 triu /nm - Tin t u ra? Ngoi ngh mu, Adriana cn lm qun l mt qun bar sang trng nht th gii vi tng ti sn tr gi 5 triu  la.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. Doutzen Kroes  6 triu  la/1 nm&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Doutzen Kroes - ngi p ngt ngo n t x s hoa tuy lip duy tr thu nhp 6 triu  la mi nm tnh t nm 2008, c xp th 5 trong cuc bnh chn ny. Doutzen Kroes, 23 tui, cao 1,78m l mt trong nhng siu mu t gi nht th gii hin nay, c l thin thn ca  lt Victoria's Secret, Bc chn vo sn din thi trang nm 2000, nhng ch sau 2 nm c  c mt trong cc chng trnh thi trang ln nh: Victoria"s Secret, Calvin Klein, Gucci, Escada, Dolce &amp;amp; Gabbana v Valentino.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="490" align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;     &lt;tbody&gt;         &lt;tr&gt;             &lt;td colspan="2"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="8 triu /nm - Tin t u ra? Doutzen lin tc c mt trn ba cc tp ch hng u th gii nh: Harpers Bazaar, Numero, Avant Garde v Vogue. (Phn 2)'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-3920629997683962575</id><published>2009-09-18T20:18:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:54.951-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hoa Hu - Siu Mu'/><title type='text'>Siu mu giu nht th gii kim tin t u? (Phn 1)</title><content type='html'>&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Ngoi vic s hu sc p tri ph, thn hnh hon ho n tng cm, cc siu mu cn da vo ti nng v tr c  vn ln tr thnh nhng ci tn ni ting trong lng mu th gii. Ly s ni ting lm im ta, khng t ngi trong s h u pht trin ngh tay tri v  cng l nhng ngh mang li khon thu khng l trong ti khon c nhn ca h...&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Mi bn hy cng chng ti tm hiu cch kim tin ca nhng siu mu giu nht th gii:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Siu mu Gisele Bundchen  25 triu  la/1 nm&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Lin tip ot ngi v qun qun trong bng danh sch nhng siu mu giu nht th gii, nhng thnh cng ca chn di gc Brazil l mt c gi p a ti. Ngi hm m khng khi sng st v cch kim tin d nh tr bn tay ca Gisele. Tuy nhin u tin khng th khng k n ngun thu nhp quan trong nht ca ngi p ny l t ngh lm mu:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="490" align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;     &lt;tbody&gt;         &lt;tr&gt;             &lt;td colspan="2"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Siu mu giu nht th gii kim tin t u? Gisele l ngi s hu nhiu bn hp ng hn bt k siu mu no trn hnh tinh.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;- Tng xut hin trn 500 ba bo, qung co cho hng trm nhn hiu thi trang nh: Christian Dior, Balenciaga, Dolce &amp;amp; Gabbana, Missoni, Versace, Cline, Givenchy, Bvlgari, Lanvin, Valentino, Ralph Lauren, Chlo, Michael Kors, Louis Vuitton, Victorias Secret v  tui 29, c vn l mt trong nhng siu mu t hng nht.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="490" align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;     &lt;tbody&gt;         &lt;tr&gt;             &lt;td colspan="2"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Siu mu giu nht th gii kim tin t u? Mi ln ra mt b su tp, siu mu ny u t mnh qung co cho mu sandal mi. Mi b su tp u c tung ra th trng khong 100 triu i, mi i sandal u c bn vi gi 17 euro tr ln v doanh s t c ln ti c t USD. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="490" align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;     &lt;tbody&gt;         &lt;tr&gt;             &lt;td colspan="2" style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Siu mu giu nht th gii kim tin t u? Cng vic ny n vi c cng rt tnh c. Bt u t u nm 2007 khi c bn ngi nh  Los Angeles c gn 4 triu USD, gp i gi mua trc . K t , vic kinh doanh bt ng sn ca c dng nh rt thun bum xui gi. Vo khong thng 9/2007, Gisele mua mt cn h khc  New York, sau khi sa sang li c  bn c vi gi 10.9 triu USD. Ngi ta ni rng, s d c c th lm n thun li nh vy l bi c nhng nh t vn rt gii, gip c c th u t ng ch. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Gisele Bundchen cn th hin r ti nng kinh doanh ca mnh khi mua li khch sn Palladium Executive ca mt thng gia  qu nh Brazil v tip nhn n vi cng v ch tch. Dng nh danh ting ca Gisele Bundchen chnh l im thu ht hng ngn khch du lch n min nam Brazil. H n thu phng  khch sn cng ch bi mong c c hi c ngm nhn b ch Gisele.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="490" align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;     &lt;tbody&gt;         &lt;tr&gt;             &lt;td colspan="2"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Siu mu giu nht th gii kim tin t u? Ngun thu ny, chn di dnh ht cho qu t thin ca mnh ti qu hng.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Heidi Klum  16 triu  la/1 nm&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt; qun ca bng xp hng nm nay l Heidi Klum. Siu mu ngi c d  c 3 con nhng vn v cng t s v kim c 16 triu USD trong vng 12 thng qua.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;- Heidi cn l ngi mu qung co ca nhn hiu  lt hng u th gii Victorias Secret. C cng l ngi mu qung co t gi ca hng lot nhn hiu ln nh Diet Coke, Volkswagen v ang lm n rt pht t vi dng sn phm chm sc da ca ring mnh mang tn In An Instant. Vy l so vi nm ngoi Heidi Klum c thu nhp nhiu hn 2 triu USD d  35 tui.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="490" align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;     &lt;tbody&gt;         &lt;tr&gt;             &lt;td colspan="2"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Siu mu giu nht th gii kim tin t u? (Phn 1), Thi trang, " src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-18/1253284468-Heidi-_Klum_sieu_mau_190906.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;         &lt;/tr&gt;     &lt;/tbody&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Heidi Klum trong nhng hot ng qung co cho nhn hiu thi trang danh ting ca M Victorias Secret&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;- Siu mu ngi c Heidi Klum cng nhanh chng theo bc Tyra Banks. Ngoi vic lm b ch ca hng lot chng trnh tm kim ngi mu trn truyn hnh nh "Germanys Next Top Model", bng hng nc c ny cn tham gia chng trnh truyn hnh thc t mang tn Project Runway trn i truyn hnh Bravo nhn c nhiu li khen v va c  c gii Emmy.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;- S nghip kinh doanh ca c cng bt u t thi trang. Dy sn phm trang phc ca Klum (c c trang phc cho tr s sinh) c bit nhiu ti c vi ci tn "Otto", c catalog v t hng qua mng Internet. C cng thit k giy cho thng hiu Birkenstock, n trang cho Mouawad v  tm trong Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue nm 2002...&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="490" align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;     &lt;tbody&gt;         &lt;tr&gt;             &lt;td colspan="2"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Siu mu giu nht th gii kim tin t u? (Phn 1), Thi trang, " src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-18/1253284468-Heidi-_Klum_sieu_mau_190902.jpg" width="490" height="368" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;         &lt;/tr&gt;         &lt;tr&gt;             &lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Siu mu giu nht th gii kim tin t u? (Phn 1), Thi trang, " style="width: 245px; height: 360px;" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-18/1253284468-Heidi-_Klum_sieu_mau_190909.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;             &lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Siu mu giu nht th gii kim tin t u? (Phn 1), Thi trang, " style="width: 245px; height: 342px;" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-18/1253283489-Heidi-_Klum_sieu_mau_190904.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;         &lt;/tr&gt;     &lt;/tbody&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Siu mu ngi c Heidi Klum lun nng bng trong trang phc ni y&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;- B su tp n trang Mouawad do c thit k ln u tin xut hin trong chng trnh bn hng qua mng ca QVC vo ngy 14/9/2006 c sc thu ht c bit. 14 trong s 16 mu c bn ht trong 35 pht rao bn. C cng sn xut nc hoa vi tn Heidi. Heidi cn chng t mt ti nng khc him c  cc ngi p khi nhiu bc tranh ca c xut hin trn cc tp ch m thut ti M.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;- Thu nhp hng thng ca c hin nay l 7 triu  la, cha k "s hu" i chn ngc ng tr gi 1,9 triu  la. Ngoi ra, c cn ng phim, l i din ca hng Victoria's Secret v l ch nhn ca mt thng hiu giy dp, trang sc v nc hoa.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Siu mu giu nht th gii kim tin t u? (Phn 1), Thi trang, " src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-18/1253283489-Heidi-_Klum_sieu_mau_190908.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;i chn ngc ng tr gi 1,9 triu  la ca Heidi Klum&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;- D ang trong thi gian mang bu nhng nhng hnh nh ca Heidi Klum lun xut hin mi lc mi ni trn cc trang ba tp ch v l b bu t gi cho cc thng hiu thi trang dnh cho b bu. ng thi, c cng c mi k hp ng qung co cho cng ty sn xut  chi tr em.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-3920629997683962575?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/3920629997683962575'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/3920629997683962575'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/09/sieu-mau-giau-nhat-gioi-kiem-tien-tu-au.html' title='Siu mu giu nht th gii kim tin t u? (Phn 1)'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-2881959686052124285</id><published>2009-09-18T20:17:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:54.984-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hoa Hu - Siu Mu'/><title type='text'>Nhng lp ren mng cung si</title><content type='html'>&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Lingerie - thng hiu  lt, o ng hng u th gii bao nm qua  lm say m bit bao c gi bi s ngt ngo, quyn r n tt  ca cc thit k thi trang m h to ra.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Mng manh nh sng mai, mm mi nh hi th, nhng lp ren y  l th gia v hon ho cho mi cuc phiu lu tnh i ca bit bao i tnh nhn.  Vi phi p,  lt khng cn n thun  'bo v' nhng 'im nng' trn c th m n chnh l mn 'v kh' ho hng  h gc bt c chng trai no.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;V hn ai ht, nhng nh thit k ca Lingerie hiu r mong mun y ca cc c gi tr. Bng nhng cht liu truyn thng dnh ring cho  lt  nh voan, la, sa tin, ren v c li... h  thi vo b su tp nhng 'gc nhn' mi m, to bo m quyn r n m hn.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Khng i hi bn phi c thn hnh hon ho, hay nhng ng cong no trn nh n thn, Lingerie s 'gii ta' nhng ni nim rt ph n bng cc thit k kho lo ca mnh.&lt;/p&gt;
