Da vo nhng tiu ch ny, trang tin Complex.com  cng b danh sch 9 ngi p gi cm c tm nh hng nht trong s hng triu ph n Vit, trong s  c cc ngi p gc Vit...&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Nh Loan&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Sinh nm 1981, sang M khi c mi 11 tui, xut hin ln u trong VCD Thy Nga 62 v mi y nht l show trnh din Paris By Night. &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. &lt;a target="_blank" href="http://www.24h.com.vn/news/detail/78/251098/Bom-sex-goc-Viet-lo-vet-thuong-bi-ban-trai-danh.24h"&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;Tila Tequila&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; Maggie Q&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Tn tht l L M K, sinh nm 1979, sinh trng ti M, c c b l ngi Ba Lan, m l ngi Vit Nam. Sau khi tt nghip trung hc, c n Nht Bn v Trung Quc  lm ngi mu kim tin. Nm 1998, c nhn c vai u tin ca mnh trong mt b phim truyn hnh Trung Quc, t  c khi nghip lm din vin.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="490" align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;     &lt;tbody&gt;         &lt;tr&gt;             &lt;td colspan="2"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="9 ngi p SEXY nht Vit Nam, h l ai?, Thi trang, " src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-16/1253059804-Maggie-_Q_160904.jpg" width="490" height="329" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;         &lt;/tr&gt;         &lt;tr&gt;             &lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="9 ngi p SEXY nht Vit Nam, h l ai?, Thi trang, " src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-16/1253059670-Maggie-_Q_160902.jpg" width="245" height="334" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;             &lt;td&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="9 ngi p SEXY nht Vit Nam, h l ai?, Thi trang, " src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-09-16/1253059670-Maggie-_Q_160903.jpg" width="245" height="334" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;         &lt;/tr&gt;     &lt;/tbody&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Maggie Q tn tht l L M K&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7. &lt;a target="_blank" href="http://www.24h.com.vn/news/detail/78/235253"&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;Nguyn Thy Lm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;L HH Hon v Vit Nam nm 2008, sinh nm 1987 ti Thi Bnh. Thy Lm  lt vo top 15 ngi p nht Hoa hu hon v th gii nm 2008 t chc ti Nha Trang. C tng l ca s chnh trong nhm ht Thin Thn, dn chng trnh Vui cng Hugo trn TH H Ni v  tham gia cc phim: ng i, i v pha mt tri, Tr a ca s phn. Nm 2007, do c "gng mt xinh xn v vn din 'kha kh' trong in nh", Hong Thy Linh c chn vi vai chnh Vng Anh trong phn 2 chng trnh truyn hnh tng tc Nht k Vng Anh vn c nhiu ngi trong gii tr hm m.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Thng 10 nm 2007, Hong Thy Linh dnh vo v scandal khi mt on phim quanh cnh quan h tnh dc gia c v bn trai b mt nhm ngi pht tn v lan truyn ln mng Internet t ngy 12/10. V b bi ny  gy xn xao trong d lun trong nc v c c bo ch nc ngoi quan tm (Anh, M ...) v c cho l ngi c tm nh hng nht trong gii tr t trc n nay.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="490" align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1"&gt;  bi, Thi trang, " onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2008-01-02/khanhht1.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align="justify"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:85%;"&gt;Vi kiu dng cun ht v cht liu sang trng nhng mu ni y di y c thit k va phi, khng qu ph trng, nhng vn lm ni bt ln ng nt c th hon ho. B su tp ch yu xoay quanh dng o ngc c gng y, khin cho vng mt ca phi p trng y n v hp dn hn, ng b cng qun chip quai mnh hon ton bng ren vi nhiu ha tit v mu sc an xen, lun thu ht c s ch  ca ngi khc gii.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align="justify"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:85%;"&gt;Hy  nhng b ni y gp phn em n cho bn v p hon ho hn trong mt chng, bn nh!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align="center"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" alt="V&amp;#7867; &amp;#273;&amp;#7865;p ho&amp;#224;n h&amp;#7843;o quy&amp;#7871;n r&amp;#361; h&amp;#417;n trong &amp;#273;&amp;#7891; l&amp;#243;t,  lt - Siu Mu'/><title type='text'>B quyt n t "phin bn" hp dn!</title><content type='html'>&lt;p align="justify"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:85%;"&gt;Khi nhng m xun m p v lng mn tr li, y cng l khonh khc y  ngha  cc nh thit k tn dng khi tung ra nhng trang phc  lt mi, hp dn hn dnh tng cho phi p. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align="justify"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:85%;"&gt;m hng ca ma xun lan ta trong tng thit k, t nhng kiu cch to nt mm mi v trn y, nhng gam mu cng ha trn mt cch ngu hng, u to cm gic ti mi v nng bng hn rt nhiu. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align="justify"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:85%;"&gt;Song song cng ng nt tinh t, nhng im nhn c ch nh, khoe ra v p cng trn ca c th,  khin b su tp nh c thng hoa v c sc thuyt phc v cng ln vi bt k ai nu c chim ngng. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align="justify"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:85%;"&gt;Hy tn hng nhng giy pht y cht th vi b su tp  lt ca Aliser, bn s cm thy mnh ng yu hn rt nhiu trong nhng m xun dng trn cm xc ca nhng hng v ngt ngo v m say. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;table id="table1" width="415" border="0" cellpadding="2"&gt;  &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;   &lt;td&gt;   &lt;img class="news-image" style="cursor: pointer;" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-02-04/1233716490-dolot4309_01.jpg" alt="B&amp;#237; quy&amp;#7871;t &amp;#273;&amp;#7871;n t&amp;#7915; &amp;quot;phi&amp;#234;n b&amp;#7843;n&amp;quot; h&amp;#7845;p d&amp;#7851;n!,  lt - Siu Mu'/><title type='text'>By tnh hon ho!</title><content type='html'>&lt;p align="justify"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:85%;"&gt;Vi mu sc ch o l hng, tm, en l nhng tng mu khi gi nhiu nim am m v nhng cm xc ngt ngo nht. Thm vo  l nhng ha tit da bo v k ca-r tr trung, b su tp  lt v  bi ny khng nhng thuyt phc c s la chn ca phi p, m n cn l mt ci "by tnh" hon ho dnh cho cc c lang qun m h yu thng. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align="justify"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:85%;"&gt;S mi m trong thit k vi nhng ng gn ni chy dc trn thn o, nhng nt thu hoa mm mi, nhng chic dy nh bao bc quanh thn hnh nng bng... hay iu  trong nhng chic n nh xinh cng khin b su tp to nn mt sc ht huyn b v y uy lc. &lt;p align="justify"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:85%;"&gt;Nh  ngi ta thng ni "Khng c ngi ph n xu ch c ngi ph n khng bit  lm p cho mnh". &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 300px; height: 380px;" src="http://img36.imageshack.us/img36/5106/masteringactivedirector.jpg" alt="" border="0" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Find all the information you need to manage and maintain Active Directory in &lt;i&gt;Mastering Active Directory for Windows Server 2008&lt;/i&gt;, an in-depth guide updated with over 300 pages of new material. Revised to address the new components, enhancements, and capabilities brought by Windows Server 2008 to the directory services, this book covers domain name system design, Active Directory forest and domain design, maintaining organizational units, managing group policy, implementing best practices, and more. Expect high-level coverage of the new version of Microsoft's powerful user authentication and authorization tool, fully updated for Windows Server 2008.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Tm tt c cc thng tin bn cn  qun l v duy tr Active Directory trong Mastering Active Directory cho Windows Server  2008, mt trong ti liu hng dn su cp nht vi hn 300 trang ti liu mi. Sa i n a ch cc thnh phn mi, ci tin, v kh nng a ra bi Windows Server 2008 n cc dch v th mc, cun sch ny bao gm thit k h thng tn min, rng Active Directory v min thit k, duy tr cc n v t chc, qun l chnh sch nhm, thc hin thc hnh tt nht, v nhiu hn na . Ti mun mnh trau di tht nhiu  bc vo lnh vc MC mt cch nghim tc, bn cnh vic pht trin cng vic ca mt ngi mu, MC cng l mt mng cng vic th v m ti   t lu, siu mu Phng Mai tit l.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;L th sinh duy nht i din cho Vit Nam lt vo top 10 siu mu chu  nm nay, vinh d ny  gip Phng Mai n nhn thm nhiu c hi mi trong lnh vc ngh thut. Nhng li mi din show, chp nh, ng phim dn dp trong thi gian ny cng khin c siu mu thng minh tt bt hn.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Nhanh chng "nhp vai" cng kip Shoot Studio ca o din hnh nh T Thanh Tn trong nhng bc hnh y gi cm, mi bn cng 24H chim ngng v p trn y ca c siu mu vn  tui "teen" ny.&lt;/p&gt; font-family: Arial;"&gt;&lt;span style="color:#3f3f3f;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Mi tc vng ng , i mi  mng v din b bikini bt mt, Lilo li khin fan hm m vui mng trc nhng thay i tch cc ca c nng.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"&gt;&lt;span style="color:#3f3f3f;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:85%;"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 468px; height: 414px;" alt="" src="http://vtc.vn/media/vtcnews/2009/09/07/1_26.jpg" vspace="3" border="1" hspace="3" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 32, 96); font-family: Arial;" align="middle"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Lindsay Lohan quyn r vi hnh nh bn b bi.&lt;/i&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Lindsay Lohan gn y ngy cng i xung trong s nghip, i t th gp nhiu rc ri v tnh trng th gia ng t gnh. Dng nh c qu nhiu iu khng may mn n vi ngi p ny, v vy, khi Lilo xut hin cun ht trong b bikini mu trng khoe hnh th cn i, mi ngi cho rng y chnh l mt chiu ca c nng  gy s ch , cu vn tn tui ang ngy cng km ni ca mnh.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;" lang="VI"&gt;N din vin xinh p dnh thi gian rnh  th gin bn b bi ti khch sn &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"&gt;Sunset Marquis, Hollywood, th thi nm cnh b bi vi i knh mt, dng nh Lilo ang mun qun i nhng kh khn v ni bun m thi gian gn y c nng gp phi.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:85%;"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 468px; height: 529px;" alt="" src="http://vtc.vn/media/vtcnews/2009/09/07/2_11.jpg" vspace="3" border="1" hspace="3" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 32, 96); font-family: Arial;" align="middle"&gt;&lt;i&gt;c bit, mi y ngi p nhum tc vng  "bt chc" hnh nh ca thn tng Marilyn Monroe. &lt;/i&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Lindsay khng cn xut hin vi mu da loang l na, c nng  mu da t nhin ca mnh ch khng nhum nu. So vi thi gian mi chia tay vi ngi tnh Sam, Lilo trng khe mnh v bo hn rt nhiu. Ngi p cng chm cht hnh nh xut hin trc cng chng ca mnh hn, nhng c l Lilo cn phi n lc hn rt nhiu  mt ln na li ta sng nh mt ngi sao thnh cng rc r trong s nghip ch khng th n gin ch l mn khoe v p hnh th nh th ny.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:85%;"&gt;&lt;img style="width: 468px; height: 811px;" alt="" src="http://vtc.vn/media/vtcnews/2009/09/07/3_5.jpg" vspace="3" border="1" hspace="3" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0, 32, 96); font-family: Arial;" align="middle"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Lilo  mu da nguyn bn nn trng c khng cn "loang l" na.&lt;/i&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;b&gt;Dim H&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; sang vi chm nh cc k bt mt trong b su tp &lt;a href="http://vatgia.com/1153/do-boi-nu.html" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;b&gt;o tm&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt; mt m.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="pbody1" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial;"&gt;&lt;span style="color:#000000;"&gt;Brooklyn Decker n vi nghip ngi mu t cch y 6 nm lc mi 16 tui, trong mt dp tnh c khi c b ang i trn ph Charlotte, Bc Carolina.&lt;span style=""&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;st1:place st="on"&gt;C nng &lt;/st1:place&gt; nhanh chng tr thnh ngi mu c ting ti M ngay sau . &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="pbody1" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt; &lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"&gt; &lt;div align="center"&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Chn di Brooklyn Decker nng bng cng bikini" src="http://image.tin247.com/vtc/090217062118-172-698.jpg" name="imagePhoto" width="450" border="1" /&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td class="Image" align="left"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p class="pbody1" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;"&gt; tui 22 nhng thnh tch Brooklyn Decker  to dng c tht ng k. C  xut hin trn rt nhiu tp ch tn tui nh Teen Vogue, FHM, Glamour, Cosmopolitan, Elle Girl, Spin v trn Sports Illustrated. Ngoi ra  c cn l ngi mu ca cc bng &lt;a href="http://vatgia.com/1033/bat-dia.html" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;b&gt;a&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ca nhc cho Jimmy Buffett v 3 Doors Down.  V y cng l ln th 4 c c tp ch o tm danh ting nht hnh tinh mi xut hin trn n phm c bit ca mnh.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;p class="pbody1" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt; &lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="pbody1" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"&gt;Song song vi vic lm ngi mu, Brooklyn Decker cn ht tin nh cc hp ng qung co vi nhng thng hiu danh ting nh Gap, Victoria's Secret, American Eagle, J. C. Penney, Hollister. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="pbody1" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt; &lt;div align="center"&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Chn di Brooklyn Decker nng bng cng bikini" src="http://image.tin247.com/vtc/090217062119-162-476.jpg" name="imagePhoto" width="450" border="1" /&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td class="Image" align="left"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;p class="pbody1" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="pbody1" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; M hin nay.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="pbody1" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt; trong s ny u l nhng "chn di" tn tui.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="giaitri" align="justify"&gt;Vi i hnh xut qun ton cc ngi p nh th ny (thi u thin v tn cng vi 4 tin v, 3 tin o) th khng r cc WAG s chi bng nh th no, nhng chc chn l ngi xem s c dp so snh nhng v p khc nhau ca mi mt bng hng  i hnh "c bit" ny.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Th mn Alena Seredova, hoa hu Cng ho Czech nm 1998 (b x ca th thnh s mt T Italia v CLB Juventus, Gianluigi Buffon).&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; Vi kinh nghim tng tr thnh ngi mu c quyn ca Tommy Hilfiger v Burberry cng nh tng xut hin trn cc trang ba tp ch danh ting, Esti  th hin xut sc vai tr ca mnh trong hnh nh mt nng tin c trn Sports Illustrated. B nh c thc hin ti Naples, Italy qua ng knh ca nhip nh gia Randall Grant.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="giaitri"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"&gt; vi vy ng'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-231592209317168656</id><published>2009-09-01T01:42:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:52:59.134-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hot Girl - Scandal'/><title type='text'>Ngi mu Playboy x Hn tr li tht nng trn Maxim</title><content type='html'>Ngi mu Playboy u tin ca x Hn Lee Pani xut hin trong b nh kh nng trn tp ch Maxim (Hn Quc), s thng 9/2009. Lee Pani va c mt thi gian di  n  chun b cho k hoch pht hnh album ca nhc.  &lt;span id="ctl14_ltrContent" class="bodyContent"&gt;&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;Lee Pani gia nhp lng ngi mu nh ca Hn Quc t khi cn tr nhng c ch thc s ni ting vo nm 2006 sau khi ginh chin thng trong cuc thi tm kim ngi mu ca tp ch Playboy ti Hn Quc. Sau chin thng bt ng ny, Lee Pani cn c c hi ti M, hc tp v tham gia show chp hnh qung co cho cp bng  th gii ti c nm 2006.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt; &lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;Nm 2007, Lee Pani tuyn b lp gia nh vi bp trng ca mt qun n Nht Bn. K t khi kt hn, Lee Pani quyt nh rt khi sn din, quay v chm lo hnh phc gia nh. Sau 18 thng chung sng vi ngi n ng h Cho ny, Lee Pani tuyn b  n ly d. u nm 2009, bo gii Hn Quc a tin, ngi p ny quyt nh s th sc trong lnh vc ca ht.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt; l mt gng mt quen thuc vi nhng cuc bnh chn sc p cn Katy Perry, Blake Lively, Vanessa Hudgens l nhng ci tn rt mi.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt; &lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt; Phng Mai cn ni bt vi kh nng giao tip tt bng ting Anh. Tr v vi sch v v ging ng i hc, Phng Mai vn tranh th tham gia chp mu, ng phim  c tha sc th hin mnh trn con ng ngh thut. Ch Thanh Hng, Gim c truyn thng Cng ty CP Thi trang Honey tm s: Phng Mai thc s l mt ngi mu chuyn nghip v rt yu ngh. Chng kin Mai lm vic ht mnh trong bui chp hnh loa Edifier ti Mai s cn tin xa trn sn catwalk. Mi ln to dng cho mt khun hnh l mt ln Phng Mai cng -kp tnh ton, cn nhc sao cho th hin tht c o ci ti ngi mu khi chp hnh. Phng Mai thc s  thi c tnh tinh nghch, hn nhin v tinh t ca mnh khi phiu vi  lt Honey. Chnh v vy, ti rt t ho  tng ti tr bikini cho Phng Mai v cc th sinh Vit Nam tham gia cuc th siu mu Chu  2009  va qua. Trong thi gian ti, chc chn vi phong cch din chuyn nghip v dy dn kinh nghim, Phng Mai s cn c nhiu b thi trang  lt,  bi Honey tht n tng.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-08-25/1251165109-ca-tinh-voi-honey-1.jpg" alt="Siu mu chu  Phng Mai c tnh vi  lt Honey,  lt -  bi, Thi trang, " /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; Ngi trc  l Brbara Palacios, sau khi ng quang Hoa hu quc gia nm 1986 cng  tr thnh Hoa hu Hon v cng nm. nh: &lt;em&gt;Missvenezuela&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/tbody&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/2B/14/ste2-bellezavenezolana.jpg" alt="" width="312" border="1" height="544" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Hai mn th thao s trng ca c l tennis v bi. nh: &lt;em&gt;Missvenezuela&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/tbody&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/2B/14/ste8-foro.jpg" alt="" width="400" border="1" height="600" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Nu Hoa hu tin nhim Dayana Mendoza &lt;a href="http://vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/Hoa-hau/2008/07/3BA045AB/"&gt;tng b bt cc&lt;/a&gt;, th b ca Stefania l Carlos Fernndez cng  b bn xu bt cc trong 5 ngy, ti Barinas, Venezuela, hi nm 2005. nh: &lt;em&gt;Missvenezuela&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/tbody&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/2B/14/ste5-ap.jpg" alt="" width="382" border="1" height="480" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Stefania Fernandez ti cuc thi Hoa hu Hon v. C hin l sinh vin ngnh quan h quc t. nh: &lt;em&gt;AP&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/tbody&gt; &lt;/table&gt;   &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/2B/14/ste3-mu.jpg" alt="" width="369" border="1" height="526" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Trong b o tm ng phc ca Miss Universe. nh: &lt;em&gt;MU&lt;/em&gt;. &lt;p&gt;Stefania Fernandez  Miss Universe 2009  nm nay 18 tui, cao 1,78 m. C l ngi p mang nhiu dng mu: Nga, Ukraine, Galicia v Ba Lan. Trc khi tr thnh N hong sc p th gii, Stefania  ng quang Hoa hu Hon v Venezuela vo thng 9/2008. Ti cuc thi ny, ngoi vng min, c cn ot cc gii ph: Hoa hu Thanh lch, Hoa hu c gng mt p nht, Hoa hu c hnh th p nht.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/2A/C6/to-miss-2.jpg" alt="" width="480" border="1" height="323" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Hoa hu Stefania Fernandez bt ng vi chin thng. nh: &lt;em&gt;AP.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/tbody&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;p&gt;Ti Miss Universe 2009, i din n t vng quc sc p c ch  ngay t u cuc thi. Tuy trang phc d hi ca Stefania khng phi l mt thit k xut sc, thm ch b nhiu khn gi nhn xt l trng ging nh mt cy chi qut nh, nhng c gy n tng tt trong phn thi o tm vi chiu cao ni bt v thn hnh l tng. Stefania cn to c v quyn r ring cho mnh khi thng xuyn dng mu son  ni bt trong sut qu trnh din ra cuc thi.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/2A/C6/a610x-top-5.jpg" alt="" width="495" border="1" height="280" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Top 5 ngi p ca cuc thi. nh: &lt;em&gt;Reuters.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/tbody&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;p&gt;Trong m chung kt,  phn thi ng x, Stefania nhn c cu hi:  nhiu ni trn th gii, ph n vn gp phi nhiu tr ngi trn bc ng chinh phc mc tiu ca mnh. Theo bn, h cn phi lm g  vt qua nhng tr ngi ? Ngi p khng nh: Hin nay phi n chng ti  vt qua rt nhiu tr ngi v t c s pht trin ngang hng vi nam gii. Chng ta phi nhn ra rng, s khng cn khong cch gia hai gii na.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/2A/C6/ha441889.jpg" alt="Tn Hoa hu Miss Universe 2009." width="464" border="1" height="700" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Tn Hoa hu Stefania Fernandez. nh: &lt;em&gt;Misso.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/tbody&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;p&gt;Tn Hoa hu nhn c chic vng min mi mang tn Ha bnh v n trang kim cng hiu Diamond Nexus Labs, lng mt nm lm Hoa hu, hc bng tr gi 100.000 USD cho kha hc din xut ti Hc vin in nh New York, c ti tr trang phc v chuyn n sng ti New York.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Vi vng min Miss Universe m Stefania Fernandez va t c, Venezuela li &lt;a href="http://vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2008/12/3BA097BA/"&gt;tng thm khong cch&lt;/a&gt; vi cc nc v thnh tch ti nhng cuc thi nhan sc th gii. Hin ti, quc gia ny  c 5 Hoa hu Th gii, 6 Hoa hu Hon v v 5 Hoa hu Quc t.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="286" align="right" bgcolor="#efefef" border="1" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td colspan="2"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;im phn thi o tm ca top 10&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td width="130"&gt;- Australia: 9,264 &lt;p&gt;- Dominica: 9,189&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;- Kosovo: 8,790&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;- Venezuela: 8,760&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;- Php: 8,640&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;- Thy S: 8,611 &lt;p&gt;- Puerto Rico: 8,533&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;- Nam Phi: 8,460&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;- CH Czech: 8,350&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;- M: 8,060&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/tbody&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;p&gt;Khng qu bt ng, Ada Aimee De la Cruz  ngi p tng lt vo top 16 Miss World 2007   bc ln mt nh cao mi trn con ng chinh phc cc cuc thi nhan sc ca c vi danh hiu  hu 1 Miss Universe 2009. Khng phi l mt sc p ni tri, nhng Hoa hu Kosovo Gona Dragusha tng bc vo n chung kt v ot ngi  hu 2 vi gng mt thanh t, phng pht v p ph n Trung  v s u t k lng cho cc phn thi trang phc dn tc, trang phc o tm.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;c k vng s tr thnh Jennifer Hawkins (Hoa hu Hon v 2004) th hai ca Australia nhng Rachael Finch, n MC duyn dng, ch dng li vi ngi  hu 3. Ngi p Puerto Rico ng cui top 5 vi danh hiu  hu 4.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/2A/C6/ausda-hoi-to.jpg" alt="Hoa hu Australia trong trang phc d hi." width="400" border="1" height="643" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Hoa hu Australia trong trang phc d hi. nh: &lt;em&gt;Reuters&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/tbody&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;p&gt;Ngoi 5 th sinh bc tip vo vng ng x, top 10 cuc thi cn c: Nam Phi, CH Czech, M, Php, Thy S. Trc , top 15 c s gp mt ca Miss Albania, B, Thy in, Iceland, Croatia.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/2A/C6/athia.jpg" alt="" width="495" border="1" height="397" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Ngi p Thi Lan vi danh hiu Hoa hu n nh. nh: &lt;em&gt;Reuters.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/tbody&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;p&gt;Vi s chim u th ca chu u v chu M, khu vc chu  nm nay tht th d c nh gi l c nhiu gng mt sng gi. Khng mt i din no lt vo top 15. Ngi p Thi Lan v Trung Quc tr thnh nim an i cho chu  khi ot 2 gii ph. Danh hiu Hoa hu Thanh lch, do cc th sinh bnh chn, thuc v Miss Trung Quc. i din Thi Lan ginh gii Hoa hu n nh do khn gi bnh chn qua Internet. &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"&gt;Chia s vi &lt;em&gt;VnExpress.net&lt;/em&gt; trong thi gian din ra m chung kt, V Hong Yn cho bit, c khng qu bun, khng tht vng, ch cm thy hi ngc nhin trc s mt ma ca chu &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; trong u trng sc p nm nay. D kin, Yn cng on Vit Nam s v nc trong vi ngy ti.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/2A/C6/rico1-ap.jpg" alt="Hoa hu CH Czech - mt trong nhng ng vin ca vng min. nh: Misso." width="400" border="1" height="654" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Hoa hu Puerto Rico lt vo top 5. nh: &lt;em&gt;AP&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/tbody&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;p&gt;Xut hin trn sn khu trong chic vy tm tha tht t u m chung kt, ng kim Hoa hu Dayana Mendoza chia s, khonh khc ng quang ti Vit Nam nm 2008 l giy pht p nht cuc i c. Trong giy pht chuyn ngi, ngi p tr li trong chic vy di trng. Khi tn tn Hoa hu c xng ln, Dayana sung sng m chm ly ngi ng hng n ni  nh ri vng min. y l ln th hai, Dayana trao vng min cho Stefania. Ln th nht l trong m chung kt Hoa hu Hon v Venezuela ti qu nh ca h.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/2A/C6/a-trung-quoc.jpg" alt="" width="495" border="1" height="391" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Ngi p Trung Quc Wang Jingyao nhn danh hiu Hoa hu Thanh lch. nh: &lt;em&gt;Reuters&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/tbody&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;p&gt;Hoa hu Hon v l cuc thi sc p quc t thng nin c hng Pacific Mills, M sng lp t nm 1952. Bt u t 1996, Miss Universe thuc quyn s hu ca t ph &lt;a href="http://vnexpress.net/topic/donald-trump"&gt;Donald Trump&lt;/a&gt;. Nm nay, cuc thi quy t 84 th sinh t khp ni trn th gii. Tuy nhin, ngay trc m chung kt, Miss Turks &amp;amp; Caicos  ngi p thp nht cuc thi   phi &lt;a href="http://vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/Hoa-hau/2009/08/3BA12A91/"&gt;rt lui&lt;/a&gt; v l do sc khe.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cu tr li ng x ca top 5 Miss Universe&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;- &lt;strong&gt;Hoa hu CH Dominica&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cu hi  &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"&gt;Tamara Tunie&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;: Theo t chc Y t Th gii WHO, xt nghim HIV cn c tin hnh khn trng trn ton th gii. Bn ngh sao?&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"&gt;Tr li&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: Ti chc chn tin rng vic kim tra HIV cn c tin hnh mt cch bt buc v nu n khng c thc hin k lng th ch trong mt pht giy, chng ta s mt i mt mng ngi.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Hoa hu Australia:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cu hi  &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"&gt;Valeria Mazza&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; Ti nay, bn  mc o tm  ban gim kho chm im. Nhng  mt s nc, ph n khng c php mc trang phc ny. Bn ngh sao?&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"&gt;Tr li&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: Ti tin rng, mc o tm, c bit trong mt cuc thi sc p, l iu tuyt vi. Hy cho chng ti c hi  ph din v p hnh th  v p m chng ti  phi luyn tp vt v mi c c. Ti ngh, thn hnh l mt trong nhng b phn p nht ca ngi ph n. Chng ta chc chn nn ph by cho c th gii c chim ngng.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Hoa hu Puerto Rico: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"&gt;Cu hi  Riyo Mori&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: Sc p khin bn gp nhiu thun li hn trong cuc sng, hay n gy tr ngi cho bn nu mun c mi ngi nh gi mt cch cng bng, nghim tc trong cng vic?&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"&gt;Tr li&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: Ti ngh sc p l mn qu tng. Ngi s hu sc p phi c chun b tt, phi c hc hnh bi bn, chuyn nghip. Qua , v p bn trong s c th hin ra bn ngoi. iu  gii thch v sao, mi ngi s nhn nhn ti mt cch nghim tc, cng bng trong cng vic.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Hoa hu Kosovo:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"&gt;Cu hi  Dean Cain&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: Ngi sao nhc pop Justin Timberlake tng ni: Mt trong nhng iu i km vi danh ting l vic i t ca bn b xm phm. Vy, iu g  hp dn, khin cho nhiu ngi, trong  c bn, mun tr nn ni ting:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"&gt;Tr li:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; Nhng tri nghim m ti c  mang li s ni ting cho ti. C nhng cch khc  cm nhn v danh ting v  c ni ting l nhng ngi thng minh, xinh p.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Rc r m chung kt Miss Universe 2009&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;nh n lp lnh cng ting nhc rn r du bc chn ca cc ngi p Hon v trn sn khu. m chung kt ti hn o Paradise  Bahamas din ra si ng vi &lt;a href="http://vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA12AC6/"&gt;s ln ngi&lt;/a&gt; H s c chnh sa mi b phn cha hon thin, mt, mi hay mi... trc khi bc vo cc cuc thi sc p.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Nhng hnh nh trong phng s, do&lt;em&gt; Seattle Times&lt;/em&gt; thc hin di y,  tit l c mt dy chuyn o to hoa hu bi bn ca Venezuela. N cng phi by s thc, con ng n vi ngi v ca cc ngi p khng ri hoa hng m y nhc nhn, kh luyn, c khi l c m hi, nc mt.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Hu trng ngnh kinh doanh hoa hu  Venezuela tng c VnExpress.net gii thiu trong bi vit "&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2008/12/3BA097BA/" class="Normal"&gt;Cng ngh chnh sa nhan sc hoa hu  Venezuela&lt;/a&gt;".  , hng nm c hng trm, hng nghn c gi khao kht s hu vng min sc p. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/2B/F0/ekralla.jpg" width="350" border="1" height="419" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td class="Image"&gt;Eva Ekvall - mt "sn phm" thnh cng ca cng ngh o to Hoa hu. nh: &lt;em&gt;Missvene.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Mun t c gic m, trc ht, h s phi lt vo mt xanh ca Osmel Sousa - thy ph thy trong ngnh cng nghip kinh doanh sc p ti Venezuela. Sousa cng cc cng s s phn tch, ch ra nhng im cha n trn gng mt v thn hnh ca cc c gi. Nhng ngi c chn, sau , tip tc tri qua cc cuc phu thut thm m  chnh sa nhan sc, nhm to ra mt v p, tim cn nht c th, n s hon ho. Cng on cui cng ca h l c dy d cch i ng, n ung, ng x  ni bt nht gia mt rng ngi p trong cc cuc thi nhan sc. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Dayana Mendoza cng tng c nho nn di bn tay ca Osmel Sousa." src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/2B/F0/dayg.jpg" width="400" border="1" height="500" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td class="Image"&gt;Dayana Mendoza cng tng c nho nn di bn tay ca Osmel Sousa. nh: &lt;em&gt;People.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Sau tt c nhng cng on , vic cn li ca h l ch i giy pht ng quang trong nhng m chung kt hoa hu.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Ngoi Dayana Mendoza - Miss Universe 2008, mt trong rt nhiu nhng hc tr xut sc ca Osmel Sousa l Eva Ekvall. Mt nm sau, c ot ngi  hu 3 trong cuc thi Miss Universe 2001. Tuy nhin, khng phi mi qu trnh o to u thnh cng. Ngoi ra, c cn l mt ca s nhc pop.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA12964/page_6.asp" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/64/ukrai-da-hoi-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA12964/page_6.asp" onclick="return openMeExt(this,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,1,300,400,0,0,0)" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/64/ao-tam-1-ukr-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA12964/page_6.asp" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/64/2Ukraine-dan-toc-nhi.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Khng cn qu tr cho mt cuc thi sc p quc t, nhng b li, Kristina c gng mt bp b, mi tc nh ri n tng khin c tr hn nhiu so vi tui. S dy dn kinh nghim ti cc cuc thi nhan sc ln nh, cng vi k nng ca mt ngi mu chuyn nghip l nhng yu t c th gip Kristina gp mt trong top 15 ca Miss Universe.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-7954883684919385444?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/7954883684919385444'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/7954883684919385444'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/08/5-nguoi-ep-chau-au-noi-bat-nhat-tai.html' title='5 ngi p chu u ni bt nht ti Miss Universe'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-1516719611613476827</id><published>2009-08-24T23:13:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:53:00.388-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><title type='text'>Top 7 ngi p Hon v chu M</title><content type='html'>&lt;p class="Lead"&gt;i din Colombia lun lm sng bng sn khu bi gng mt p rng r. Hoa hu CH Dominica chinh phc Miss Universe nh thn hnh gi cm v bn lnh 'thi u", cn Miss Puerto Rico p mt v yu kiu, nh nhnh...&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;H l nhng th sinh ni bt nht, i din cho v p chu M ti Miss Universe 2009.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hoa hu Colombia - Michelle Rouillard&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Chn dung" src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/colombia-chan-dun.jpg" width="400" border="1" height="606" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td class="Image"&gt;Chn dung Michelle Rouillard.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;22 tui, cao 1,73 m, s o 3 vng 92 - 62 - 92, Michelle l sinh vin ngnh Kinh doanh ti i hc Concord, Canada. C ni c 3 th ting: Anh, Php v Ty Ban Nha.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_2.asp" onclick="return openMeExt(this,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,1,300,400,0,0,0)" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/Colom-da-hoi-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_2.asp" onclick="return openMeExt(this,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,1,300,400,0,0,0)" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/colom-ao-tam-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_2.asp" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/colombia-dan-toc-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Sau khi ng quang Hoa hu Colombia 2008, Michelle gy bt ng ln khi quyt nh ct phng mi tc di v nhum thnh mu ht d. Ngi p tin rng, c s gy n tng hn bi mi tc ngn c nht ti Miss Universe. Dng nh Michelle  ng. Mu tc ht d lm sng khun mt vi ln da trng mn ca c. Mi tc ngn, t nhin mang n cht c tnh cho v p trong sng, gi cm. Nhan sc, thn hnh cn, kin thc v kh nng ngoi ng  m bo cho Michelle mt sut vo vng trong. Tuy nhin, im yu ca c l chiu cao. Ch vi 1,73 m, Hoa hu Colombia kh lng ni bt gia hng chc ngi p khc. n nay, Colombia mi ch mt ln ng quang Hoa hu Hon v vo nm 1958.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hoa hu CH Dominica - Ada Aimee De la Cruz&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Chn dung" src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/do-chan-dung.jpg" width="400" border="1" height="598" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td class="Image"&gt;Chn dung Ada Aimee De la Cruz.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;23 tui, cao 1,83 m, Ada l siu mu tng tham gia rt nhiu cuc thi sc p. C l th sinh Miss World 2007, ot gii Hoa hu Bin v lt vo top 16 ca cuc thi nm .&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_3.asp" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/dominica-da-hoi-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_3.asp" onclick="return openMeExt(this,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,1,300,400,0,0,0)" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/dominica-ao-tam-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_3.asp" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/do-dan-toc-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Ada l mt trong nhng th sinh cao nht, c thn hnh p nht v c nhiu kinh nghim d cc cuc thi nhan sc nht ti Miss Universe 2009. V vy, Ada hon ton c th khin cc i th khc mt bnh tnh khi c ta sng trn sn khu vi n ci rng r, thn hnh l tng v k nng catwalk kh ai bng. Tuy nhin, nhiu ngi nhn xt,  mt s gc , Ada c v p hi cng, phn no ging vi cc ngi p chuyn gii.  c th l bt li cho ngi p CH Dominica.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hoa hu Jamaica - Carolyn Yapp&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Chn dung" src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/ja-chan-dung.jpg" width="490" border="1" height="301" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td class="Image"&gt;Chn dung Carolyn Yapp.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;25 tui, cao 1,75 m, Carolyn Yapp l nh thit k ni tht. C va ng quang Hoa hu Hon v Jamaica 2009 hi thng 7.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_5.asp" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/jamaica-dan-toc-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_5.asp" onclick="return openMeExt(this,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,1,300,400,0,0,0)" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/ja-ao-tam-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_5.asp" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/ja-da-hoi-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Carolyn t c nhc n nh mt ng vin hng u cho ngi v Miss Universe, nhng kh c th ph nhn v p c bit tot ra t n ci, nh mt v ln da mn mng, khe khon ca c. Vi n ci ngt ngo, thn hnh gi cm, ngi p Jamaica c d on s khng gp qu nhiu kh khn  c xng tn trong top 15 m chung kt.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hoa hu Mexico - Karla Carrillo&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Chn dung" src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/me-xi-chan-dung.jpg" width="400" border="1" height="601" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td class="Image"&gt;Chn dung Karla Carrillo.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;21 tui, cao 1,76 m, Karla Carrillo l mt ngi mu. C ni thnh tho 3 th ting: Anh, Php v Ty Ban Nha.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_4.asp" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/me-da-hoi-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_4.asp" onclick="return openMeExt(this,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,1,300,400,0,0,0)" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/mexia-am-tam-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_4.asp" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/mexico8-dan-toc-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Karla c gng mt p ngang nga vi Hoa hu Colombia. V vi chiu cao 1,76 m, khng c g ng ngc nhin khi c lt vo top 15, thm ch cn l ng vin cho vng min Hoa hu. Karla hon ton c th em li vinh quang cho Mexico, nu c may mn hn Hoa hu tin nhim Elisa Najera - ngi tng chng  cm chc vng min Hoa hu nhng cui cng ch ot danh hiu  hu 4 ti Miss Universe 2008.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hoa hu Nicaragua - Indiana Sanchez&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Chn dung" src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/nica-chan-dung.jpg" width="400" border="1" height="606" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td class="Image"&gt;Chn dung Indiana Sanchez.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;22 tui, cao 1,77 m, Indiana ang l sinh vin. C thng tho ting Anh v Ty Ban Nha.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_6.asp" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/ni-ca-da-hoi-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_6.asp" onclick="return openMeExt(this,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,1,300,400,0,0,0)" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/nicaragua-ao-tam-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_6.asp" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/nicaragua8-dan-toc-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Indiana c v p rng r, trong tro v chiu cao kh n tng. Nhiu thng tin cn cho rng, c l mt trong s cc th sinh lt vo mt xanh ca ngi Donald Trump - ngi s hu cuc thi Miss Universe.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hoa hu Puerto Rico - Mayra Matos&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Chn dung" src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/puerto-rico-chan-dung.jpg" width="400" border="1" height="602" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td class="Image"&gt;Chn dung Mayra Matos.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;20 tui, cao 1,78 m, Mayra l ngi mu. Trc khi n vi Miss Universe, c tng ginh vng min Hoa hu tui Teen Quc t 2006 (&lt;span style="color:#000000;"&gt;Miss Teen International). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_7.asp" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/puerto-dahoi-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_7.asp" onclick="return openMeExt(this,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,1,300,400,0,0,0)" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/pue-biki-nhp.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_7.asp" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/puerto-rico7-dan-toc-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Mayra Matos n t mnh t c nhiu ngi p lt vo hng top cc cuc thi nhan sc quc t. Gng mt, thn hnh v k nng catwalk  c th a ngi p Mayra vo thng cc vng trong.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hoa hu M - Kristen Dalton&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Chn dung" src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/my-chan-dung.jpg" width="400" border="1" height="603" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td class="Image"&gt;Chn dung Kristen Dalton.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;22 tui, cao 1,71 m, Kristen Dalton sinh ra trong mt gia nh p di truyn v c truyn thng tham d cc cuc thi nhan sc. Kristen hin l sinh vin ti i hc ng Carolina.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_8.asp" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/my-da-hoi-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_8.asp" onclick="return openMeExt(this,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,1,300,400,0,0,0)" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/my-ao-tam-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/08/3BA129A3/page_8.asp" class=""&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/29/A3/usa8-dt-nho.jpg" width="158" border="1" height="383" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Kristen s hu v p qu phi, sc so, nhng c bc l s thn thin, tnh cch hn nhin v nim tin mnh m vo bn thn. Qua nm thng, n din vin ngy mt gi cm vi i g bng o cng y.&lt;br /&gt;&gt; &lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/Guong-mat-Nghe-sy/2009/08/3BA12510/" class="Lead"&gt;Cng Li v nhng thc phim nng bng&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Theo nh gi ca trang gii tr &lt;em&gt;Cri&lt;/em&gt; (Trung Quc):&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cng Li (Gong Li)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A1/2A/53/cung1.jpg" width="495" border="1" height="384" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Ch s sexy: 6 sao (     )&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;N din vin Hong kim gip c hnh th chun ca ngi Sn ng - ni c trng thnh. Kh gi cm nhng vng mt ca Cng Li hi nh. Qua thi gian, s nghip ca ngi p h Cng ni danh c trong nc v th gii. Din mo ca c cng dn p hn. &lt;p class="Normal" align="right"&gt;(nh: &lt;em&gt;Hon V cung cp&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-7535111786728243795?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/7535111786728243795'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/7535111786728243795'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/08/nhat-ky-hinh-anh-cua-hoang-yen-tai-miss.html' title='Nht k hnh nh ca Hong Yn ti Miss Universe'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-7579969235913980059</id><published>2009-08-17T23:17:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:53:01.579-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><title type='text'>Vn bn chuyn nghip hn vi CutePDF Writer</title><content type='html'>&lt;div id="VietAd"&gt;&lt;div id="maincontent"&gt;&lt;div class="ttvtIntro"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vn bn, sch, chuyn... s chuyn nghip hn  nh dng file PDF. Nhng lm th no  trnh by cc ni dung text v nh  dng PDF? Cu tr li c  CutePDF Writer, d dng ngay c vi dn i-t my tnh.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;" class="ttvtFigCenter"&gt;&lt;a href="http://ms.thongtincongnghe.com/upload/large/0908/15/img-1250287956-1.jpg" title="" rel="lightbox"&gt;&lt;img src="http://ms.thongtincongnghe.com/upload/med/0908/15/img-1250287956-1.jpg" alt="" title="" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt; CutePDF Writer la tin ich min phi cho phep ban bin i bt c inh dang vn ban nao thanh file pdf ma vn gi nguyn cac thuc tinh va ni dung co trong file gc nh c ch, mau ch, cac hinh anh Download chng trinh &lt;a href="http://soft4all.info/free-software-download/cutepdf-writer-easy-to-create-pdf-files-from-any-document/"&gt;tai y&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Sau khi download, ban giai nen va kich hoat file CuteWriter.exe  tin hanh cai t. Tai bc cui cung cua qua trinh cai t, chng trinh yu cu may tinh kt ni Internet  cai t thm 1 tin ich phu (PS2PDF Converter). Nu may tinh cua ban hin khng kt ni Internet, ban nhn NO trong hp thoai yu cu kt ni Internet, sau o kich hoat file converter.exe giai nen c  trn  cai t PS2PDF Converter ma khng cn kt ni Internet. (Trong trng hp may tinh ang kt ni Internet, ban chon Yes  chng trinh t download va cai t).&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;" class="ttvtFigCenter"&gt;&lt;a href="http://ms.thongtincongnghe.com/upload/large/0908/15/img-1250287956-2.jpg" title="" rel="lightbox"&gt;&lt;img src="http://ms.thongtincongnghe.com/upload/med/0908/15/img-1250287956-2.jpg" alt="" title="" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;   &lt;strong&gt;Lu y:&lt;/strong&gt; Ban phai cai t u ca 2 ng dung nay thi chng trinh mi co th hoat ng c.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; c im chinh cua CutePDF Writer o la chng trinh nay hoan toan khng co giao din ngi dung.  tin hanh chuyn i file vn ban sang PDF, ban m file cn chuyn i bng chng trinh mc inh (chng han file .doc m bng Word, file xls m bng Excel hay file txt m bng Wordpad). &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; Tip theo, tai ca s chng trinh ban dung  m file vn ban gc, chon lnh  tin hanh in (Print). Vi du, nu ang s dung Microsoft Office  m file, ban nhn t hp phim Ctrl + P hoc chon nut Print t trn menu. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Lu y:&lt;/strong&gt; Ban co th chon lnh nay bt k may tinh cua ban co kt ni vi may in hay khng. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; Tai khung hp thoai Print hin ra tip sau o, muc Name trong khung Printer, ban chon CutePDF Writer va nhn OK. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;" class="ttvtFigCenter"&gt;&lt;a href="http://ms.thongtincongnghe.com/upload/large/0908/15/img-1250287956-3.jpg" title="" rel="lightbox"&gt;&lt;img src="http://ms.thongtincongnghe.com/upload/med/0908/15/img-1250287956-3.jpg" alt="" title="" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;    &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;i trong giy lat, hp thoai Save As hin ra, cho phep ban chon vi tri trn  cng  lu file va t tn cho file pdf ma CutePDF Writer tao ra. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; Cui cung, tim n vi tri ma ban a chon  trn, 1 file vi inh dang PDF va tn file do ban t se xut hin, cha toan b ni dung cua file gc trc o. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; Trn y la cac bc  s dung CutePDF Writer tao ra file PDF t nhng inh dang file vn ban thng dung, giup cho ni dung vn ban cua ban c bao v an toan hn. Hy vong, bai vit nay se hu ich cho ban.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;(Theo Dn tr) &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-7579969235913980059?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/7579969235913980059'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/7579969235913980059'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/08/van-ban-chuyen-nghiep-hon-voi-cutepdf.html' title='Vn bn chuyn nghip hn vi CutePDF Writer'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-5859331068787808301</id><published>2009-08-17T18:09:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:53:01.815-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hoa Hu - Siu Mu'/><title type='text'>Siu mu chu  Phng Mai qung co loa Edifier</title><content type='html'>&lt;p class="Lead"&gt;N sinh vin i hc RMIT, ni ting sau khi lt vo &lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/07/3BA11B12/" class="Lead"&gt;Top 10 siu mu chu &lt;/a&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;m s kho l bui trnh din ra mt u tin trn sn khu ca 84 ngi p ti Miss Universe 2009. Hin nay, s nghip ngi mu ca chn di ny ang ln nh diu gp gi. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Bar s tip tc 'nng' trn Sports Illustrated 2010, Ngi mu n, Thi trang, " src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-08-14/1250256660-Bar-Refaeli-SI-2010-01.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Bar s tip tc 'nng' trn Sports Illustrated 2010, Ngi mu n, Thi trang, " src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-08-15/1250296758-Bar-Refaeli-SI-2010-020.jpg" width="490" height="368" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0000ff;"&gt;Bar Refaeli lm tr trong mt bc nh trn bi bin c chp cho tp ch Sports Illustrated&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span id="_ctl0_rContent_lbDesc"&gt;Vi chiu cao 1m73 cng cc s o 89 - 61 - 90,  Bar Refaeli c coi l chn di "hot" nht hin nay v tr thnh siu mu bikini s 1 th gii vt qua rt nhiu gng mt nh m ca lng mu. y cng khng hn l l do  ngi p Israel ny vt ln ng u&lt;/span&gt; trong bng danh sch tn vinh nhng ph n p nht th gii trong nm nay.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Bar s tip tc 'nng' trn Sports Illustrated 2010, Ngi mu n, Thi trang, " src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-08-14/1250256660-Bar-Refaeli-SI-2010-02.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Siu mu gi cm trong b bikini tut quai trong khi cc chuyn vin trang im ang sa sang li khun mt.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;a phn mi ngi ch bit rng Bar Refaeli bt u lm ngi mu khi mi 11 tui nhng thc ra c bc vo lng thi trang sm hn rt nhiu. Mi ch 8 thng tui, c nhc nh Refaeli  c xut hin trong mt qung co thng mi ca Israel. y chnh l t cht  gip ngi p ny thnh cng trn con ng ngi mu ca mnh.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Bar s tip tc 'nng' trn Sports Illustrated 2010, Ngi mu n, Thi trang, " src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-08-14/1250256660-Bar-Refaeli-SI-2010-03.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bar khoe ng cong nng bng vi b bikini hng th hn lng mn trong gi&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Khng ph lng ngi hm m, ngi p ca min t thnh ny ha hn s tr li trn trang ba tp Sports Illustrated vo nm 2010 trong nhng bc nh nng bng v rt c bit.  &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;H l mt vi bc nh mi nht ca Bar chp cho tp ch SI nm 2010, chn ai ny lun th hin s li cun v v p quyn r ca mnh trong tng gc chp.&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Bar s tip tc 'nng' trn Sports Illustrated 2010, Ngi mu n, Thi trang, " src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-08-14/1250256660-Bar-Refaeli-SI-2010-034jpg.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Cng trong mt bc nh, chn di gi cm ny eo mt chic knh ln v thc s li cun trong b bikini nh xu cng vi nhng ngi bn.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Bar cng tng xut hin trong qung co ca hai hng thi trang sng s th gii l Victoria's Secret v Ralph Lauren ng thi c cng l ngi p trang ba n khch ca tp ch Elle v GQ.&lt;/p&gt; Gi y, khi cuc ua ca Miss Universe 2009 ang i n nhng vng ua cui, cng l lc Dayana Mendoza c quyn lm mt iu g  cho mnh, nm trong nhng quy nh khng c php sut 1 nm qua&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;Trong bi phng vn ngn dnh cho Dayana Mendoza c Maxim ng ti trn trang tin in t, Dayana cho bit: &lt;em&gt;12 nm lin tip nc ti khng c 1 hoa hu Hon v, v th khi v thn may mn mm ci vi ti, lc tr v, bn kh c th tng tng ti  c n tip nh th no. Rt nhiu c, hoa, nhng ci m hn v li cho n. Ti  o khc trong s vui sng v hnh phc. t nc chng ti cn c chic vng min ny!.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mi bn ngm nhn nhng hnh nh nng bng ca Dayana Mendoza trn tp ch Maxim:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Hoa hu Hon v &amp;quot;chnh thc&amp;quot; khoe... ngc!, Thi trang, " src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-08-14/1250217630-dayana-mendoza_l3.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Hoa hu Hon v &amp;quot;chnh thc&amp;quot; khoe... ngc!, Thi trang, " src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-08-14/1250217740-dayanamendozal2.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nhng bc hnh ny vn c thc hin trong khu ngh dng Atlantis ca 84 th sinh d thi nm nay trn quc o Bahamas&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Hoa hu Hon v &amp;quot;chnh thc&amp;quot; khoe... ngc!, Thi trang, " src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-08-14/1250217630-dayana-mendoza_l4.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Hoa hu Hon v &amp;quot;chnh thc&amp;quot; khoe... ngc!, Thi trang, " src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-08-14/1250217740-dayanamendozal1.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;c gi chc hn s thy nhng chic gi nhiu mu sc y thn quen, i din Vit Nam V Hong Yn  tng to dng bn cnh chng. Gi y, hoa hu Hon v 2008 li bn kha thn bn cnh nhng tng mu nng bng ny&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Hoa hu Hon v &amp;quot;chnh thc&amp;quot; khoe... ngc!, Thi trang, " src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-08-14/1250217630-dayana-mendoza_l5.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img class="news-image" onclick="return openNewImage(this, '')" alt="Hoa hu Hon v &amp;quot;chnh thc&amp;quot; khoe... ngc!, Thi trang, " src="http://www15.24h.com.vn/upload/news/2009-08-14/1250217630-dayana-mendoza_l8.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"&gt;&lt;em&gt;S "bc la" ny  khng c cho php xut hin trong 1 nm nay. &gt;&gt;  Hunh Thanh Tuyn d thi Hoa hu Bikini Quc t&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;  &lt;span id="ctl14_ltrContent" class="bodyContent"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hunh Thanh Tuyn bc chn vo lng ngi mu t nm 19 tui, khi c va tt nghip PTTH. 3 nm si chn trn sn catwalk, c gi tr ny  gt hi c thnh cng ng k: Th sinh c n ci p cuc thi Hoa hu bo Ph n Vit Nam qua nh nm 2005; Gii vng cuc thi Ngi sao ngi mu th h mi 2008 v tham gia kh nhiu chng trnh thi trang ln  nc ngoi.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div&gt;iu  l gii v sao, Thanh Tuyn khng qu lo lng cho cuc thi Hoa hu o tm Quc t sp ti din ra ti o Hi Nam, Trung Quc. C bt m, cng  tham kho, hc hi kinh nghim t mt vi ngi bn  tng u  trn u trng sc p quc t nh Tin on, Hng Giang&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div align="center"&gt;&lt;img style="margin: 5px;" src="http://dantri.vcmedia.vn/Uploaded/nguyenhang/2009/02/tuyen1_1922009.jpg" _fl="" width="350" align="center" /&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div align="center"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Tahoma;"&gt;Ngi mu Hunh Thanh Tuyn (nh NV cung cp)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;Ngi mu tr ny cho bit, cng nh bao cuc thi sc p khc, cuc thi Hoa hu o tm Quc t tri qua cc phn thi: Hoa hu Bin, Hoa hu Ti nng, Hoa hu Thn thin, Trang phc t chn. Nu c la chn tham gia phn thi Ti nng, Thanh Tuyn s tr ti nh n Tranh.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Hin ti, iu ti quan tm nht l luyn tp th thao nh i bi, chy b v gi gn sc kho sao cho tht do dai, Thanh Tuyn th l.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div&gt;Thanh Tuyn chia s:  Ti cha c bn trai v ang trn ng tm kim ngi n ng ca mnh. Con ngi ta c lc ny lc khc, ti khng c bt c tiu chun no c th v ngi mnh s yu. Nhng trn thc t, ti thy nhng ngi n ng hiu tho vi b m, c ch cu tin tht ng mn. V, c ni khinh ght ngi n ng hn v trong cuc sng khng kh khn  gp phi nhng ngi n ng nh th.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div align="center"&gt;&lt;img style="margin: 5px;" src="http://dantri.vcmedia.vn/Uploaded/nguyenhang/2009/02/tuyen2_1922009.jpg" _fl="" width="350" align="center" /&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div align="center"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Tahoma;"&gt;Ngi mu tr ny s hu gng mt kh i v n ci lm ng tin duyn dng&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;Ngi p ny cng khng giu gim, trc y c  tri qua vi mi tnh. C mi tnh su sc v c mi tnh chng vnh nhng cho n gi cha ai thc s khin ngi p ny khng th qun!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Sau y mi c gi Dn tr chim ngng chm nh Hunh Thanh Tuyn nng bng vi bikini:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td class="Image"&gt;Siu mu nghin ngp Kate Moss.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A0/FF/4D/ke10.jpg" width="380" border="1" height="647" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td class="Image"&gt;Lily Allen va ln va bo.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A0/FF/4D/ke11.jpg" width="480" border="1" height="333" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td class="Image"&gt;Fearne Cotton khng cn i.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;  &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A0/FF/4D/ke7.jpg" width="380" border="1" height="611" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td class="Image"&gt;Coleen Rooney bo .&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-4941012938311682685?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/4941012938311682685'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/4941012938311682685'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/07/top-5-ngoi-sao-co-hinh-ep-va-xau-nhat.html' title='Top 5 ngi sao c hnh th p v xu nht'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-4766177379065141716</id><published>2009-07-20T20:49:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:53:06.357-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hoa Hu - Siu Mu'/><title type='text'>10 du hiu nng mun hn h</title><content type='html'>&lt;p class="Lead"&gt;Khi mun pht tn hiu tnh cm vi ngi khc gii, phi p cng phi mt nhiu thi gian  suy ngh v cc th thut "bt n xanh". V th, ngoi vic mi da k nng tn tnh, cc anh chng cng nn nng cao kh nng quan st v phn tch hnh vi ca ph n.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Di y l 10 du hiu cho thy mt ph n mun hn h vi bn.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="SubTitle"&gt;1. Ci vi bn&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Khi mt ph n quan tm ti bn, n ci ca nng c th thu ht s ch  ca bn ngay c khi bn ang ng trong mt cn phng ng ngi. Cc chuyn gia tm l khng nh n ci l mt trong nhng cng c hiu qu ca phi p trong vic pht tn hiu tnh cm. Phi rt c gng ph n mi dm n n ci vi mt ngi n ng xa l. V th hy p tr c y bng mt n ci ti.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="SubTitle"&gt;2. i qua i li trc mt bn&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Nu mt thiu n c lin tc i li  nhng v tr nm trong tm nhn ca bn trong khi r rng c y khng c bt c l do g  lm vic  th c th khng nh nng mun li ko s ch ca bn. Nng ang c gng gi thng ip rng nng mun c gp g ring vi bn. Trong trng hp  bn nn ni mt cu g  tht ngn gn nhng m tai.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="SubTitle"&gt;3. Dng mi  thu ht s ch .&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Cp mi ca phi p l mt b phn c sc quyn r m hn v a s ph n  thc c iu . Khi mt ph n mun hn h vi mt ngi n ng, nng s dng son bng, a ngn tay ln mi hoc dng ng ht  ung cocktail thay v ung trc tip. Nn nh rng mi l cng c v cng hiu qu trong vic pht tn hiu tnh cm.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="SubTitle"&gt;4. T tch ra khi m ng&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Nu sau khi giao tip bng mt vi bn, nng tch ra khi m bn th  l du hiu nng ch i bn ti gn  bt chuyn. Phi p hiu rng ro cn ln nht ca mt ngi n ng trong vic tip cn mt ph n chnh l nhng ngi bn ca nng. Hnh ng tch ra khi m ng l cch  nng "nhn nh" rng, nng ang h thp ro chn  bn tip cn.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="SubTitle"&gt;5. Bt chc hnh vi ca bn&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;V mt vi l do, khi con ngi quan tm hoc m mn ln nhau, h s hc mt vi c im c nhn t i tc. Nu nng bt chc hnh vi ca bn - t cch cm ly hay ngi - th c th ni nng ang mun li ko s ch  ca bn.  l tn hiu chc chn v vic nng mun hn h. Bt chc l mt hnh thc ly lng  bc cao  con ngi v ng vt. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Khi nng tch ra khi bn b sau khi ci vi bn,  l du hiu cho thy nng ang h thp ro chn  bn tip cn." src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A0/70/7C/h33.jpg" width="350" align="left" height="350" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td class="Image"&gt;Khi nng tch ra khi bn b sau khi ci vi bn,  l du hiu cho thy nng ang h thp ro chn  bn tip cn. nh: &lt;em&gt;pbase.com&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="SubTitle"&gt;6. Nghch tc&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Mc d hin tng ny kh n gin v ph bin, song c mt thc t l trong bn tay phi p, tc tr thnh mt v kh a nng. Khi mun li ko s ch  ca nam gii, h c th dng cc ngn tay vn v tc hoc  chng xa xung mt mt  lm tng thm v b n.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="SubTitle"&gt;7. Chm vo bn&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Khi nng ti gn v chm nh vo cnh tay hoc vai bn th bn phi nhanh chng p li bng mt hnh ng tng t hoc n ci, bi  l du hiu nng mun n ti hoc i chi vi bn.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="SubTitle"&gt;8. Giao tip bng mt&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Ngi ta thng ni con mt l ca s tm hn v s tht c th c thy qua i mt. Giao tip bng mt l mt du hiu ca s t tin v tin tng. Thng qua hnh vi y, nng mun tuyn b rng nng chng quan tm ti my tr chi trn my tnh m ch ch bn mi i u . Thi gian tn ti ca hnh vi giao tip bng mt t l thun vi mc  hng th ca nng.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="SubTitle"&gt;9. Xm nhp th gii ring ca bn&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Th gii ring t l ni m ch c bn c quyn tip cn. Khi mt ph n bc vo khng gian y, chng hn nh ti thm ch  ca bn vi mt n ci, th  l du hiu nng quan tm ti bn. Mc  quan h v tnh cch ca nng s l nhng yu t bn cn xem xt trc khi a ra phn ng.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="SubTitle"&gt;10. Ti gn bn  ni chuyn&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Hnh vi ny ca nng c th lin quan cht ch vi vic i qua i li trc mt bn, nhng n c nhiu  ngha su xa hn. N cho php nng duy tr c cc hot ng giao tip bng mt, nghch tc, chm vo ngi bn, bt chc hnh vi ca bn v nhiu k thut by t tnh cm khc. Nu nng bc ti pha bn  ni chuyn tc l nng mun xc tin bc u tin trong mt qu trnh m ngi ta gi l hn h.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class="Normal" align="right"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vit Linh&lt;/strong&gt; (theo &lt;em&gt;Askmen&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-4766177379065141716?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/4766177379065141716'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/4766177379065141716'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/07/10-dau-hieu-nang-muon-hen-ho.html' title='10 du hiu nng mun hn h'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-5701417375475770963</id><published>2009-07-20T20:47:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:53:06.373-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Hoa Hu - Siu Mu'/><title type='text'>nh Mai Phng Thy lm nng Nha Trang</title><content type='html'>&lt;p class="Lead"&gt;Bc la, hp dn v y sng to l n tng m b nh bikini ca &lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/06/3BA0FB24/" class="Lead"&gt;Mai Phng Thy&lt;/a&gt; mang n cho ngi xem. &lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/05/3BA0EC53/" class="Lead"&gt;Mai Phng Thy xc cm trc bin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Nhng tm hnh mc bikini nm trong trin lm V p trc bin ca Mai Phng Thy c gii thiu ti Festival Nha Trang vo 6/6. V p trc bin gm nm b nh mang tn &lt;i&gt;Yoga bin m, Tinh khi trc bin, Bu vt bin xanh, Gi tn bn ma&lt;/i&gt; v &lt;i&gt;Dt c m&lt;/i&gt;,&lt;i&gt; &lt;/i&gt;khng ch gii thiu v p ca ngi ph n hin i, quyn r v nng ng m cn thng qua  thu ht nhng tm lng nhn o. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Mai Phng Thu" src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A0/FB/24/3.jpg" width="400" border="1" height="600" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Hin ti, ngi p 20 tui  thu c 300 triu ng t vic bn 5 trong s 100 tc phm trng by ti trin lm cho Euro Window. Hoa hu Vit Nam 2006 tm s, c khng cm thy lo lng hay hi hp v trc  tng cm cn ny mc trong gn 50 cuc thi sc p trong v ngoi nc nh Hoa hu Th gii ngi Vit 2007 ti Anh v c, Miss Vietnam 2009 ti Php&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Mai Phng Thu" src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A0/FB/24/1.jpg" width="400" border="1" height="600" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Trn cng v gim kho, ngi p H Ni cho bit c s tht cng tm, khng thin v mt ai, d trong s cc th sinh ca Miss Vietnam Global 2009 c ngi p &lt;a href="http://www.vnexpress.net/GL/Van-hoa/2009/05/3BA0F49E/" class="Normal"&gt;Hng Giang&lt;/a&gt; l bn quen bit t trc. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Mai Phng Thu" src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A0/FB/24/5.jpg" width="400" border="1" height="600" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Hoa hu Vit Nam Ton cu chc chn phi hi t mt cch ton vn cht Vit tht tha  mn trnh din o di dn tc; s duyn dng,  nh, thng minh v thc t trong cch tr li ng x; khe mnh, gi cm vi o tm; sang trng, kiu sa nhng khng qu tay vi trang phc d hi. Ti mong rng mnh s c c hi tm hiu mt cch cn k nht  a ra nh gi khch quan nhm chn ra ngi con gi p i din cho t nc, m khng phi np sau hnh nh mt c Ty no c, Mai Phng Thy chia s v tiu ch chm im ca mnh.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;table width="1" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="Mai Phng Thu" src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A0/FB/24/06.jpg" width="400" border="1" height="600" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;p class="Normal"&gt;Thng su l thng bn rn nht ca Mai Phng Thy trong nm.
