Nhng ngy nay, vic eo knh t ra c hiu qu hn trong vic che i nhng khuyt im ca mt ni trn, v th vic xm nhn cu mt t c thc hin hn.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Tuy nhin, khng phi ai cng c th mang nhng knh eo mt, v khng phi ai cng mun con ngi ca h trng c v nh li thm ra v knh. K t  xm nhn cu mt  tr thnh 1 dng phu thut thm m  lm p c tnh ngh thut cao.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Rch da &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/ShFK_lC7sTI/AAAAAAAAD1I/mhGYMTcIQDA/s1600-h/CucHot.Net_GheQua_2.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 146px;" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/ShFK_lC7sTI/AAAAAAAAD1I/mhGYMTcIQDA/s400/CucHot.Net_GheQua_2.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5337129489547374898" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Vic rch nng da l ng dng sng to v ngh thut rng rn n t nhng vt so. Cy m 3D ngh thut&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/ShFK_on5goI/AAAAAAAAD1A/u1uiFCFzTLo/s1600-h/CucHot.Net_GheQua_3.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 253px;" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/ShFK_on5goI/AAAAAAAAD1A/u1uiFCFzTLo/s400/CucHot.Net_GheQua_3.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5337129490507727490" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Loi hnh cy m 3D ngh thut ny dnh cho bt k i tng no thch c xm di da ph hp vi mt iu khc trn b mt da.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ban u, "pht minh" v vic ph bin rng ri vic cy m nh ngh thut 3D c tin tng ch yu t 1 ngi c tn l Steve Haworth. Nhng m cy c th c ko cng ging nh vic c cc l. Mt trong nhng v d l cc m cy sng, lc bt u chng ch l nhng vt khc nh, n khi chng c ly ra khi c th th  da  lnh. Chng li c thay th bng nhng ming ln hn. Qu trnh ny c lp li  t bng c kch thc cui cng. Tuy nhin c khng t nguy c v s kch ng da  trn m cy nu trong khi thc hin, qu trnh ny c thc y qu nhanh.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Xu l o nt ngc&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Mt trong s khuynh hng mi nht ca vic s ci bin thn th chnh l tr c l o nt ngc. B mt sau da  lng b chc thng c sp thng thnh hai ct dc ng. Vic c l c xc nh ng vo trong nhng l xu  xu o nt ngc.  l mt s uc l i xng vi mt s lng l bng nhau trn mi cnh. V phi xu t nht bn l mi c th s dng c, v cn ty vo da ngi xu c th chu c n mc no khi cng da ra. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. Nhng nhnh cy au n&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/ShFK3ntXahI/AAAAAAAAD0w/43YQNj0zIHM/s1600-h/CucHot.Net_GheQua_5.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 196px;" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/ShFK3ntXahI/AAAAAAAAD0w/43YQNj0zIHM/s400/CucHot.Net_GheQua_5.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5337129352823269906" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Vic to hnh nhng nhnh cy trn c th con ngi c l l dng gy au n nht trong mi s ci bin thn th. Trong ton din tch da tht b kha, st c nung  nng v c ng dng  di  to nn vt thng cho ra kt qu l nhng nhnh cy (lu : tr ny c nguy c lm hoi dy thn kinh y!). Th nhng, phi c tn mt chng kin cc mn lc git tung c&amp;#8230; qun o, nhng i chn nhn nhy ca cc c  ngang st mt mnh, trong hn n no khi thuc, no hi ru, no ting nhc, v khng th thiu nhng ting go r tc tu, nh vng n t mt min hoang ng ca cc g n ng  ngt ng v ru, c rn cc cp mt ang chc dp li  m ngm cc c, v thi nhau tun ra nhng li bnh lun, mi thy, cc c kim c ng tin t cng vic nhy thot y v cng n gin nhng cng v cng kh khn.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;img alt="" src="http://hehe.vn/upload/heheasp/images/03/VuNuThoatY1.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;  &lt;p align="justify"&gt;Kh khn khi trong tm hn nhng c gi nhy y cn cht dn vt ca lng tri&amp;#8230; Cc c quan chc nng  rt tch cc u tranh chng li t nn ny nhng tic thay thi gian gn y loi hnh gii tr bnh hon  li c xu hng ti xut hin  mt s ni.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p align="justify"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bc nhy d chin&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p align="justify"&gt;Khng kh khn nh chng ti tng, sau c nhp nhy ca mt nhn vin karaoke trn con ph gn b  sng Hng chng 30 pht sau,  thy mt nhn vin nam ln thu dn chin trng l nhng chic cc ru vt chng ln trn bn, nhng v chai bia v v s mu thuc l  chic bn g chc chn ngay lp tc pht huy cng dng bin thnh bc nhy d chin. Cu nhn vin lm cc ng tc thun thc nh v bt cm, chng ni chng rng i lui ra ca, khng qun vi tay tt bt mt bng n. 1 pht tri qua. Cng hi hp khng km khi phi ch i cc cnh gay cn trong phim hnh ng M. T chic loa  bn gc phng vang ln ting nh ca pht thanh vin thng thy ti cc sn bay. Tng ai  chuyn nhm nhng khng,  chnh l on m u m thc lon ca mt phi i bay, gm c 3 th h 7X, 8X, 9X.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;img alt="" src="http://hehe.vn/upload/heheasp/images/03/VuNuThoatY2.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;  &lt;p align="justify"&gt;Ting nhc lc rn r, ln cao dn ch sau 1 &amp;#8211; 2 pht. Ca bt m. o vo phng 2 c gi trn ngi ch c 2 mnh nh xu. Tri rt, th nn thy thng cho nhng mnh da tht l l di nh n nh nh. Guc cao 15 phn. cc c vt vo nh i lm xic. Nhy bp pht ln chic bn, ci tht ti cho &amp;#8220;khn gi&amp;#8221;. V mn lc bt u vi nhng ng tc tht do, tht chuyn nghip cng tht sexy. Cng chng bit t lc no, mt chic cc nha (khng bit c phi cc c mang theo hay khng) c t ngay pha u bn, c c 1 pht, mt t tin 100 nghn hoc 200 nghn c nhng thiu gia i cng chng ti cm vo. Mt thiu gia gh st tai ti ni: Cm thm tin vo, n nhn thy nhiu tin mi ci ht. Ra th!&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p align="justify"&gt;Chc cp mt n ng hau hu nhn nhng ng tc un o, trn b nh rn m ta thng thy trong cc hp m qua phim nh Hng Kng, M. Hn l cc c quen ri nn khng thy ngn ngi. V vy, khi mt g vi tay bt thm bng n &amp;#8230; nhn cho r hn, cc c nhon ming ci lm ng tc b st ra mp bn&amp;#8230; khiu khch g. Nhng khi g cha kp th tay  vut m th c  nhanh hn g tng, li pht li, ban cho g mt n ci na nh giu ct, na nh cm thng. Khi chic cc nha  c v hi cht, 2 mnh nh xu pha trn  c cc c trt xung, tht nhanh v cng tht chuyn nghip. Mt ting r ln phn khch, ngi xung quanh my chic bn g, my g n ng  bt u nhp nhm, tu tng chic cc ru, ung ng c mt cch v thc. V khi n bt thm mt bng na th hai mnh nh xu bn di li c trt nt.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;img alt="" src="http://hehe.vn/upload/heheasp/images/03/VuNuThoatY3.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;  &lt;p align="justify"&gt;Lc ny th c m nhao nhao, nhy ma lon x. Nhng, khi m nhng ci u ang ang bung bing v ru, bia v c nhng l do khng bit na cn ang ph pha tng tng, th nhc tt pht, hai c gi ci tht ti, ci u cho khn gi. Trn mng da trn lm tm m hi. Ngi  gc phng, cc c h hoy mc qun o. Lc ny, ti mi c dp ngm k h. Hai khun mt tr trung, khng th ni l khng xinh. Hi tn, cc c khng ni, hi qu, cc c ch ci. V cng nhanh nh khi n, h o ra ca, khng qun nhn theo chic cc nha ng tin.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p align="justify"&gt;Nhng  ch l mn 1. Nhc li tip tc ni ln, ln ny c v ph phng hn ln trc. Khng phi 2 m l&amp;#8230; 5 c cng vo mt lc&amp;#8230;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p align="justify"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thc lon&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p align="justify"&gt;Hai pht ngh gia gi, cu phc v  kp k thm hai chic bn na, vung vc nh&amp;#8230; chic ging. Li ci gp ngi cho khn gi. Li vn nhng mnh nh xu b ra th thiu m eo vo th tha. Nhng ln ny, mn nhy ch din ra rt ngn gn, c v kh hnh thc. Cn mn chnh li c bt u khi m nhn vin kh n b vo phng c kt bia Ken. Nhng np v chai c bt ra bm bp, bt tro ra trng xa. Chng ai ung. ng nhin ri. Bia l  cho cc c&amp;#8230; t tm cho nhau. G bn cnh bo ti: N phi nhy nht khi ng cho nng ngi ln, khng n lc bia ti ln ngi, lnh thy b ni, chu sao ni.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;img alt="" src="http://hehe.vn/upload/heheasp/images/03/VuNuThoatY4.jpg" border="0" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;  &lt;p align="justify"&gt;Nhng d  thy cc c khi ng, ti vn thy mt c rng mnh khi nc bia c mt c khc ri ln ngi. Xin khng k ra y nhng ng tc m cc c b bt buc phi lm nu mun ly tin t nhng g n ng ang vy xung quanh. Ch bit rng, ci gi l cng vic ca h khng th dng t khc hn ngoi t tc tu. Sex &amp;#8211; khi ch hai ngi trong phng the, th  l s thing ling nhng khi c cp mt ngi th ba nhm vo th n tr thnh s v duyn, kch cm, thm ch bnh hon. V cm trc n ng, v cm trc nhng li tc tu, ct nh. Tt nhin anh lm c, nhng chng lm ti thy tho mn. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ngi v v ngi chng trong hai cu chuyn trn  tch cc tham gia din n cng chia s trn mng, cng nh tm n cc nh tm l  h tr khi hn nhn ca h c u hiu tan v. Nhng cui cng, h quyt nh ly hn  c t do,  c sng mt i lm v, lm chng tht s. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nhng ngi mc chng t yu mnh (hay cn gi l i k) &lt;/em&gt;khng phi l nhng ngi bt lc v tnh dc. Nhng thay v kht vng vi ngi yu, h li u t kht vng  vo chnh bn thn mnh. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/ShDfn1-VftI/AAAAAAAADwA/i_mk4PPA8zU/s1600-h/CUcHot.Net_TuYeu_4.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 300px; height: 400px;" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/ShDfn1-VftI/AAAAAAAADwA/i_mk4PPA8zU/s400/CUcHot.Net_TuYeu_4.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5337011434030464722" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;H cng c th t tho mn bn thn bng th dm, bng quay hnh nh kho thn ca mnh ri tua i tua li  xem cho sng mt. H cng chp nh p ca mnh  dng kho thn, ri post ln mng, khng phi  ngi khc xem, m  thnh thong t m ra xem. V vy, nhiu blog ca nhng ngi b mc chng t yu mnh lun   ch  Just me. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/ScH0wgQhzTI/AAAAAAAAAK4/DfjXy01zL1k/s1600-h/TungPro.Com_ThuDam1_2.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 300px;" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/ScH0wgQhzTI/AAAAAAAAAK4/DfjXy01zL1k/s400/TungPro.Com_ThuDam1_2.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5314798149404052786" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Chng tc gin, v kht khao cng kh thay i c h, bi h ly v ly chng cho ging mi ngi, do gia nh thc p, ch bn thn h ch yu mnh l . V hu nh cc cuc hn nhn  khng ko di c lu. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/ScH0wx14GjI/AAAAAAAAALQ/yoDRAyH5omE/s1600-h/TungPro.Com_ThuDam1_5.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 301px;" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/ScH0wx14GjI/AAAAAAAAALQ/yoDRAyH5omE/s400/TungPro.Com_ThuDam1_5.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5314798154124106290" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Chng t yu mnh khng ch lin quan ti lnh vc tnh dc, m cn nhn r  mi kha cnh tm l khc. V y l nhng du hiu nhn bit v chng ny:&lt;br /&gt;- C du hiu v cung, tc l cho rng mnh l v i nht, xinh p nht, mi ngi phi ngng m bn thn mnh.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/ScH0w3V4_GI/AAAAAAAAALI/ar7dKFSCJaY/s1600-h/TungPro.Com_ThuDam1_4.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 300px;" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/ScH0w3V4_GI/AAAAAAAAALI/ar7dKFSCJaY/s400/TungPro.Com_ThuDam1_4.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5314798155600559202" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;- Cho rng mnh l ngi c bit, mi ngi kh lng m hiu c. Hay ni v tnh yu cao thng, nng v tm hn, coi thng tnh yu thn xc, cho  l xu xa, khng th snh c vi ci p thing ling ca tnh yu thanh khit.&lt;br /&gt;- Ngm vut, trang im, gn gi nhan sc mt cch thi qu.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;- C hin tng th dm, hay ph by thn th mnh cho ngi khc chim ngng. qua ri ci thi m mm  cc qun bar, sn nhy  tm "i tc", dn "gay" ngy nay  p dng "cng ngh thng tin" v nhng tuyt chiu "sn tnh" m ngi bnh thng kh c th tng tng ra... &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gi "tnh" trn blog...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgzU81n0XJI/AAAAAAAADYg/K0IUSdPHIeU/s1600-h/CucHot.Net_Gay_1.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 300px;" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgzU81n0XJI/AAAAAAAADYg/K0IUSdPHIeU/s400/CucHot.Net_Gay_1.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5335873800178523282" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Chng phi mt cng m mm, ve vn v ong a nhng cu trai "p m"  qun c ph, sn nhy hay qun bar mt cch l liu nh trc, dn "gay" thi nay  coi nhng trang blog c nhn l mt phng tin "cc k hiu qu v kn o" ... tm bn tnh. Khi kt ni c vi 1 blog "gay" mang tn BabyK, chng ti  khng khi git mnh v ngay t "trang ch - homepage" ch nhn ca blog  "gy sc" khi a 4 bc nh "2 cu trai ang hn nhau" ln lm nh i din.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgzV8T4zAjI/AAAAAAAADYo/1wCUlXfcHJo/s1600-h/CucHot.Net_Gay_blog.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 300px;" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgzV8T4zAjI/AAAAAAAADYo/1wCUlXfcHJo/s400/CucHot.Net_Gay_blog.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5335874890634560050" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Sau vi ci click chut  vo c blog th ngi vit pht hong tht s khi li l v hng chc tm hnh "t sng" cc k bnh hon  c ch nhn "trng" ln nhm mc ch "show hng" vi bn tnh. Thm ch trong mt entry xut bn ngy 9/5/2008, ch nhn ca blog cn mnh dn  ngh: "c lm quen vi tt c nhng bn trai  - ang v s c blog BabyK". Phn cui ca entry ny, g cn a lun c s in thoi di ng ca mnh ln  "cc bn c nhu cu" tin lin lc.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Khng trng qu nhiu nhng bc hnh bnh hon nh blog BabyK, nhng blog ca Cuois cng s dng nhng bc nh t chp khi ang "vui v" vi bn tnh  lm nh i din. V ngay trong phn "t thut v bn thn" trn blog, g trai ny cng khng nh: "Ti l gay... Ti c quyn yu v c yu".&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgzUI_j6_VI/AAAAAAAADYQ/LEdIYlQNZ5c/s1600-h/CucHot.Net_Gay_2.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 265px; height: 400px;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgzUI_j6_VI/AAAAAAAADYQ/LEdIYlQNZ5c/s400/CucHot.Net_Gay_2.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5335872909493337426" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ni dung bn trong ca blog ny ngoi nhng li "trn tnh" v "th gii th 3", ch nhn ca blog ny thng xuyn km theo khng t li mi gi theo kiu "Ngh cui tun - cn tm bn trai i du lch", "Ti c n gia bao bn b - mun tm mt ngi bn nh mnh  tm s sao kh qu" hay thm ch "Bn trai no  Tuy Ho - Ph Yn cng l ngi "thuc th gii th 3" hy n vi ti".&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Khng hiu nhng li mi gi ca g "gay" ny hiu qu n mc no nhng c lu lu ngi ta li thy trn blog ca g li c nhng bc nh mi "cc k tnh cm" ca g chp vi mt cu trai khc. Ngoi ra, blog ca Cuois cn nhn c v s nhng li tn dng, lm quen ca hng trm g trai khc: "Bn p lm... nick ca t l congio_t... Chng mnh lm quen nh".&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;V c nh vy, danh sch bn b trong Friendlist ca g "gay" ny ch sau hn 2 thng k t ngy xut hin  ln ti con s 253 blog, m ch ton l blog ca dn ng tnh.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgzUI1kGuFI/AAAAAAAADYI/vGkTP7E0YmA/s1600-h/CucHot.Net_Gay_3.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 300px; height: 400px;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgzUI1kGuFI/AAAAAAAADYI/vGkTP7E0YmA/s400/CucHot.Net_Gay_3.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5335872906809751634" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tuyt chiu... " u"!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Khng bit ting Anh v li cng chng bit t to g v chat chit v blog, nhng "tuyt chiu nhn  u" mt s g "nht gi" hnh ngh "bun thn bn thnh"  t H Ni li t ra hiu qu hn hn so vi tr dng blog  gi tnh ca nhiu g "nht tr", bi "phi nhn tn mt - bt tn tay th mi c "g p", "g t" c", "d" Hnh, mt g "gay" khng nh.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-46xSTtsI/AAAAAAAACO4/80Pb9lbAIZ8/s1600-h/1.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 300px; height: 400px;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-46xSTtsI/AAAAAAAACO4/80Pb9lbAIZ8/s400/1.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332183803632006850" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Thch c gi l "d" Hnh, g "gay" tn tht l Thng ny c v b ngoi "trm phn trm" l n ng vi mi tc  di v nhng khi c bp lc lng. "D" Hnh ni vi v lp l: "Ci tr loanh quanh c ph vi sn nhy  "tm bn" xa lm ri. Gi m cn dng my cch c k  th "qu ", m khng kho li dnh qu la th nhc xc lm. Bn ny , gi ch cn i n  my nh hng kha kh, i ht karaoke "c" hoc i ung bia hi l tha h "tm bn" m chng mt my cng sc v tin bc".&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-43cWxHtI/AAAAAAAACOw/KoHLAa0mLKg/s1600-h/2.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 301px; height: 400px;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-43cWxHtI/AAAAAAAACOw/KoHLAa0mLKg/s400/2.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332183746473959122" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-43MlfUNI/AAAAAAAACOo/688elnMCREU/s1600-h/3.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 300px;" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-43MlfUNI/AAAAAAAACOo/688elnMCREU/s400/3.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332183742240739538" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Phi mt gn 1 tun tri v vt m hm cng nhm "gay" m "d" Hnh cm u ny trong nhng nh mt xoi mi ca nhiu ngi, ti mi khm ph ra "tuyt chiu" m nhng k b gi l "xng pha nht" ny vn p dng  "kim bn tnh" -  l dng "mi"  nh nhng cu trai mi ln t cc tnh v H Ni kim sng bng ngh chy bn, gip vic.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-43HyGgpI/AAAAAAAACOg/pYgja5A1nyU/s1600-h/4.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 300px; height: 400px;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-43HyGgpI/AAAAAAAACOg/pYgja5A1nyU/s400/4.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332183740951462546" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;"n qun no m gp "g" a mt th ngy no d cng n cho "g" quen mt, ri tm lc vng khch m gi chuyn. Thi th chuyn trn tri, chuyn di bin, chuyn nh chuyn ca ri dn dn gi n chuyn "v gip vic Thnh" cho cc "cu", va nhn h, va "c lc". Thy "cc cu" u l n ng, mt mi u t t, li sng ng hong th "g" no chng tin, chm lm th cng 1 thng l dt c "g" v nh... gip vic" - "d" Vinh mt trng ni ro honh.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-43AMhI1I/AAAAAAAACOY/oK2Il3g_N0Y/s1600-h/5.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 270px; height: 400px;" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-43AMhI1I/AAAAAAAACOY/oK2Il3g_N0Y/s400/5.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332183738914775890" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Khc vi nhm ca "d" Hnh,  dt c "g" v nh, nhm "gay" ca "d" Quang thng t tp  khu vc ph Hng Giy. "D" Quang khng d "g" v nh gip vic m li nhn...  u, dy ngh "bun thn bn thnh" cho nhng cu trai thch n ngon, mc p v li lao ng.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-426jHEvI/AAAAAAAACOQ/XAOU2334gEw/s1600-h/6.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 271px; height: 400px;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-426jHEvI/AAAAAAAACOQ/XAOU2334gEw/s400/6.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332183737398924018" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Th nhng, cng chng bit ci s "gip vic Thnh cho cc cu" vt v hay cc nhc n u m c i thng li thy "g" c bin mt v thay vo ch ngi pha sau xe my ca cc "d" li c mt gng mt mi, cn nguyn v ngng ngp khi ln u tin i chi m, ung bia, ht h. C gng tip cn, hu ht cc cu trai, d  vi ba ln gp nhng khi c hi chuyn "gip vic Thnh n ra lm sao" cng u m  cho qua. Cu trai no bo lm th cng ch qua loa c vi cu "Th em cng ch gip cc "d" hu bng, dn nh thi"!.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-4unKj-QI/AAAAAAAACN4/pT73sv-rR2I/s1600-h/9.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 300px; height: 400px;" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-4unKj-QI/AAAAAAAACN4/pT73sv-rR2I/s400/9.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332183594756733186" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-4uq8TfiI/AAAAAAAACNw/_KlEEL1oTvw/s1600-h/10.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 300px; height: 400px;" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-4uq8TfiI/AAAAAAAACNw/_KlEEL1oTvw/s400/10.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332183595770674722" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;B Qunh - ch qun n c ting trong khu ph c bc dc: "Ti  "mt" my thng b gip vic v ci v d chng ra d, cu khng ra cu y ri. Chng bit c g m hoc m chng n c n n vi ba l y nh rng c thng b xin "ngh vic v qu.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-4u-tU5cI/AAAAAAAACOI/12ZKbV7vdLY/s1600-h/7.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 336px; height: 400px;" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-4u-tU5cI/AAAAAAAACOI/12ZKbV7vdLY/s400/7.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332183601076561346" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Thc ra lc u ti cng ngh l ngi gip vic v qu tht, n mi gn y c thng b quay li xin lm vic tip n k ra ti mi bit l my tn  n d con trai nh ngi ta v nh gip vic  ri li dng. Tc lm nhng ti cng chng bit lm th no c. Chng n l con trai, cng ln ri, khn th kh m di th kh".&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf-4u_D7IyI/AAAAAAAACOA/qWm6uKWYSkc/s1600-h/8.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; Nguyn nhn l do mt cu bn va mi n, nhy lun xung b, chng thm   g n nhng ngi xung quanh.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Va mi nhy xung, nguyn vng nc quanh cu bn kia bng chuyn mu nu nu. Ha ra, cu chng va mi i  bng v, ngi y t ct, m hi nh nhi, nng qu nn n thng b bi  tm. Do  bi khng mang theo, nn chic qun dnh t cng c i theo lun xung b.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Cha ht, mn tip theo khin ai cng shock,  l cu ta thn nhin k c khp ngi, ri thnh thong li hn nhin: Mt qu, vi Sng tht.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Bao con mt t ngc nhin n bc xc chng khin cu ta quan tm, c v t kiu Vic ti, ti lm. Mi ngi nh leo c ln b, ai cng lc u vi th di thn tht.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thi trang k d&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Khng ch c th, mt iu v cng   khc ca mt s teens  b bi chnh l cch n mc k cc n kh .&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sfvckn74rfI/AAAAAAAABTg/KGVa-t70OsU/s1600-h/BK_2.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 380px; height: 400px;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sfvckn74rfI/AAAAAAAABTg/KGVa-t70OsU/s400/BK_2.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5331097105676676594" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Khng hiu c b lm sao vi dy thn kinh xu h hay khng, m ti b bi MX, c c nng thay v mc  bi, li din ngay qun o chip ra b. iu ng ni l  chic qun chip en ca nng, n ton ren l ren, h n ni m cn l m thy c rng bn trong.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SfvcksADLuI/AAAAAAAABTo/V-xt4QMv9Yk/s1600-h/BK_1.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 277px;" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SfvcksADLuI/AAAAAAAABTo/V-xt4QMv9Yk/s400/BK_1.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5331097106767884002" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SfvcaCpWg4I/AAAAAAAABTI/tUewo1ixu0w/s1600-h/BK_5.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 376px;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SfvcaCpWg4I/AAAAAAAABTI/tUewo1ixu0w/s400/BK_5.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5331096923868136322" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Nu l mt ln, c khi ngi ta cn ngh c rng c nng chc vi, qun khng mang  thay, nn mc tm. ng ny, vn l khch quen  , v mt s khch quen khc cho bit: Ngy no chng vy, th ng l b tay vi nng tht. Li gn hi han, nng xi mt ci, ri bo: Cng c khc g bikini u, mc ci g chng c.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SfvcaVkximI/AAAAAAAABTY/18RBMhD3F7w/s1600-h/BK_3.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; Ai chng bit l  bi. Th m khng phi nh vy. S hu gng mt p, ngoi hnh bt mt (cao 1,68 mt) cng ging ht nhiu cm xc, Mi Trn ang bt u tn cng tr li lnh vc m nhc vi album u tay c ta  &lt;i&gt;Hy thuc v em. &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div align="center"&gt;&lt;font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A0/DD/F5/mi-tran.1.jpg" border="0" alt="" onload="NcodeImageResizer.createOn(this);" /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"&gt;Mi Trn la chn phong cch tr trung, gi cm trn sn khu. nh: &lt;i&gt;Nhn vt cung cp.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;Tn tht ca c ca s gc H Ni l &lt;b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font color="#de981e"&gt;Trn Tr My&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, nhng nhc s Huy Tun  t cho c ngh danh d thng l Mini Trn cho l, trnh ng hng vi mt s ca s khc. Sau c quyt nh rt ngn li l Mi Trn v s nghe Ty qu. Nhiu ngi nh n Mi Trn khng phi l mt n ca s m bi vai th chnh y c tnh m c th hin trong phim truyn hnh &lt;i&gt;Nhng cnh hoa bay&lt;/i&gt;.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;Khi chuyn sang cng vic ca ht, Mi Trn c ch Trn Mnh Tun m li gip  vi hy vng c s hu thun, c chu gi ca mnh s thnh danh sm hn. Nhng Mi Trn cho bit c mun t ng ln bng thc lc. C cng mong mun mnh s c v o p nh ngi ch l ca s hi ngoi Nguyn Hng. D bt u con ng ca ht kh mun  tui 23, Mi Trn t ra kh t tin: Ti c mt cht hnh thc, mt cht kh nng, cng vi s kh luyn, ti tin mnh s thnh cng.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;div align="center"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;div align="center"&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Hy thuc v em&lt;/i&gt; gm 9 bi ht, thin v s th hin tm trng yu ui, mong manh ca ngi con gi trong tnh yu. y cng chnh l nhng xc cm ca Mi Trn qua hai mi tnh. Tuy nhin, vic dn tt c nhng g ca s a thch vo trong mt album khin cht nhc v th loi nhc cha c nh hng r rng. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;Album do nhc s &lt;b&gt;&lt;font color="#de981e"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Trng L Sn&lt;/b&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;gip  hon thnh nn Mi Trn gp kh nhiu li n i v vic cp k vi lo hi. Tuy nhin c bnh tnh cho rng, nhng tin n l chuyn kh trnh khi trong ngh ca s: Ti thn vi gia nh anh Trng L Sn v hay n chi nh, thy anh v ch Hong L Vy rt hnh phc. Ch Vy khi nghe thy nhng tin n ny cng ch ci xa. Nhiu ngi hiu lm y l chiu PR tn tui ca ti, nhng ti cho rng scandal l con dao hai li v ni ting bng scandal th khng th lu di.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;div align="center"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div align="center"&gt;&lt;div align="center"&gt;&lt;font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;img src="http://img.news.zing.vn/img/185/t185188.jpg" border="0" alt="" onload="NcodeImageResizer.createOn(this);" /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;Mi Trn&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font color="#ff7f00"&gt;&lt;div align="center"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"&gt;&lt;font size="3"&gt;Ti khng phi l mt hot girl&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div align="center"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;font color="#80ff00"&gt;- Ra album trong thi im khng hong kinh t ko theo s  m ca showbiz, Mi Trn khng s rng CD ca mnh s ri tm vo s im lng v lng qun?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;div align="center"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div align="center"&gt;&lt;font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;- ng l cng s tht, nhng a  lm xong ri, t lc trc khi showbiz  m, nn kiu g th ti cng phi tung ra th trng thi. &lt;/TD&gt;&lt;/TR&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;TR&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;TD class=Image align=left&gt;&lt;FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: arial"&gt;&lt;I&gt;&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;/TR&gt;&lt;/TBODY&gt;&lt;/TABLE&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;DIV align=center&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;TABLE cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=3 width=1 align=center border=0&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;TBODY&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;TR&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;TD&gt;&lt;IMG src="http://vtc.vn/newsimage/original/vtc_297450_13.jpg" width=475 border=1 name=imagePhoto&gt; &lt;/TD&gt;&lt;/TR&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;TR&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;TD class=Image align=left&gt;&lt;FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: arial"&gt;&lt;I&gt;Vi mi thay i kiu tc, Hyori vn tht xinh p.&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;/TR&gt;&lt;/TBODY&gt;&lt;/TABLE&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-6150222707146487307?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/6150222707146487307'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/6150222707146487307'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/05/thoi-trang-toc-cua-hyori.html' title='Thi trang tc ca Hyori'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-543582010248020427</id><published>2009-05-06T23:07:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:41:40.751-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Phong Cch Tr'/><title type='text'>Quyn c "in in"</title><content type='html'>&lt;strong&gt;Hai ngi cng i du lch n vng ni. Mt ngi gi v mt ngi tr. Hai ngi cng ht "A...a...a..." tht ln  nghe ting vng vo vch ni. Nu nhn ngi ln tui lm nh vy, bn thy tht k cc. Cn nu nhn bn tr, bn thy tht th v. Nu bn cn tr, bn c lm th khng?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgJ6tYV_VUI/AAAAAAAADAg/vxRiBubtNb8/s1600-h/quyen.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 300px; height: 200px;" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgJ6tYV_VUI/AAAAAAAADAg/vxRiBubtNb8/s400/quyen.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332959828807472450" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Mi  tui c mt cch in ca n. Tui teen cng vy. y l ci tui phong cch c nhn c nh hnh,  thc c nhn c thit lp, ci ti c nhn c bc l. V nhiu khi bc l theo nhng cch in in.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Bn ti cng c nhng cch in kh ngy th nh kiu: chy n m chm a bn m ni tao nh my qu d va gp nhau hm trc. Hay t nhin thy yu i k l, ht vu v mt mnh mi khng chn. Cng c th in in kiu nh Hu (hc sinh trng P) mua mt bng hng  thm mang ln lp,  trn bn, mc bn b t m, ci vu v mt mnh ri li mang v. n gin v ang trn ng i hc, Hu thy mnh xng ng nhn bng hoa p kia lm ch. Th l mua tng mnh. Ngh cng thy vui vui.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;C bao gi bn in nh vy khng?  c ai ni bn in in cha? Ti th nhiu ri.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ngi ta ni ti in  m i ct phng mi tc di th?. Ti k. Ct cho gn gng, thoi mi. Ti mun thay i hnh nh ca mnh khi bc chn vo i hc.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ngi ta ni ti: in  m i hin mu. Ngi th gy teo. Ti k.  ngh c lm mt ngha c cao p khin ti thy sng. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ngi ta ni ti: in  m i b? Xe u?. Ti k. Ti thch cho i chn trn lu lu c hng mi t, mi  trn tri, hoang s.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ngi ta ni ti in  rt nhiu. Nhng ti k. c in tht thoi mi v th v. Lu lu ti li truyn th kinh nghim v nhng kiu in in cho bn b cng th.&lt;br /&gt;Sau ci ln ti in in b nh n vng rng ni Sn La, "lm khng cng" cho ngi ta, th ti  r c mt nhm bn cng i tnh nguyn vi mnh.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;C t ti thy anh thanh nin nh mng chi bi mt ngi ph n thm t bn v ng. Ngi ng xem rt ng. Mi ngi thc mc v a ra nhiu li bnh lun v cch ng x th bo ca chng trai. Ti in in nhy vo can, b anh ta nh lun. C nhm bn ti ngay lp tc cng in in theo, nhy vo, can anh thanh nin v cng ti bo v ngi ph n. Rt may, ln  chng ti in khng lu v an ninh phng n kp.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Cng c ln ti cm ti rc trn tay, thy c ci ti nilon ng my th v tri cy, v bnh ko lung tung  trn gh . Ti in in tin tay cm lun, cho vo thng rc mt th. Sau ngh li thy mnh lm th cng chng mt g nn in thm nhiu nhiu ln na, cng chng thit thi g. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Tt nhin, in khc a dua, ua i. Khi bn a dua, ua i l bn ang hc lm theo s ng hoc mt s ngi c cch sng, cch ngh v hon cnh khc vi mnh. Ti chng lm th. Ci g thy ng, thy hp vi mnh th lm thi. Phi ging ngi khc, chy theo ngi khc mt mi v kh chu lm.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;in cng khng ging vi liu. Khi bn in in, bn ngh mnh lm c nn th, d n c khc ngi mt cht, khc cch lm ca mi ngi mt cht. Cn liu l bn ngh mnh khng c lm, sc bn khng th lm nhng bn vn c. Liu nh th rt nguy him, d gy nn hu qu khng mong mun.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;in in i khi cng rt vui. Khi ti cng mi ngi nm tay, tha h chy nhy, h ht xung quanh ng la tri ti thy mnh tht sng v mnh cn  tui c quyn c in nh vy.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Khi ti c ht to mt ting t nhin gia khng gian thong rng, ti thy tht hnh phc v mnh vn cn sc m in nh vy.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Tui tr vn rt qu gi v khng th tn ti mi. Vy th ti sao khi cn tr, khi cn quyn c in bn khng in in mt cht?  th sc mnh.  th thch mnh.  tri nghim mnh. V  xc nhn gi tr ca mnh. Sao bn khng tn dng quyn c in ca tui tr  in th mt ln xem sao? Vui lm!&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-543582010248020427?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/543582010248020427'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/543582010248020427'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/05/quyen-uoc-ien.html' title='Quyn c &amp;quot;in in&amp;quot;'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author><media:thumbnail xmlns:media='http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/' url='http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgJ6tYV_VUI/AAAAAAAADAg/vxRiBubtNb8/s72-c/quyen.jpg' height='72' width='72'/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-603651235601974625</id><published>2009-05-06T21:30:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:41:41.181-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Scandal - Shocking'/><title type='text'>P tay th h 10x</title><content type='html'>&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/ScNYfFxrxKI/AAAAAAAAAQA/deRQHptuvJw/s1600-h/TungPro.Com_10x_1.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; Vi ai cng sn sng ln x ht mnh, sng cht cho tnh yu.  l chn dung ca nhng c nng mc hi chng yu ai cng in cung.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nhng tnh yu ln  li hu qu ln&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Li thm mt ln mui mt dn Ngn n bnh vin  x l hu qu, Thy nhm tnh y tng cng l ln th 3, vn   ch tc gi ca chng chng ln no ging nhau. Nhn c bn mt mi xanh lt, rn r ku au, Thy va thng va gin.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; nhiu ln Thy khuyn Ngn khi yu hy tm hiu k trc khi mun ht mnh nhng kh ni c bn a su a cm ny rt i bng bnh. Mi chm quen bit anh chng no, c nng cng qu quyt y ch th l tnh yu ln trong i, thm ch cn v ra vin cnh ngi nh v nhng a tr. Vi ai cng y p k nim v bao iu kh qun. ng nhin, an xem trong  l nhng pht my ma qun ngy thng,  li bao hu qu.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://vtc.vn/newsimage/original/vtc_255347_yeu%20hoc%20tro.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 300px;" src="http://vtc.vn/newsimage/original/vtc_255347_yeu%20hoc%20tro.jpg" border="0" alt="" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;center&gt;&lt;em&gt;u tin l mi tnh thi o trng vi mt cu bn cng lp... &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ngn khng nh: Mnh khng h n hn khi trao i con gi cho anh y. V 18 tui, Ngn ln u tin bit n phng khm sn v m thanh ca nhng dng c ht thai. Ht cp 3, ngi yu Ngn i du hc, h chia tay, c nng tm s: ng tri c tnh chia ct. Chc tao khng th yu ai c nh th na.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Nhng d kin sai hon ton, cha y 2 thng sau, Ngn hnh phc thng bo: Ln ny mi l mt na ch thc. Mt anh chng hn 5 tui, c v tay chi, Ngn t ho khoe: Anh y cc k manly v tng tri. Th mi l n ng!. Song, ch n khi ci bng nh ra, Ngn mi thc s kim nh c ci s n ng ca hn. n mt xu i gii quyt hu qu cng chng c. Lc y, Ngn th khng bao gi tin n ng na. Kt qu th no? Gi y, sau c sc kia chng na nm, c nng tip tc l lng vi anh chng th 3. Ln ny, Ngn qu quyt: Nu n nh s nghip, c l anh y v tao  kt hn. Anh y l ngi chng l tng!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thn ny chng tic v cc chng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Trng hp ca Hoa th lm li hn. Ngi trong bnh vin, m Hoa ngi khc tc ti bn cnh c con gi di dt: Ti sao ti kh th, c mi a con gi m nay n t t v thng ny, mai n t t v thng khc. C vi ngi l ngi gn  nghe thy khng khi lc u: S nht l nhng em v giai no cng i cht nh th!.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ngi ta ni th chng ngoa. Kiu con gi nh Hoa n ng by gi s nht. Bnh thng yu th thch, tnh cm lm, li chiu chung na! Song, h c vn  g l li ngay mng sng ra nh i. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Chuyn ca Hoa mi ngi bn tn kh nhiu. Nghe u, c nng ny yu ai cng tng da cht. V y l ln th 2 c chng minh cho  ngh  qun mnh, x thn v trai. Nm ngoi, Hoa ni ting khp trng nh phi v ung 3 v thuc ng khi nhn thy ngi yu i vi c gi khc. Cn nm nay, li tip tc gy scandal bng vic liu mnh dng dao lam ca t tay bi bn trai i i du hc. May m c hai ln gia nh Hoa u kp thi pht hin, a i cp cu. Tt nhin, hai anh chng c coi l nguyn nhn chnh gy nn v t st khng thnh ny u v cng hong s. Mt ngi trong h tng tm s: Tht en i vi phi loi con gi yu in nh th.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;in cung nhng nng ni&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://vtc.vn/newsimage/original/vtc_255348_1.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 450px; height: 300px;" src="http://vtc.vn/newsimage/original/vtc_255348_1.jpg" border="0" alt="" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;center&gt;&lt;em&gt;C chia tay g ny l c g khc "gi u" ngay...&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Hu ht, nhng c nng mc chng "yu ai cng in cung" thng ng nhn mnh giu cm xc, c chiu su tm hn. Tuy nhin, ch ngi ngoi cuc v nhng nn nhn ca h mi thu hiu v khng nh ngc li. Thy  bn thn ca Ngn chia s: Thc ra, c y t l tng ha tnh yu ca mnh. Yu ai cng cho rng  l tnh yu ln. Vy m cha bao gi mnh thy c y c n. C chia tay g ny l c g khc "gi u" ngay. Thm ch, c ln ang yu in cung anh ny song vn thm nh in cung anh khc!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Cn mt trong s ngi yu c ca Hoa k li rng  v cng sc khi b Hoa . Bi cu ta lun tin rng Hoa yu mnh n sng d cht d, my ln  dm ma n pht m khi b cu ta gin hoc nhng ba i nhy sng t vn nu hai a chia tay. Th m ch thng trc thng sau, c nng b cu  n vi tay n ng khc. Nhng nc ci nht l Hoa vn st si ni rng: D cho c chuyn g xy ra, em cng khng bao gi qun anh!. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Nh vy  hiu, ci s "in cung" ny khng h t l thun vi s su sc. Cng in cung c khi li cng nng ni.&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-5472998326247607202?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/5472998326247607202'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/5472998326247607202'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/05/pha-thai-3-lan-tac-gia-chang-lan-nao.html' title='Ph thai 3 ln tc gi chng ln no ging nhau'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-786195736308916924</id><published>2009-05-05T03:57:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:41:41.715-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Phong Cch Tr'/><title type='text'>Chm nh cc p ca bng hng wushu Thy Linh</title><content type='html'>&lt;strong&gt;Nm nay 19 tui, Thy Linh l mt trong nhng VV ti nng v xinh p nht lng wushu Vit Nam. scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Phong Cch Tr'/><title type='text'>Ma h si ng cc hot vi la tui hc tr</title><content type='html'>&lt;strong&gt;- Ma h si ng - b phim di 30 tp ca Hng phim Hnh Tinh Xanh chnh thc bm my vo hm nay, ngy 23/2,  kp pht sng trong ma h nm nay.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ma h si ng (o din: Nguyn V Duy Ngc -  Mai - Nht Tun, bin kch: Trn Th Hng Hnh) ni v 6 thiu nin hon ton khc bit v hon cnh gia nh v tnh cch, cng quen nhau trong mt chuyn du lch.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Vi tnh cch khc nhau, Nam  Duy  Qun  An  Hn  Chi  b li sau lng nhng thi h tt xu thng c trong i thng, ha mnh tht s vo chuyn i, gip  bn ng hnh bng s hn nhin ng yu ca la tui hc tr.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAak3PfAFI/AAAAAAAACv0/QHzr4yCF7Ww/s1600-h/1.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 268px;" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAak3PfAFI/AAAAAAAACv0/QHzr4yCF7Ww/s400/1.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332291179413176402" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;center&gt;&lt;em&gt;Dn din vin x-tin ca "Ma h si ng".&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Hnh trnh 10 ngy l hnh trnh gip h t hon thin mnh, bit chia s, bit thng yu ngi khc v hc c nhng iu khng c trong trng hc. Nam kiu ngo va du hc  Anh v Vit Nam, An tiu th ng nh, Duy lu c  trng thnh hn  bit cuc sng khng ch c ganh ua v s ph trng.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Da trn  tng v tour du lch mang tn Hun luyn qu t ca mt cng ty du lch m nhiu bc ph huynh quan tm gi gm qu t ca mnh trong nhng k ngh,  bin kch Trn Th Hng Hnh  khai sinh &lt;em&gt;Ma h si ng. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Cc tnh hung trong phim cng l nhng kinh nghim, bi hc sng ng nht gp phn hnh thnh tnh cch ca la tui teen. S c nhiu th lm cc em trng thnh hn, c bit l nhng chuyn i du lch vi bn b cng trang la. Cng i, cc em s  hc hi nhiu iu b ch  t hon thin mnh.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAakvHDavI/AAAAAAAACvs/sXezxEc-mlA/s1600-h/2.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Vi s c mt ca cc din vin: Khng Thnh, Phng Trinh, Vn Anh Duy, Phan Nht Phi Long, M Kim, Bo Trung, Dim My, Ma h si ng ha hn s l b phim truyn hnh th v dnh cho la tui hc tr.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Phim c bm my vo ngy 23/2 vi nhng cnh u tin ti TP.HCM, sau  on lm phim s quay ti Phan Thit, Nha Trang,  Lt&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-7939347373992763978?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/7939347373992763978'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/7939347373992763978'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/05/mua-he-soi-ong-cuc-hot-voi-lua-tuoi-hoc.html' title='Ma h si ng cc hot vi la tui hc tr'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author><media:thumbnail xmlns:media='http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/' url='http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAak3PfAFI/AAAAAAAACv0/QHzr4yCF7Ww/s72-c/1.jpg' height='72' width='72'/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-1632674277009177589</id><published>2009-05-05T03:49:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:41:41.780-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Phong Cch Tr'/><title type='text'>Phm Diu Linh cha bao gi ngh mnh yu "i gia"</title><content type='html'>&lt;strong&gt;Tr v vi v tr Top 15 Hoa hu Vit Nam nm 2008, c gi 19 tui Phm Diu Linh kh im hi lng ting. Gp li c SV Ngoi thng mi bit Linh va chia tay "bn trai i gia ca mnh&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAaDWdl7UI/AAAAAAAACvk/6c0ovHpemPc/s1600-h/1.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 300px;" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAaDWdl7UI/AAAAAAAACvk/6c0ovHpemPc/s400/1.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332290603678297410" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Cho Linh, sau cuc thi hoa hu Vit Nam, bn c v im hi lng ting?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;- ng l sau cuc thi hoa hu Vit Nam, Linh khng c nhiu hot ng trong lnh vc ngh thut gii tr, tr mt s hot ng t thin cng vi nhng ngi bn cng tham gia cuc thi. Phn ln thi gian ca mnh, Linh tp trung cho vic hc  trng H Ngoi thng, nm th nht nn Linh cng kh vt v. Thi thong gp li cc c bn thn ca mnh sau cuc thi hoa hu, i chi v bun da l. (Ci).&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Thi gian chun b cho cuc thi hoa hu, bn va phi tp trung n thi i hc, &lt;br /&gt;lm th no  bn c th hon thnh tt c hai?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;- Trc khi thi i hc, Linh dn ton b thi gian v cng sc cho vic n thi. Sau khi thi xong Linh mi bt u chun b k hn cho cuc thi hoa hu, nn hai vic cng khng qu chng cho&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAaDEphHGI/AAAAAAAACvc/3YtIXhfHfGI/s1600-h/2.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 240px; height: 400px;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAaDEphHGI/AAAAAAAACvc/3YtIXhfHfGI/s400/2.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332290598896475234" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Sau cuc thi, mt s th sinh  c nhng hot ng ngh thut ni bt. Khi bit nhng thng tin nh th, Diu Linh c cm thy mnh thua thit?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;- Linh cng c theo di trn bo ch. Linh cm thy mng cho cc bn trc nhng thnh cng ban u. Nhng vi ring bn thn th Linh hi bun mt cht v ngh ti sao mnh khng bt u vi mt hot ng no , ti sao li lng l vy. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Tuy nhin,  cng ch l nhng suy ngh thong qua. Mi ngi chn mt con ng. C nhng bn chn con ng ngh thut gii tr. Cn Linh li chn theo ui vic hc i hc. V vy, Linh phi c gng  hon thnh tt vic hc.&lt;br /&gt;Nu c c hi tham gia hot ng ngh thut g  cng l  Linh th sc mnh thi.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAaC5EMHCI/AAAAAAAACvU/NE7mGTvOjso/s1600-h/3.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 240px; height: 400px;" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAaC5EMHCI/AAAAAAAACvU/NE7mGTvOjso/s400/3.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332290595787119650" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Mi y c thng tin Linh mi chia tay ngui yu i gia ca mnh. Thc h tin n nh no vy Linh?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;- (Ci). Mi ngui vn c hay ngh chn di th phi c i gia nh. Nhng Linh cha bao gi ngh ngi yu mnh l i gia c. Anh y bng tui Linh, gia nh cng kh gi. Nhng u phi c nh th l i gia. Bn mnh quen nhau trong mi trng hc ng, anh y i hc nh mnh thi. Nn chuyn tnh yu cng bnh thng nh bao tnh yu sinh vin khc. Tuy nhin by gi bn mnh  chia tay ri, khng cn l g ca nhau na, Linh li alone.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Nu c ai  ni Linh v sau khi tham gia cuc thi Hoa hu, c nhiu v tinh hn nn c mi ni c?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;- Khng c chuyn . n thi th ch l n thi thi. Linh v bn trai chia tay v khng hp, nh rt nhiu nhng chuyn chia tay khc. Ch vy thi v Linh khng mun nhc nhiu n chuyn .&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAaC-To-xI/AAAAAAAACvM/bB1LgufLP54/s1600-h/4.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 320px; height: 400px;" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAaC-To-xI/AAAAAAAACvM/bB1LgufLP54/s400/4.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332290597194103570" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Quan im ca Linh v chuyn chn di  i gia?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;- Linh ngh vi bt c vn  g, cng u c 2 mt. C nhng bn xinh p yu mt ngi giu c v h thc s c tnh cm vi nhau, ngi yu c iu kin th cng tt ch sao. Vic  chng c g ng phi ch trch c. Nhng cng c ngui yu i gia  li dng vt cht. Linh khng  trong hon cnh ca h th khng hiu c nn cng kh  phn xt.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Trong thi gian ti Linh s c hot ng g mi khng?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;- Mnh s vn tp trung vo vic hc  trng. K 1 Linh  c kt qu kh tt. V ch i mt c hi cng vic mi n vi Linh.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;- Cm n Linh v chc bn s t c nhiu thnh cng trong cuc sng!&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;Theo Knh 14&lt;/em&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-1632674277009177589?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/1632674277009177589'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/1632674277009177589'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/05/pham-dieu-linh-chua-bao-gio-nghi-minh.html' title='Phm Diu Linh cha bao gi ngh mnh yu &amp;quot;i gia&amp;quot;'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author><media:thumbnail xmlns:media='http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/' url='http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAaDWdl7UI/AAAAAAAACvk/6c0ovHpemPc/s72-c/1.jpg' height='72' width='72'/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-6788343268844364410</id><published>2009-05-05T03:47:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:41:41.815-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Phong Cch Tr'/><title type='text'>Nhng 'fan cung' tui teen</title><content type='html'>&lt;strong&gt;Nhng c nng mi lp 7, lp 8 nhng thch lm "Cng cha du ty", "Cng ch bong bng"... v khi "xung" ln th sn sng nh nhau v b bn b tru chc.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Gi tan s ngy cui tun, cng vic va khp li, cha kp dn dp ch lm vic th ch trng phng  r r: i siu th vi ch nh!. Ti v ch mi i mua sm vt dng gia nh cch y vi ngy, thi bui kh khn, phi tit kim, chng hiu v l do g m ch li hng hi mua sm th! Ch th tht: Con t nh ch c nng nc phi c chai ln nch m 'cng cha bong bng' ang dng, n khc i my ngy qua. Con b 9 tui, cha dy th m  i dng m phm th ng l k qui tht!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hong t, cng cha trong trng hc&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Chiu lng sp, ti i cng ch n siu th. Gia mt rng sn phm ln nch, nhn ngi m ang  hng U50 ny loay hoay tm cho bng c thng hiu m c con gi cn, thy tht ti nghip! Ch l ha khi bi vit tp lm vn ca n c 8 im tr ln, ch s thng nn by gi n i mi. By gi mua v nh chc n vui lm y! - sp ti gii thch.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAZaZRBJfI/AAAAAAAACvE/Y3nhEXbYnzQ/s1600-h/1.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 300px;" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAZaZRBJfI/AAAAAAAACvE/Y3nhEXbYnzQ/s400/1.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332289900056225266" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;center&gt;&lt;em&gt;Cng cha bong bng" Bo Thy c cc bn tr hm m&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;ng l con b vui tht, nhn thy mn qu m mnh vi vnh, n m chm ly m, hn ly hn  ri nhanh chng m ra, qut qut ln tay ht h, t v snh iu. Con s mang ci ny vo lp khoe vi cc bn. T m, ti hi nguyn nhn, con b tr li: Trong lp con, ai mun chi chung  'vng quc bong bng' phi c cc vt dng ging nh ch Bo Thy.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ri n li t trong cp ra mt xp nh, no l hnh ch Bo Thy m con gu Teddy, ch Bo Thy chi bp b, ch Bo Thy mc vy trng... Khoe xong m hnh, con b mnh dn kt lun: Ngh h, con s sn mng tay en ging ch Bo Thy! Con cng s l cng cha bong bng. Con b ni n u, ti trn xoe mt n y! Cn m n th kt lun: Ch ni n khng nghe nhng chc Bo Thy ni l n khng dm ci u.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;i mua cc vt dng ging thn tng l cn nh, con trai mnh by gi ton bt b m, ng b gi n l hong t Sn Ca, mt ci tn chng lin quan g n n. Ch hng xm ca ti khi nghe cu chuyn trn  k thm th! Ch cho bit thm, thng b con ch, hin ang l hc sinh lp 9 mt trng chuyn hn hoi, bo rng  trng bn no cng c bit danh l hong t, cng cha. Gi nhau bng tn tht l... qu lm! Tho no, c v n nh l ti nghe thng b bt my ri nghu ngao ht theo nhng bi ht ca ca s Quang Vinh.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bt cp cng thin s&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Nhng tng, chuyn n mc, xng h ging vi thn tng ca mnh ngay trong i sng  l qu . Vy m, khi n thm a chu h, ti mi bit nh hng ca cc ca s tr n khn gi tui nh cn i xa hn rt nhiu.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Chu ti tm s: Con l 'cng cha du ty' nhng bn Hong Anh (bn hc cng lp ca c b) khng chu lm 'thin s ma', con au kh lm!. Mi ln 10 tui, con b c bit g l tnh yu u m au kh! Thy c ca s Khng T Qunh lc no cng k k vi anh chng Thin Minh, tm khng ra ngi ng cp cho ging vi thn tng l chu ti au kh. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Chuyn cn bi hi hn khi cc nng cng cha du ty bt chc, khu chin vi cc c thn tng cng cha bong bng. Trc nay, ton c mi hp ph huynh khi con mnh lnh thng, tun trc, ti mi bit 'mi' hp ph huynh khi con mnh... nh nhau - ng anh ti bc xc. S l c con gi ngoan hin ca anh  tc in ln lao vo tm tc c bn cng lp (mt fan rut ca ca s Khng T Qunh) v dm chc thn tng ca mnh l... cng cha hch t trong ni! n nc ny th ph huynh c con em khng phi m m l nghin thn tng, khng than tri cng l.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAZaUHWpPI/AAAAAAAACu8/l9z_L-b9jmk/s1600-h/2.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 276px;" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAZaUHWpPI/AAAAAAAACu8/l9z_L-b9jmk/s400/2.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332289898673513714" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;center&gt;Nhng "fan cung" tui teen tung h thn tng ca mnh&lt;/center&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Chuyn gii tr chn cho mnh mt nhn vt  ngng m l chuyn ng nhin. Ngy nh, ti cng tng m ngh s Thanh Thanh Tm n mc... p xe n tn qun 11  ngm nh c o ny. ang thp th ngoi ca th ch y bc ra. Trng thy ti, ch hi han v bo: Em thch ch th hc bi xong, m ti vi ln xem ch ht l ch vui lm. Em cng hc gii, ch cng vui. ng sa , ph thi gian n nhn ch nh vy na nh!. Li khuyn ca ngi ngh s y ti nh n tn by gi. Nh  m ti hc chm hn.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Tuy nhin,   l chuyn ca ngy xa. Chuyn by gi, l cng ngh lng x v tn dng truyn thng n trit  ca ngi qun l ca s. V iu ny m tr con b hi chng nh hng thn tng n nng n. n mc theo thn tng, ng x, xng h theo thn tng... m ton l thn tng tr, nh nhnh v cha  chn chn trong c x. Cho n mt ngy, thn tng y vng phi scandal, nh chuyn c nng Vng Anh chng hn, th l cc teen ua nhau by tr trong nh ngh. - Ni ting vi cc chng trnh t thin dnh cho ngi ngho, c bit l tr em,  nhiu vng su xa khp mi min T Quc, c ca s tr Hong Dung vn khng v th m l l vi ngh thut. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAYw40BHsI/AAAAAAAACu0/iBhOZtfVwNE/s1600-h/hd_1.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; Trong cc chuyn i , Dung cng gp nhiu mnh i bt hnh.  l cc tr m ci v cc em thuc gia nh chnh sch, ngho nhng hc rt gii. Khi v H Ni, mnh  bn vi cng ty v kt hp xin ti tr t cc nh ho tm thc hin tm nguyn gip  cc tr ngho mt phn no  v tinh thn cng nh gip cc em sm c nhng sch v c bn  cc em c thm ng lc trong hc tp. y l vic lm cn thit i vi vng qu ngho ni mnh  c ln ln v vun p cho Dung trng thnh. Bi vy, cch tr n hiu qu nht l hy lm nhng vic thc s tt vi ni chn rau ct rn ca mnh. .&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Trc Tt,  Dung cng  c dp trao 52 sut hc bng, 52 phn qu Tt tng cc em hc sinh ngho vt kh, hc gii ca trng Tiu hc Sn Nga, huyn Cm Kh, tnh Ph Th. Va qua Dung cng  kt hp vi tp on dc quc t IMC n thm v tng qu ti lng tr SOS thnh TP Vit Tr, tnh Ph Th. Nhn dp ny, ng Nguyn Xun Hong - ch tch hi ng qun tr tp on IMC v ng L Cng - ph Tng gim c Vina-link  trao qu vi tng gi tr ln n gn 50 triu ng cho qu nh trng v h tr cc m. Ngoi ra on cn tng 100 sut qu cho tr em ngho vt kh tnh Vnh Phc.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAYw-1WtKI/AAAAAAAACus/Q_iN4pSTwQc/s1600-h/hd_2.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 339px;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAYw-1WtKI/AAAAAAAACus/Q_iN4pSTwQc/s400/hd_2.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332289188586239138" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAYwvROnKI/AAAAAAAACuk/tr6SLjwM0q0/s1600-h/hd_3.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 341px;" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAYwvROnKI/AAAAAAAACuk/tr6SLjwM0q0/s400/hd_3.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332289184408181922" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;center&gt;&lt;em&gt;Hong Dung n vi tr em ngho&lt;/center&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;Hot ng ny c gip g bn trong vic khng nh mnh trong bu tri ca nhc Vit? Vic lm t thin c phi  nh bng tn tui khng?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Dung lm vic  gip  nhng ngi kh hn Dung. Vic lm t thin ca Dung u phi  khng nh mnh trong bu tri ca nhc v Dung lm t thin cng khng nhm mc ch nh bng tn tui. Nhng vic Dung ang lm v ng gp d nh b vi x hi nhng n gin li xut pht t tm v tnh cm.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;K hoch t thin trong nm nay ca Dung th no?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;K hoch cho nm 2009 vn ang c Dung ln lch v lin lc vi mt s a phng ngho kh ca cc tnh  h tr v gip  cc gia nh chnh sch, kh khn, cc tr em ngho hc gii. Cng ty ca Dung hot ng kh n nh v hiu qu nn Dung khng phi lo lng v cc chng trnh ny.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAYwnRsBbI/AAAAAAAACuc/-cv6mY-P9IQ/s1600-h/hd_4.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 281px;" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAYwnRsBbI/AAAAAAAACuc/-cv6mY-P9IQ/s400/hd_4.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332289182262625714" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gii thiu ngi yu cng phi ln k hoch&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ngoi hot ng ngh thut, Dung c v cn l mt ngi kh tnh to v bit tnh ton trong cc cng vic kinh doanh?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Dung ngh mnh cn tr nn th sc  nhiu lnh vc. Vi Dung, hai vic  c tch bch ring r.  Dung c hai con ngi. Khi ng trn sn khu l mt Hong Dung phiu theo nhng xc cm ca bi ht. Cn trong cng vic kinh doanh, Dung li cn phi tnh to  tnh ton v nh hng chin lc pht trin ca cng ty  tng thi im.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nghe ni Hong Dung c mt ca hng thi trang ring v hnh nh bn cng l tn  ca hng hiu? Bn c th tit l mt s cc thng hiu bn ang s dng? &lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;(Ci). Hong Dung b coi l tn  ca hng thi trang LV, Chanel, Burberry, MG. Mnh thng s dng ti LV, qun o MG, ng h rolex, nc hoa Chanel v mt s hng thi trang khc nh Gucci, Hermet, Versarce, Cartier. Bn cnh  l Lady&amp;Gent - hng thi trang ring m Hong Dung l ngi thit k. Lc ny Dung ang thc hin nhiu d n nn tm thi ca hng c trao cho ngi khc gim st.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAYwXbdVmI/AAAAAAAACuU/10nx3s2edUA/s1600-h/hd_5.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 282px; height: 400px;" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAYwXbdVmI/AAAAAAAACuU/10nx3s2edUA/s400/hd_5.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332289178008639074" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;Th cn chuyn gia nh, n khi no bn s chia s nim vui v gii thiu vi khn gi  v na kia ca mnh y?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Chc khng lu na u. Dung mun mi ngi b bt ng v nhng k hoch ca mnh. "Gii thiu mt na" cng nm trong chui k hoch nm 2009 ca Dung. Mi ngi cng ch i v chia s vi Dung nh!&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-6470136979020749551?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/6470136979020749551'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/6470136979020749551'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/05/hoang-dung-tu-thien-khong-phai-e-anh.html' title='Hong Dung: T thin khng phi  nh bng tn tui'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author><media:thumbnail xmlns:media='http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/' url='http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAYw40BHsI/AAAAAAAACu0/iBhOZtfVwNE/s72-c/hd_1.jpg' height='72' width='72'/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-4717158665123956138</id><published>2009-05-05T03:39:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:41:41.854-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Phong Cch Tr'/><title type='text'>X tai mnh hc xng mai</title><content type='html'>&lt;strong&gt;Vi thn hnh "mnh hc xng mai" bn s mix trang phc g cho ma mi? Ngha qua mt vi gi  cc hay ho ca chng t, bn s c nhiu gi  cho ngy 8/3 sp ti y.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Mt thn hnh nh nhn xinh xn l m c ca nhiu bn gi hin nay, nhng cng l ni kh ca nhng c nng qu dy. Vi vc dng qu nh nhn nn nhiu bn gi rt kh s trong vic chn cho mnh b trang phc tht ph hp. ng qu lo lng bn nh, ch cn mt cht tinh  trong cch chn trang phc v ngha qua mt vi gi  l mi chuyn li nh nh con th  m. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Nhng chic o s mi dng rng v di c tht lng tht ngoi o hay chic o voan rng bay bng mc kt hp vi chn vy ngn hoc legging s to cho bn gi mnh dy dng v y n hn v khng h lm gim cht no chiu cao ca bn. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SgAYNROKRmI/AAAAAAAACuM/W7nNOYacCOE/s1600-h/1.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; Nhng trong cuc sng hin i, ngi ph n khng c nhiu thi gian dnh cho con b, vy lm sao  gip tr pht trin tt nht? &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Trong mi trng sng cng nghip hin i nh hin nay, cc b m phi hc cch nui con sao cho ph hp nht  nhp sng cng nghip khng nh hng n s pht trin v sc khe ca b. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf_Rm74ligI/AAAAAAAACsw/gxGH8Hli16A/s1600-h/TungPro.Com_SuaMe_1.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 300px;" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf_Rm74ligI/AAAAAAAACsw/gxGH8Hli16A/s400/TungPro.Com_SuaMe_1.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332210950670223874" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3 loi sa&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Sa non: L dng sa u tin c bu v m tit ra rt giu nng lng, cha  cc vi cht dinh dng cn thit, cc vitamin v cht khong, cc yu t min dch cn cho c th non nt ca tr s sinh, gip tr chng li bnh ng rut v cc bnh nhim khun khc, gip gim nguy c mc bnh vng da. V vy ngay gi u sau sinh, cn cho tr c b m. Nu v mt l do no  tr khng c gn m ngay th cn vt sa non ra cho tr ung.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sa chuyn tip:&lt;/strong&gt; C t ngy th 5 n ngy th 14 sau khi sinh.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sa vnh vin:&lt;/strong&gt; T ngy 10-14 sau khi sinh. T thi im ny, sa m tng nhiu v s lng v hon thin dn v cht lng vi cc thnh phn dinh dng n nh dn. Trong sut thi gian cho con b, ch  dinh dng v sinh hot, ngh ngi, lao ng ca ngi m c nh hng ln n cht lng cng nh lng sa tit ra.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf_ReOynPGI/AAAAAAAACso/KLMtUJOvqzM/s1600-h/TungPro.Com_SuaMe_2.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 286px;" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf_ReOynPGI/AAAAAAAACso/KLMtUJOvqzM/s400/TungPro.Com_SuaMe_2.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332210801126620258" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sa m l thc n tt nht cho b&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; mt b m khe mnh trong mt ngy lng sa c tit ra t 600  1.000ml, ngi m gi c lng ny 1 thng sau  v duy tr trong vng na nm.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ngi ta nhn thy rng sa m thng xuyn c gi  nhit  khong 37oC, rt ph hp vi thn nhit ca tr ng thi li rt v sinh so vi bt k ngun sa no. Ngoi ra, thnh phn ca sa m rt khc so vi sa b, trong sa m lng m (protein) v cc mui khong nh clorua, canxi nhiu gp 3 ln sa b, c bit trong sa non lng m rt cao. Trong sa m cn cha cc globulin min dch, ch yu l IgA (c nhiu nht trong sa non). IgA khng hp thu m  li trong lng rut, nn tc dng i khng vi mt s vi khun nh: E.coli v virut trong rut. Chnh v vy nhng chu b c b m t b tiu chy v cc vim nhim ng rut. Trong sa m c lactoferin  mt protein gn vi cht st, s gn kt ny lm cho mt s vi khun c hi khng pht trin c. Cht lysozym (mt loi men trong sa m cao hn sa b hng ngn ln) cht ny c tc dng tiu dit mt s vi khun c hi v nhiu loi virut khc.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf_Rd8z7rhI/AAAAAAAACsg/QLyR4bmc_9Y/s1600-h/TungPro.Com_SuaMe_3.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 300px;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf_Rd8z7rhI/AAAAAAAACsg/QLyR4bmc_9Y/s400/TungPro.Com_SuaMe_3.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332210796300316178" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Trong hai tun l u sau sinh, sa m cha 4.000 bch cu trong 1ml sa m, nhng bch cu ny tit ra IgA, lactoferin, lysozym v interferon  nhng cht ny c ch hot ng ca mt s virut. Do  trong thi gian b m, tr t b tiu chy cng nh cc bnh khc. Sa m cn c yu t bifidus  mt cht carbohydrat c cha nit l yu t cn thit cho s tng trng ca vi khun lactobacillus bifidus  c vai tr bin mt vi loi lactoza trong sa thnh acid lactic nn ngn c s tng trng ca vi khun v k sinh trng c hi lm cho phn ca tr c mi chua khc vi phn ca tr n sa b.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf_Rd03lf0I/AAAAAAAACsY/sc0x3oPLEw0/s1600-h/TungPro.Com_SuaMe_4.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 299px;" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf_Rd03lf0I/AAAAAAAACsY/sc0x3oPLEw0/s400/TungPro.Com_SuaMe_4.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332210794168155970" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tr b m t b d ng, eczema hn n sa b&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Cho con b sa m s thun li v kinh t v khng ph thuc vo gi gic, khng cn phi un nu, ra v sinh dng c pha ch. Sa m khng phi mt tin mua. Khi cho b, ngi m c nhiu thi gian gn gi vi con, iu ny rt c ch cho vic pht trin hi ha ca a tr. Ngoi ra cho con b cn gp phn hn ch sinh  v lm gim t l ung th v.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf_Rd7s9nzI/AAAAAAAACsQ/SuvIdFK34o8/s1600-h/TungPro.Com_SuaMe_5.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 299px;" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf_Rd7s9nzI/AAAAAAAACsQ/SuvIdFK34o8/s400/TungPro.Com_SuaMe_5.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5332210796002647858" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Trong mi trng sng cng nghip, khi m phi chia s thi gian cho cng vic vn cn bo m cho b c b bng nhiu cch khc nhau. Cho tr b ngay sau khi n sng, trc khi i lm v bui chiu ngay khi i lm v, k c ti v m. Nu b m lm vic gn nh th nn b tr thi gian thch hp  v nh cho con b. C gng duy tr t nht 3 ln b/ngy cho b... C th vt sa  vo bnh tit trng,  vo t lnh cho b khi i lm, v sa m c th bo qun trong bnh vi gi  nhit  bnh thng v trong vng 24 gi trong t lnh. Khi i lm v, phi v sinh trc khi b con v cho b. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/Sf_RdhQFLvI/AAAAAAAACsI/HJ1waCrzcE4/s1600-h/TungPro.Com_SuaMe_6.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px;
