scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Scandal - Shocking'/><title type='text'>nh nng Minh Hng v b mt tht ca Knh14</title><content type='html'>Trong thi gian gn y, c mt s trang web  lm r ln mt tin n ca s Minh Hng l "nh nng", v cc i tng pht tn c cc trang web  ch ch danh l din n GameVN, vy, s thc l g ?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;GameK, Kenh14, GameThu  li dng cc cuc tn gu trong mc th gin ca GameVn  tung tin n tht thit nhm to Scandal cho Minh Hng v bi nh GameVN.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1) a thng tin bo chi sai lch v da trn ngun khng ng tin cy.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Khi u ca s vic l trang web GameK (Gamek.vn)  ng tin rng Ran Idol Minh Hng b "l nh nng".&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Trang web GameK  cho ng trn trang thng tin ca mnh l Box Th Gin (sau y gi l BoxTG) ca trang din n tho lun GameVN tung cc "hnh nh nng" c cho l ca Minh Hng chp trong cc t th gi cm ln v co but mt thnh vin trong din n GameVN vi nickname l MapleKhoa ng cc hnh . K thc ngi tung nh ln khng phi l MapleKhoa m l mt thnh vin khc. Th nhng trang GameK  cho a hnh nh chp mn hnh ( c ct xn) v mt bi vit ca MapleKhoa nhm tung thng tin l din n GameVN l ngun gc pht tn cc nh c cho l ca Minh Hng ng thi c vic pht tn cc nh nude. K thc cu ni ca MapleKhoa l mt tr a nhn ngy C thng t ( c chnh MapleKhoa khng nh) ng thi cu ni ca MapleKhoa khng c bng chng g cho bit nu cu ta c s hu nh nude th  l nh ca Minh Hng. Vic GameK a tin da trn thng tin t mt khu vc gii tr ca mt din n tho lun (mt knh tr chuyn mang tnh cht ni b) v c bit l ly c s t mt nhn vt khng r danh tnh tht ln c s xc thc ca li ni (thc cht l ni xo)  tung ra bi bo cho thy s thiu trch nhim v hiu bit ca trang thng tin i chng ny. Ngoi ra vic GameK ch ch danh trang GameVN l ngun c th nhm mc ch bi nh uy tn ca din n ny bng kh nng cng b tin tc rng ri ca GameK.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;K thc ta tht vic pht tn rng ri cc nh gi cm ca Minh Hng  c chnh GameK thc hin do GameK c chc nng pht tn thng tin mnh hn rt nhiu so vi GameVN. Tuy nhin trang web ny sau   nhn thy sai lm v cho d b bt cc hnh nh  xung, sau khi  ng mt thi gian di.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SdrFkplaDqI/AAAAAAAAAeg/QyRM0-_67xw/s1600-h/TungPro.Com_MinhHang_1.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 300px; height: 400px;" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SdrFkplaDqI/AAAAAAAAAeg/QyRM0-_67xw/s400/TungPro.Com_MinhHang_1.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5321783143120375458" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;S vic tip theo sau , Minh Hng xc nhn l cc nh  tht s l ca c ta. Tin tc ny bt ngun t GameK v Kenh14.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Tuy nhin cc bng chng ca Minh Hng a ra l rt m h. Minh Hng (sau y gi l MH)  khng nh rng s nh  l do m c ta chp vo dp sinh nht khi c ta nhn c qu l cc b  lt t m ca c. Sau  c cho rng s nh ny  b mt cp khi c b mt tr my nh v Laptop.&lt;br /&gt;iu ng ng  y l cc s vic MH a ra c qu nhiu im bt hp l. Th nht l cc nh chp  kh lu (t sn Minh Hng) nhng vn ch  trong my nh (c khng nh khng chp i u), y l im bt thng. Th hai l trong lc chp cc hnh  khng c bn th 3 chng kin  xc nhn rng m con c  chp cc hnh  ti thi im . V th 3 cng khng c bn no xc nhn hay c bng chng rng trong my nh hay laptop ti thi im b mt c hnh ca c. Ngoi ra c cng cho rng "cng an vn ha"  tm ra "th phm" ca vic pht tn hnh nh, nhng cc bi bo c lin quan sau  li a cc tin sai s vic. Liu c phi y l Scandal do c to dng nn  nh bng tn tui hay y l chuyn ba ca cc trang thng tin in t ni trn ?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Cu chuyn cha dng li  y, tip treo trn trang Kenh14 cn ng bi khng nh ngi pht tn chnh l MapleKhoa&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Nh  ni  trn, MapleKhoa tht s khng phi l ngi tung nh nng, cu y l ngi  a tin bng a rng c nhiu nh p hn (y dc MapleKhoa xc nhn l mt tr a  mt ni dng  a gin). Th nhng Kenh 14 li ch ch danh l MapleKhoa lm vic ny.  che ia61u cho hnh ng ca mnh, Kenh 14  c  lm m i nhng chi tit nh tn ca ngi vit bi, bit che (MapleK***) nhng li  lin kt n bi vit trc  ni v GameVN. iu ny cho thy Kenh14 vn ngm m ch gameVN l ni pht tn cc cnh gi cm "ring t"  - ("(ni u tin  tung hnh Minh Hng ln mng Vit Nam)"- Nguyn vn.&lt;br /&gt;Bi vit ny c nhiu im s h v nghi vn. Th nht ton b bi vit khng c nh hay on ghi m chng t Kenh 14  trc tip tr chuyn vi MapleKhoa. th hai bi vit lp lun rng tr a ny gy nh hng n MH v lm n ha thnh "mt tr xuyn tc", "tr by b" m qun rng y l khu vc c nhn ca mt din n tho lun ni b, tc c th xem nh tr a ca mt nhm bn b v khng c tc dng bo ch. Th ba l nhng vic l m m v d nh che hnh chp bi vit, chng ta c th   Avatar ca i tng khc nhau, khng c lin kt n bi vit , khng c hnh chp chng thc post, tn b lm m. Bi vit  ngy 30-thng 3 nhng trong danh sch bi vit ca MapleKhoa khng h c chi tit chng t cu c post bi vo ngy ny.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SdrFgj9iVDI/AAAAAAAAAeY/p5L43OcSCj0/s1600-h/TungPro.Com_MinhHang_2.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 271px;" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SdrFgj9iVDI/AAAAAAAAAeY/p5L43OcSCj0/s400/TungPro.Com_MinhHang_2.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5321783072891491378" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Tip theo l Kenh 14 li ng thm mt cu chuyn ba t rng MapleKhoa  "n hn" v c cuc tr chuyn vi Kenh 14. Thc t rng MapleKhoa ch b p lc tinh thn do cc bi bo bi chnh cc trang GameK, Kenh 14, GameThu lien tip tung ra. Kenh 14  i dng mt hnh chp trong trang tho lun ca GameVN  lm bng chng gi to cho "cuc tr chuyn" ca h ng ln. Nh cc bi vit trc, ln bo ny cng y nhng chi tit nc ci. D thy nht l vic trc  Kenh 14 khng nh MapleKhoa sinh nm 91, nhng trong bi bo ny li vit "Mnh ang hc v mng ti mt trng cao ng, va hc vn ha va hc ngh lun. ". Khng r bng cch no mt cu hc sinh sinh nm 91 li chc cao ng trong thi im ny ? Mt thin ti chng ? Li cn "va hc vn ha va hc ngh" ? trng Cao ng no  TP HCM  kh nng cho vic ny ?. C bi vit khng h c mt hnh nh/ on bng ghi m no chng t rng MapleKhoa tr chuyn vi Kenh 14 cho thy y hon ton l s ba t ca t bo ny.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SdrFgKxfwpI/AAAAAAAAAd4/y0BNkTx7MQ8/s1600-h/TungPro.Com_MinhHang_6.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 267px;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SdrFgKxfwpI/AAAAAAAAAd4/y0BNkTx7MQ8/s400/TungPro.Com_MinhHang_6.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5321783066130104978" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2) S hp tc bi nh GameVN ca GameK, GameThu, Kenh 14.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Li dng Scandal ny, cc trang thng tin in t trn  toa rp nhau lin tip tung cc bi vit gy nh hng n uy tn ca GameVN&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Chng ta hy xem cu ny Hm nay vo n 2 qu la ca anh em, khng ung cng vo ngy 1/4, n la m ph c ngi tht s y l s ba t ca GameK nhm vo din n GameVN nhm mc ch trc li, vn  ny ti s phn tch sau. Tuy nhin cc bn s khng th tm thy bn no  GameVN ni cu ny. GameK  li dng tr a ca cc thnh vin GameVN vi nhau nhm a thng tin rng cc thnh vin GameVN li dng danh ting cc trang thng tin in t ng tin by b. K thc y l tr a c thng t ca cc thnh vin ni b box th gin.&lt;br /&gt;Tip theo l Kenh 14 li tm cch gn kt v vic ny v GameVn vi cc vic khc nh HTL, thy tin, an L...c bit cu ni "Khng c g ni nhanh hn scandal sex, v th nhiu thnh vin  chn cch thi phng qu mc cu chuyn  gy tn tui trong forum, cn admin th tha h cu ko visit, member cho forum ca mnh." l ch ch danh gameVN mun "ni ting, cu khch" bng cc a Scandal Sex, ng ngha vi vic gn ghp GameVN l din n ni ting nh i try. Tht s ai cng bitt GameVN l 1 forum v Game lu i v trong sch. Trang Kenh 14 l k sinh sau  mun nhng ang mun li dng kh nng cung cp thng tin rng ri ca mnh  h nhc GameVN, y l nhm mc ch g ?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;"Ngoi nhng k chuyn th cu, ng k trong vic moi mc scandal cn phi nhc n i ng a dua a tng theo m ng. Thnh phn ny ch bit ti 50% s tht nhng  hng phi trn 200%. Cha cn bit ng sai ra sao, ngay lp tc h  c th ln ging bi mc hoc thm tht cho cu chuyn thm phn hp dn."&lt;br /&gt;Cu ni ny c gn vi nh chp mt tr a C Thng T ca ni b din n GameVN. Tht s th nhng ngi "bi mc Scandal, th cu..." chnh l cc trang GameK, Kenh 14. H  li dng tr ua v t ca vi thnh vin trong din n nhm bi nh GameVN, tung lin tip cc tin bi thiu  tin cy t ngun cho n bi vit nhm tng s lng truy cp cho mnh. CHng ta u c th d dng nhn thy rng GameVN khng phi l knh thng tin i chng nh cc trang trn, kh nng ph bin thp v cc trang GameK, Kenh 14...u c tin s ng cc nh gi cm nh Bikini,  lt...ngay trn trang ch ca h nhm cu khch. Bi bo trn  bin h thnh nhng k t tt vo mt mnh.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Vy vn  tht s  y l g? GameK, GameThu, Kenh 14 t lu  c him khch vi GameVN v h rt ganh t v s lu i cng nh hiu bit ca cc thnh vin GameVN, nhng ngi thng a ra nhng im sai/v l trong cc bi vit ca GameK, GameThu, Kenh 14...Cc bi vit lin tip gn y cho thy h li dung kh nng truyn b thng tin ln ca mnh vi chc nng nh cc bo in t nhm gim uy tn ca GameVN, tng Page view cho h v gim ngun thu nhp ca GameVN qua cc qung co trn din n vi hy vng GameVN sp .&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SdrFga_gGUI/AAAAAAAAAeQ/t_dj1WDEc5Q/s1600-h/TungPro.Com_MinhHang_3.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 265px;" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SdrFga_gGUI/AAAAAAAAAeQ/t_dj1WDEc5Q/s400/TungPro.Com_MinhHang_3.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5321783070483814722" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Chng ta c th hy cc lun c ca GameK, GameThu, Kenh 14 a ra rt m h, thiu xc thc. Mang nhiu mc ch xu. Cha k mi quan h ca "MapleKhoa" (c cc trang trn  cp) vi MapleKhoa thc, vi MH v cc Kenh14. Khi trang im, n mc ra ng, ti khng lm mnh xu i so vi nhng ci sn c. Cn ci duyn, n l tri sinh, ch mnh khng t to ra c.&lt;br /&gt;- By gi chng thiu cng ngh v ngi c gu, nhng u phi ai cng hp dn?&lt;br /&gt;- Ngoi c gu, s t tin rt quan trng, nhng ti khng t tin thi qu. Ti bit mnh c ci g, mnh mnh ci g v ci g mnh khng c. C th l ngoi hnh hi thp, nhng khun mt ca ti rt trung ha.&lt;br /&gt;Ti c cp mt hi nh, nhng hin nay li l mt. Ti quan nim cp mt p nh nh nhn, v ti t tin vo nh nhn ca mnh, ch khng phi mt to, mi cong mi l p.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SdA9e1PaOwI/AAAAAAAAAZ4/notYsUdzk28/s1600-h/TungPro.Com_MaiKhoi_8.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 230px;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SdA9e1PaOwI/AAAAAAAAAZ4/notYsUdzk28/s400/TungPro.Com_MaiKhoi_8.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5318818759821638402" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;- &lt;em&gt;Ch ni ting n mc gi cm! S h hang  cho ch cm gic g?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;- Th nht, v thm m, ngi thp v trn nh ti mc h p hn mc kn. Th hai, ti thy thoi mi. Th ba, ti thch khoa nhng ci p ca mnh. u phi ai mc  h cng p, vn  l bit khoe thi. V d mnh c ngc th khoe ngc. Thiu g c c chn di khoe chn, nhng ti u c khoe chn. Bng chng l rt t khi ti mc vy ngn.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SdA9nWjKBdI/AAAAAAAAAaA/Vd6F5A6UFWk/s1600-h/TungPro.Com_MaiKhoi_7.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 341px;" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SdA9nWjKBdI/AAAAAAAAAaA/Vd6F5A6UFWk/s400/TungPro.Com_MaiKhoi_7.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5318818906201785810" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ngoi ra, ti thch h eo lm. V ci eo l ng cong p nht ca ph n. Cn chuyn khng mc o ngc, theo quan nim ca ti khng mc mi p, mc o ngc rt cng, nt p  ging nh bp b vy, xa ri!&lt;br /&gt;By gi nt p phi thoi mi, gi cm, mm mi. ng nhin phi ty thuc vo qun o v phi c ngc p na!&lt;br /&gt;Ti thch khoa nhng ci p ca mnh. u phi ai mc  h cng p, vn  l bit khoe thi&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;- T cch n mc, cch ni chuyn, c bit l nhng pht ngn, ny sinh kh nhiu nhn xt v Mai Khi, trong  c c nhn xt v s lng l. Ch  nghe bao gi cha?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;- Ti b nhiu ngi ni lng l lm. Nhng ti khng lng l. Lng l l ngi bn ny lic bn kia, cn ti hon ton khng c. Ai nhn tin chc gho, tn tnh, ti cng khng nhn li, khng y a g ht, vy sao ni ti lng l.&lt;br /&gt;Nu thch ai, nh mt ca ti ch lng l vi ngi  thi. M ti khng thch t lng l lm u, ni ti yu iu thc n th c. Mi y nht trang tin Thesun  ng ti on clip gy sc trong sinh nht ca Hugh Hefner. title='Cuc thi &amp;quot;hn&amp;quot; ti TQ'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-8529672500511489406</id><published>2009-04-29T05:32:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:41:46.850-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><title type='text'>Tnh sinh vin trc ngng ca tt nghip</title><content type='html'>&lt;strong&gt;Thay v vt sc cho k thc tp, chun b cho bi lun vn, nhiu sinh vin nm cui li mt n mt ng lo lng cho tnh yu ca mnh s i u v u sau khi nhn bng tt nghip.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ngi v k &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Trc ngng ca tt nghip, sinh vin nm cui gnh trn mnh rt nhiu ni lo v tin nong, cng vic. Cnh , mt vn  khng t ngi phi nng lng l chuyn tnh cm. Nhn tm bng c nhn vi mt s ngi ng ngha vi vic phi dt khot vi tnh yu ca mnh. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Khi bn b ang vt chn ln c cho k thc tp, li phi chun b bi lun vn hoc n thi tt nghip th Hin, sinh vin trng H V li lo lng n pht m chuyn tnh yu ca mnh. Hin yu Hun t khi c hc nm th hai. Hun cng qu vi Hin, hc Ngn hng, trc c mt kha. Hun tnh lm vic  H Ni mt nm, ch Hin tt nghip, sau  hai ngi s khn gi v qu. Nhng cng vic Hun sun s nn gi y Hun s khng v qu. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SfhJEwW1_4I/AAAAAAAAA8Y/eTDNuKQmI_k/s1600-h/vtc_297620_tinhsv.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 300px;" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SfhJEwW1_4I/AAAAAAAAA8Y/eTDNuKQmI_k/s400/vtc_297620_tinhsv.jpg" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5330090505042001794" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;center&gt;&lt;em&gt;Trc ngng ca tt nghip, tnh yu tr thnh mt mi &lt;br /&gt;lo ln ca cc tn c nhn.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Th l, thay v vt sc cho k cui, Hin li phi xin x ngi yu suy ngh li. Hin cho hay: Mnh hc ngnh xut bn, ngay thc tp nhiu ngi cn phi thc tp tri ngh. Ri vo thi im khng hong th ny xin vic  H Ni l iu khng tng, nh mnh li c hiu sch  qu, ch cn con ng v. Nhng anh y i  li, th khc no ni chia tay. &lt;br /&gt;Cng tui v cng chun b ra trng nhng Mnh v Tho cng ang nhiu kh nng ng ai ny i. Mnh hc trng Thng mi, qu Thanh Ha ang c  nh tin Nam v anh ch u lp nghip trong . Cn Tho, c tt nghip ngnh bo ch,  kh nng  bm tr  H Ni. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Mnh chia s: C y  Hng Yn, l con gi duy nht trong gia nh, c hi  H Ni cng nhiu, ni c y vo Nam l lm kh cho ngi ta. Cn mnh, th tht bt u mt cng vic  Th  qu kh, vo Nam  c nn tng, khng i cng khng c". &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Nguyt, mt n sinh trng H Lut bn khon: "Ngi yu em ang lm vic  TPHCM. Em khng bit mnh c nn vo Nam khng?".  &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;ng thi vi vic tt nghip, nhiu sinh vin ang phi gii quyt cho xong chuyn tnh cm. Cnh sinh vin nm cui tht tnh v th cng din ra nhiu hn. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;My, sinh vin nm ba H Vn ha cho bit: Phng mnh c bn ch nm cui th ba ch ang phi b ngi yu. Tt c u v cng vic, mi ngi mi tnh, ngi no v qu ngi ny, ngi  li, ngi v. Ch no cng bun cng khc, c ch cn i cht. Ri My lc u: Chng l tnh yu thi sinh vin lun c thi hn sao. Th ny em cng thy lo qu!.  &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gian nan tm chung bn  &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;i mt vi cnh ng ai ny i nhiu ngi tm bng li thot  c  bn cnh ngi mnh yu. Nhng con ng  n c ch ca h cn lm nhng gian nan. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Khng h nm trong d nh nhng khi thi gian nhn bng tt nghip sp cn k, Giang, sinh vin ngnh K ton, trng Thng mi ln ngay k hoch i hc tip  c  li vi ngi yu. Ngi yu Giang  i lm, ra trng nu c khng  li H Ni th chc chn cng ng ai ny i. Nhng vi Giang, xin c mt cng vic ng  lc ny  Th  khng phi l d. C ch cn nc chn cch hc tip  gi chn ngi yu. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Giang ni: Em s v nh ngh ngi mt thi gian, sau  xung hc vi kha o to chng ch v kinh t ch n t thi cao hc. Hi v vic hc tip ca mnh Giang tht th chia s: Gia nh em kh khn, vic hc tip tht ra khng ph hp vi hon cnh ca em lm nhng gi ch cn cch  th em mi c c hi tip tc  li ch khng th chia tay. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Cn hn hai thng na mi n ngy nhn bng nhng Lan, H T.L ngnh kin trc li c k hoch n kh hiu. Bn trai Lan  Ph Th, ang lm vic  qu. Lan c kh nng  li H Ni nhng anh chng khng h c  nh chuyn xung v cng trong cnh lp lng: Nu em v c Ph Th th ci. Lan ni vi bn b, c sn sng xin v Vit Tr lm... cng nhn nh my Dt  c ly ngi mnh yu. D nh ca Lan khng c ai tn thnh. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Hng, H Bch khoa cng ang au u v chng bit phi xoay x th no khi c cu v bn gi u c  nh v qu sau khi tt nghip. Hng qu  Bc Ninh, bn gi cu qu H Tnh. Qu em nhiu khu cng nghip, ngnh hc ca em rt ph hp nhng bn gi em cng i v qu - Hng ni. Hng ang tnh s theo bn gi v H Tnh nhng y lo lng: V ni xa l, cng vic li kh khn chng bit s i n u. Li thm b m mnh cng ang phn i kch lit. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Trc khi kt thc qung i sinh vin, bn cnh nhiu ni lo th chuyn tnh cm cng ang tr thnh mt thch thc i vi cc tn c nhn, k s&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/8196011166746920645-8529672500511489406?l=bikini2012.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/8529672500511489406'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8196011166746920645/posts/default/8529672500511489406'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://bikini2012.blogspot.com/2009/04/tinh-sinh-vien-truoc-nguong-cua-tot.html' title='Tnh sinh vin trc ngng ca tt nghip'/><author><name>mmovn</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08943472905816451420</uri><email>mjning@gmail.com</email></author><media:thumbnail xmlns:media='http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/' url='http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_dAsqJt5v5W0/SfhJEwW1_4I/AAAAAAAAA8Y/eTDNuKQmI_k/s72-c/vtc_297620_tinhsv.jpg' height='72' width='72'/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8196011166746920645.post-8524225017504833045</id><published>2009-04-28T21:55:00.000-07:00</published><updated>2011-03-07T23:41:46.917-08:00</updated><category scheme='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind' term='http://schemas.google.com/blogger/2008/kind#post'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Scandal - Shocking'/><title type='text'>Sextoy : Th chi ng tnh ln ngi</title><content type='html'>&lt;strong&gt;Chuyn tay nhau mt ci n du bng cao su, nhm ba c bn trng TH h hng ci ri giu bit vo cp sau  ngi rm r bn chuyn:Tao xem phim thy by gi bn nc ngoi bn teen chi hng gi khng !          &lt;div class="atc_txt"&gt;           &lt;span id="_ctl0_rContent_lbContinue"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id="_ctl0_rContent_lbBody"&gt;&lt;p align="justify"&gt;Dch v ngn ti nguyn h thng nht l &lt;strong&gt;Automatic Updates&lt;/strong&gt;, chy thng trc trong b nh v nh k kt ni ti my ch ca Micrsoft  cp nht cc bn v li h thng. Tuy nhin, bn c th ti mt ln bn v Service Pack 3  cp nht h thng v tt dch v ny bng cch phm phi chut vo My Computer chn Manage, ti mc Services v nhn p mc Automatic Updates. Nhng dch v ny lm gim ng k tc  my tnh ca ngi dng.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Nu l my tnh s dng trong gia nh bn cn c th tt tip mt s dch v nh &lt;strong&gt;Computer Browser&lt;/strong&gt; (d qut cc my tnh trn mng ni b); &lt;strong&gt;DHCP Client v DNS Client &lt;/strong&gt;(cp pht a ch mng t ng - c th tt nu phn thng s mng  c t c nh);&lt;strong&gt; Error Reporting and Event Log &lt;/strong&gt;(cung cp thng tin h tr k thut vin khc phc s c khi my tnh c li);&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Help and Support &lt;/strong&gt;(tr gip v hng dn s dng h thng bng ting Anh); &lt;strong&gt;Indexing Service&lt;/strong&gt; (nh ch mc h tr tm kim tp tin nhanh); &lt;strong&gt;Messenger &lt;/strong&gt;(h tr gi thng ip cnh bo gia my trm v my ch trn mng); &lt;strong&gt;Print Spooler &lt;/strong&gt;(vng nh m  np trc cc trang in - c th tt nu my tnh ca bn khng c my in);&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Remote Registry&lt;/strong&gt; (cho php thay i cu hnh h thng t xa); &lt;strong&gt;System Restore Service &lt;/strong&gt;(phc hi h thng khi gp s c xung t phn mm hoc cc trnh iu khin); &lt;strong&gt;Windows Image Acquisition &lt;/strong&gt;(ly nh t my nh k thut s hoc my qut - nu bn khng c thit b s tng ng th c th tt dch v ny); &lt;strong&gt;Wireless Zero Configuration &lt;/strong&gt;(cu hnh t ng cho thit b mng khng dy).&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; tt cc dch v ny, bn thc hin mi thao tc nh i vi dch v&lt;strong&gt; Automatic Updates.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ngoi ra, bn cng nn tt c tnh nng &lt;strong&gt;Remote Assistance v Remote Desktop Sharing&lt;/strong&gt;. y l nhng tnh nng cho php cc k thut vin h tr bn t xa, truy cp vo my tnh ca bn  khc phc li.
